wn%20diamonds%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20set%20to%20tumble%20this%20year%2C%20industry%20veterans%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Zimnisky%2C%20a%20leading%20diamond%20analyst%2C%20foresees%20jewelers%20scaling%20back%20their%20business%20in%20lab-grown%20diamonds%20while%20ramping%20up%20their%20focus%20on%20natural%20diamonds%20over%20the%20next%20year.%20In%20fact%2C%20most%20jewelers%20aren't%20even%20bothering%20to%20stock%20lab-grown%20diamonds%20in%20inventory%2C%20and%20are%20only%20purchasing%20them%20on%20consignment%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20exact%20opposite%20of%20what%20jewelers%20have%20been%20doing%20since%202018%2C%20when%20the%20hype%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frise-and-fall-diamonds-lab-grown-2021-12%5C%22%3Elab-grown%20diamonds%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20fad%20is%20starting%20to%20fade%20a%20bit%2C%26quot%3B%20Zimnisky%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20lower-priced%20retailers%20like%20Walmart%20and%20Pandora%2C%20who%20have%20started%20to%20%26quot%3Baggressively%26quot%3B%20push%20lab-grown%20stones.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20become%20a%20lot%20more%20mainstream.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrices%20for%20lab-grown%20diamonds%20will%20continue%20to%20fall%20over%20the%20next%20year%2C%20he%20said.%20Ziminsky%20didn't%20have%20a%20price%20target%2C%20but%20said%20he%20believed%20loose%20lab-grown%20diamonds%20could%20see%20nearly%20the%20same%20price%20decline%20as%20they%20did%20in%202023%2C%20which%20the%20jewelry%20analytics%20firm%20Tenoris%20estimated%20to%20be%20about%2020%25%20in%20the%2012%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20November.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECormac%20Kinney%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20commodities%20trading%20firm%20Diamond%20Standard%2C%20believes%20the%20plunge%20could%20be%20even%20steeper%20as%20the%20hype%20over%20lab-grown%20gems%20fades.%20Man-made%20diamond%20prices%20could%20ultimately%20drop%20another%2050%25-80%25%2C%20he%20estimated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFashion%20jewelry%20is%20always%20worth%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20real%20jewelry%2C%26quot%3B%20Kinney%20said.%20%26quot%3BOnly%20real%20is%20rare.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EMan-made%20fad%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20hard%20to%20imagine%20why%20man-made%20diamonds%20were%20so%20popular%20last%20year.%20Even%20A-list%20celebrities%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeghan-markle-lab-grown-diamond-jeweller-kimai-rings-2020-10%5C%22%3EEmma%20Watson%20and%20Meghan%20Markle%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20known%20to%20buy%20lab-grown%20jewelry%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20cheaper%20and%20basically%20identical%20to%20the%20naked%20eye.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20basically%20a%20manufactured%20version%20of%20one%20of%20humans'%20most%20valuable%20and%20natural%20resources%2C%26quot%3B%20Zimnisky%20said%20of%20lab-grown%20stones.%20%26quot%3BIt%20basically%20allowed%20consumers%20to%20buy%20a%20diamond%20at%20really%20affordable%20prices%20that%20allowed%20consumers%20to%20buy%20very%20large%20diamonds%20that%20would%20cost%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20if%20they%20were%20natural%20diamonds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20of%20the%20shine%20behind%20lab-grown%20gems%20has%20diminished%2C%20largely%20because%20they're%20so%20widely%20available.%20Lab-grown%20diamonds%20now%20make%20up%20around%2020%25%20of%20the%20total%20diamond%20market%2C%20Zimnisky%20estimates%2C%20up%20from%20nearly%20zero%20percent%20in%202015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESales%20of%20lab-grown%20diamond%20jewelry%20soared%2051%25%20in%20the%2012%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20November%2C%20while%20sales%20of%20loose%20lab-grown%20diamonds%20grew%2047%25%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tenoris.bi%2Fus-jewelry-market-positive-in-november-holiday-season%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.tenoris.bi%2Fus-jewelry-market-positive-in-november-holiday-season%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETenoris%3C%2Fa%3E%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20prices%20for%20lab-grown%20diamonds%20have%20actually%20been%20declining%20since%202015%2C%20the%20year%20they%20first%20started%20to%20become%20mainstream.%20Back%20then%2C%20a%20man-made%20diamond%20was%20priced%20at%20around%20a%2010%25%20discount%20to%20a%20natural%20diamond.%20Today%2C%20they're%20priced%20at%20a%2090%25%20discount%2C%20Zimnisky%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20kind%20of%20just%20bought%20it%2C%20and%20they%20thought%2C%20'you're%20the%20only%20one%20with%20a%20three-carat%20diamond.%20But%20%E2%80%A6%20if%20you%20go%20to%20a%20wedding%20these%20days%2C%20you're%20just%20looking%20at%20people's%20engagement%20rings%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20three-%2C%20four-%2C%20five-carat%20diamonds%20and%20it's%20become%20ubiquitous%2C%26quot%3B%20Zimnisky%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20now%20you%20might%20actually%20start%20to%20see%20the%20opposite%20happen%2C%20where%20people%20are%20like%2C%20I%20just%20want%20a%20smaller%20natural%20diamond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20synthetic%20diamond%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20a%20natural%20diamond%2C%26quot%3B%20Kinney%20added.%20%26quot%3BAny%20gem%20lab%20can%20tell%20the%20difference%2C%20and%20your%20friends%20probably%20can%20too%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20the%20diamond%20does%20not%20match%20your%20economic%20status.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20demand%20for%20lab-grown%20stones%20will%20disappear%2C%20and%20the%20gems%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-dont-understand-why-you-wouldnt-buy-lab-grown-diamond-2023-6%5C%22%3Ewill%20surely%20still%20hold%20appeal%20for%20some%20buyers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20sales%20will%20likely%20grow%20at%20a%20slower%20pace.%20Zimnisky%20estimates%20that%20sales%20growth%20could%20fall%20as%20low%20as%20a%20single-digit%20percentage%20this%20year%2C%20down%20from%20the%2020%25-30%2