2C%20Says%20Anupam%20Mittal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAnupam%20Mittal%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Shaadi.com%20and%20'Shark%20Tank%20India'%20judge%20has%20become%20a%20household%20name.%20Mr%20Mittal%20has%20made%20a%20significant%20impact%20in%20the%20business%20world%20with%20his%20remarkable%20achievements.%20The%20entrepreneur%20spoke%20to%20%C2%A0Bombay%20Shaving%20Company%20CEO%20Shantanu%20Deshpande%20on%20his%20Barbershop%20podcast%20and%20stated%20that%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20and%20the%20worst%26quot%3B%20example%20for%20founders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20the%20reason%2C%20Mr%20Mittal%20highlighted%20Mr%20Musk's%20vast%20business%20empire.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20believe%20they%20can%20do%20what%20he's%20doing-%20run%2010%20companies%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20And%20we%20know%20it's%20very%20hard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20understandable%20if%20a%20founder%20says%20that%20it%20has%20been%20five%20years-%20I%20want%20to%20buy%20a%20house%20and%20all%20that.%20But%20if%20you%20are%20going%20to%20create%20wealth%20for%20yourself%20while%20your%20investors%20have%20not%2C%20that%20is%20a%20big%20no.%20It%20becomes%20tough.%20Then%20your%20incentives%20will%20not%20align.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FDZdyUGThPLc%3Fsi%3D1BE6wNrn8WHk3stc%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20podcast%2C%20Mr%20Mittal%20also%20recalled%20starting%20as%20an%20entrepreneur%20and%20going%20from%20living%20in%20a%20small%20Mumbai%20apartment%20with%2020%20people%20to%20becoming%20a%20multimillionaire%20in%20his%2020s.%20Mr%20Mittal%20clarified%20that%20his%20father%20had%20a%20successful%20business%20in%20textile%20but%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20they%20were%20not%20well-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20Mr%20Deshpande%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20wouldn't%20realise%20it%20as%20kids%2C%20but%2020%20of%20us%20were%20living%20in%20a%201%2C000-square-foot%20house%20at%20the%20time.%20People%20were%20sleeping%20on%20the%20dining%20table%2C%20under%20the%20dining%20table.%20But%20as%20kids%2C%20you%20don't%20think%20of%20that.%20You%20enjoy%20having%20so%20many%20kids%20around%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20struggling%20for%20a%20few%20years%2C%20Mr%20Mittal's%20father%20became%20successful%2C%20and%20Anupam%20Mittal%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20for%20studies.%20However%2C%20he%20couldn't%20find%20a%20job%20there%20and%20he%20decided%20not%20to%20share%20it%20with%20his%20parents%20as%20they%20would%20insist%20him%20return.%20He%20revealed%20he%20had%20no%20money.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%20the%20situation%20was%20such%20that%20I%20had%20no%20money%2C%20and%20if%20I%20asked%20them%20for%20money%20they%20say%2C%20'Where's%20your%20salary%3F'%20I%20had%20no%20money.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20experienced%20hunger.%20This%20is%20something%20everybody%20should%20do%20in%20life%20once%20because%20experiencing%20hunger%20teaches%20you%20a%20lot.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20I%20didn't%20eat%20for%20two%20or%20three%20days%20because%20I%20couldn't%20eat.%20How%20long%20could%20friends%20help%3F%20They%20would've%20helped%2C%20but%20you%20also%20feel%20bad%20after%20a%20while...%20Credit%20cards%20are%20maxed%20out%2C%20everything%20is%20finished.%20It%20wasn't%20like%20I%20was%20out%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20but%20I%20did%20experience%20some%20level%20of%20lack%20of%20resources%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708261260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fjpg9mguo_anupam-mittal_625x300_18_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Felon-musk-great-and-worst-example-for-founders-says-anupa