0broke%20her%20arm%20a%20month%20ago%2C%20and%20he%20had%20to%20pay%20an%20exorbitant%20medical%20bill%20which%20he%20says%20has%20landed%20him%20in%20debt%2C%20as%20he%20has%20not%20received%20his%20salary%20since%20August%202023.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EESIC%20card%20bhi%20nahin%20hai%20ki%20kuch%20madad%20ho%20paaye%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(I%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20an%20Employees%E2%80%99%20State%20Insurance%20Corporation%20card%20which%20could%20have%20been%20of%20help)%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20the%20story%20of%20DUSIB%E2%80%99s%20Jan%20Suvidha%20Complexes.%20The%20staff%2C%20including%20the%20supervisor%2C%20the%20caretaker%20and%20the%20safai%20karamcharis%2C%20have%20not%20received%20their%20wages%20for%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Jan%20Suvidha%20Complexes%20serve%20the%20population%20in%20jhuggi%20clusters%2Fslum%20areas%20at%20different%20locations%20in%20Delhi%2C%20in%20order%20to%20make%20them%20open-defecation-free.%20This%20was%20done%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Abhiyaan%20or%20Clean%20India%20Mission.%20The%20JSCs%20were%20earlier%20run%20on%20%E2%80%98pay%20%26amp%3B%20use%E2%80%99%20basis%20by%20the%20DUSIB%3B%20however%2C%20all%20the%20toilet%20facilities%20were%20made%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdelhishelterboard.in%2Fmain%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2FBUDGET-2018-19-1.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efree%20of%20user%20charge%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20effect%20from%20January%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAt%20present%2C%20DUSIB%20runs%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdelhiplanning.delhi.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FPlanning%2Fgeneric_multiple_files%2Fevaluation_study_of_functioning_of_jan_suvidha_complexes_of_dusib_in_delhi.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eover%20662%20JSCs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20Delhi%2C%20serving%20more%20than%20300%2C000%20jhuggis%20with%20around%201.5%20million%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EOverworked%20and%20underpaid%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EKanhaiya%20Singh%20is%20a%20caretaker%20at%20a%20JSC%20in%20RK%20Puram%E2%80%99s%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20Basti.%20A%20father%20of%20two%2C%20he%20is%20the%20sole%20breadwinner%20in%20his%20family.%20His%20family%20lives%20in%20Bihar%20and%20he%20stays%20in%20the%20caretaker%20room%20of%20the%20complex.%20When%20his%20wife%20fell%20sick%2C%20he%20brought%20her%20to%20Delhi%20for%20treatment.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20rent%20a%20room%2C%20since%20I%20live%20in%20the%20JS%20complex%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20money%20for%20the%20medical%20bills%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20borrow.%20The%20salary%20for%20October%202023%20was%20credited%20in%20my%20account%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20work%20more%20than%2012%20hours%20a%20day%20and%20receive%20Rs%2011%2C700%20per%20month.%20Niranjan%2C%20the%20safai%20karamchari%2C%20is%20paid%20Rs%207%2C000%20per%20month.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20care%20about%20minimum%20wages%20as%20long%20as%20my%20dues%20are%20cleared%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kanhaiya%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20has%20been%20working%20at%20the%20JSC%20for%2015%20years%20now%2C%20and%20says%20he%20followed%20due%20process%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20get%20his%20dues.%E2%80%9CI%20spoke%20to%20my%20supervisor%2C%20who%20took%20our%20concerns%20to%20the%20contractors.%20When%20nothing%20happened%2C%20we%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20%5Bmember%20of%20legislative%20assembly%5D%20Pramila%20Tokas%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EKanhaiya%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20supervisor%20Jitender%20Kumar%20says%20he%20is%20in%20the%20same%20boat%20as%20his%20workers.%20While%20he%20gets%20minimum%20wage%20payments%2C%20he%20too%20has%20not%20received%20his%20salary%20since%20October.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20not%20cleared%20some%20of%20my%20payments%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20incurred%20out-of-pocket%20expenses%20of%20around%20Rs%2050%2C000%20for%20which%20I%20attached%20the%20bills%20and%20sent%20it%20to%20the%20contractors.%E2%80%9D%20He%20is%20yet%20to%20receive%20reimbursements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18175525%2F1190626-jan-suvidha-complex-at-rk-puram-1100.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221100%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18175525%2F1190626-jan-suvidha-complex-at-rk-puram-1100.jpg%201100w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18175525%2F1190626-jan-suvidha-complex-at-rk-puram-1100-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18175525%2F1190626-jan-suvidha-complex-at-rk-puram-1100-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697731%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22825%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Jan%20Suvidha%20Complex%20at%20RK%20Puram%E2%80%99s%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20Basti.%20The%20caretaker%2C%20safai%20karamchari%20and%20the%20supervisor%20have%20not%20received%20their%20wages%20since%20October%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Divya%20Tiwari%2FIndiaSpend%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EJSC%20workers%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20regulatory%20violations%20by%20contractors%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20consistency%20in%20the%20pay%20received%20by%20the%20workers%20of%20the%20complexes%20across%20Delhi.%20The%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdelhiplanning.delhi.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FPlanning%2Fgeneric_multiple_files%2Fevaluation_study_of_functioning_of_jan_suvidha_complexes_of_dusib_in_delhi.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eregulations%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0state%20that%20the%20salaries%20of%20the%20caretaker%20and%20the%20staff%20should%20be%20paid%20in%20a%20timely%20manner%20through%20bank%20transfer%20directly%20into%20their%20individual%20accounts%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Minimum%20Wages%20Act.%20The%20amount%20transferred%20is%20determined%20based%20on%20the%20number%20of%20toilets%20and%20the%20frequency%20of%20usage.%20However%2C%20workers%20have%20alleged%20that%20contractors%20have%20been%20flouting%20the%20regulations%20and%20that%20their%20rights%20are%20being%20violated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERaj%20Kumar%20has%20been%20working%20at%20the%20JSC%20in%20Inder%20Camp%20as%20a%20caretaker%20for%20the%20last%20one%20year.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20not%20received%20my%20wages%20for%20the%20months%20of%20December%20and%20January%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Furthermore%2C%20he%20stated%20that%20he%20was%20being%20paid%20by%20his%20contractor%20in%20cash.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20the%20minimum%20wages%20are%20for%20us.%20I%20have%20been%20receiving%20Rs%209%2C000%20as%20remuneration%2C%20in%20cash.%20I%20pay%20the%20safai%20karamachari%20Rs%203%2C000%20out%20of%20the%20money%20I%20receive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENanke%20Singh%2C%2038%2C%20who%20has%20been%20working%20as%20a%20caretaker%20at%20a%20Kalkaji%20JSC%2C%20has%20a%20similar%20story.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20five%20members%20in%20my%20family.%20I%20make%20Rs%2012%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20of%20which%20I%20pay%20a%20portion%20to%20the%20safai%20karamchari%2C%20who%20has%20not%20received%20his%20wages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20supervisor%2C%20Avey%20Singh%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20contractors%20on%20several%20occasions%20but%20was%20told%20that%20the%20bills%20are%20not%20being%20cleared%20from%20the%20department.%20He%20was%20also%20threatened%20with%20the%20loss%20of%20his%20job%20if%20he%20continued%20calling%20them%20for%20these%20issues.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20not%20been%20working%20for%20the%20last%2020%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20called%20the%20contractors%20to%20inform%20them%20that%20the%20workers%20are%20demanding%20that%20their%20dues%20be%20cleared.%20I%20was%20told%20to%20keep%20quiet%20and%20continue%20working%20or%20quit%20altogether.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAcross%20JSCs%2C%20staffers%20that%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0spoke%20to%20allege%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcentre-provisions-job-contracts-protect-outsourced-staff-8565591%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enon-compliance%20of%20regulations%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0including%20timely%20payment%20as%20per%20the%20Minimum%20Wages%20Act%2C%20lack%20of%20social%20security%20as%20they%20have%20not%20been%20provided%20with%20provident%20fund%20accounts%20and%20ESIC%20cards.%20Further%2C%20the%20staff%20stated%20that%20cleaning%20supplies%20have%20not%20been%20provided%20for%20over%20two%20months%2C%20which%20has%20led%20them%20to%20spend%20out%20of%20pocket%20and%20in%20some%20places%2C%20the%20toilets%20remain%20as%20clean%20as%20they%20can%20be%20without%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20September%202022%2C%20DUSIB%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdusib-launches-community-based-monitoring-of-toilets-night-shelters-101663015163935.html%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elaunched%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0an%20integrated%20control%20room%20for%20monitoring%20its%20night%20shelters%20and%20toilet%20complexes%20following%20complaints%20regarding%20their%20poor%20maintenance.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20facilities%20are%20unclean%2C%20the%20residents%20can%20call%20and%20complain.%20The%20officers%20will%20demand%20explanations%20from%20the%20staff%20at%20the%20JSC.%20More%20often%20than%20not%2C%20it%20is%20the%20contractor%20who%20fails%20to%20provide%20us%20with%20cleaning%20supplies%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Govind%20Singh%2C%2038%2C%20the%20caretaker%20at%20the%2024-hour%2C%2054-seater%20JSC%20in%20Kalkaji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20my%20job%20to%20keep%20the%20premises%20and%20the%20toilets%20clean.%20But%2C%20for%20the%20last%202-3%20months%2C%20I%20have%20not%20received%20any%20cleaning%20supplies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20clean%20a%20public%20toilet%20without%20supplies%2C%20and%20that%20he%20still%20tries%20to%20keep%20them%20clean%20to%20the%20best%20of%20his%20abilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18175642%2F1190628-across-jscs-1100.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221100%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18175642%2F1190628-across-jscs-1100.jpg%201100w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18175642%2F1190628-across-jscs-1100-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18175642%2F1190628-across-jscs-1100-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697732%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22825%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAcross%20JSCs%2C%20staffers%20that%20IndiaSpend%20spoke%20to%20stated%20that%20cleaning%20supplies%20have%20not%20been%20provided%20for%20over%20two%20months%2C%20which%20has%20led%20them%20to%20spend%20out%20of%20pocket%20and%20in%20some%20places%2C%20the%20toilets%20remain%20as%20clean%20as%20they%20can%20be%20without%20supplies.%20Photo%3A%20Divya%20Tiwari%2FIndiaSpend%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EPassing%20the%20buck%3A%20Contractors%20to%20DUSIB%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Manoj%20Jan%20Kalyan%20Samiti%20is%20an%20NGO%20that%20has%20the%20contract%20for%2015%20JSCs%20in%20South%20Delhi%20from%202022.%20When%20asked%20about%20the%20delay%20in%20payment%20of%20wages%20to%20the%20workers%2C%20president%20Manoj%20Singh%20passed%20the%20buck%20to%20DUSIB.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20attached%20all%20the%20bills%20for%20the%20salaries%20of%20the%20workers%2C%20but%20the%20department%20has%20not%20cleared%20the%20dues.%20The%20officials%20told%20us%20that%20there%20are%20no%20funds%2C%20so%20there%20has%20been%20a%20delay%20in%20payments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20apply%20for%20tenders%2C%20we%20have%20to%20give%20a%20sense%20of%20our%20financial%20capacity%20to%20operate%20and%20manage%20the%20complex.%20My%20organisation%20is%20above%20and%20beyond%20its%20capacities%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20the%20JSCs%20functional%2C%20but%20if%20the%20bills%20are%20not%20cleared%20for%20months%2C%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20help%20the%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Manoj%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcentre-provisions-job-contracts-protect-outsourced-staff-8565591%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enoted%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20delayed%20payment%20of%20monthly%20wages%20to%20contractual%20workers%20by%20the%20agencies%20and%20low%20deposit%20of%20provident%20fund%20and%20ESIC%20contributions%20of%20the%20workers.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20and%20Employment%20recently%20incorporated%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1917990%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esix%20statutory%20obligations%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20the%20GeM%20(Government%20e%20Marketing)%20portal%20in%20the%20contract%20of%20hiring%20manpower%20through%20outsourcing%20agencies%20in%20Government%20of%20India%20offices%2C%20in%20order%20to%20protect%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20contractual%20workers.%20These%20obligations%20include%20mandatory%20contribution%20of%20provident%20fund%20and%20ESIC%20by%20the%20agencies%20in%20a%20timely%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20an%20identity%20card%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nanke%20Singh%20told%3Cem%3E%C2%A0IndiaSpend%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20one%20that%20I%20had%20expired%20last%20year.%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20told%20my%20EPF%20account%20number%20and%20neither%20have%20they%20provided%20any%20assistance%20for%20the%20ESIC%20card.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20contractors%E2%80%99%20failure%20to%20follow%20regulations%20has%20led%20to%20an%20acute%20absence%20of%20social%20security%20for%20the%20workers%20employed%20at%20JSCs.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20got%20the%20contract%20in%202022%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Manoj%20Singh.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20contributed%20to%20the%20EPF%20accounts%20for%20the%20first%20two%20months.%E2%80%9D%20Most%20of%20the%20workers%20do%20not%20have%20access%20to%20their%20EPF%20account%20numbers%2C%20we%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EP.K.%20Jha%2C%20Principal%20Director%20at%20DUSIB%2C%20blamed%20the%20contractors%20for%20the%20non-payment%20issues.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20department%20reimburses%20the%20contractors%20on%20actual%20basis%20once%20they%20share%20expense%20bills.%20When%20applying%20for%20tenders%20to%20run%20the%20facility%2C%20the%20contractor%20has%20to%20declare%20financial%20capability%20to%20keep%20the%20facility%20running%20if%20the%20department%20takes%20time%20to%20clear%20the%20bills%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jha%20said%20when%20we%20spoke%20to%20him%20on%20February%202.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20NGOs%2Fcontractors%20are%20liable%20to%20pay%20the%20workers%20in%20a%20timely%20manner%20and%20to%20ensure%20no%20exploitation%20takes%20place.%20We%20have%20released%20the%20funds%20till%20the%20month%20of%20October%202023.%20If%20a%20worker%20has%20not%20been%20paid%2C%20the%20contractor%20is%20to%20be%20held%20accountable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EJha%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20contractors%20are%20accountable%20for%20contribution%20to%20the%20EPF%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20workers%20have%20ESIC%20cards.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20contractor%20submits%20the%20bill%20for%20the%20same%20and%20we%20then%20release%20the%20funds%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jha%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20taking%20steps%20to%20look%20into%20this.%20We%20will%20be%20asking%20for%20an%20undertaking%20from%20the%20contractors%20along%20with%20the%20list%20of%20workers%20and%20the%20benefits%20they%20have%20received%20as%20a%20contractual%20worker.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIronically%2C%20in%20June%202018%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Government%20won%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fnews-ians%2Fdelhi-government-bags-4-skoch-order-of-merit-awards-118062200662_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESKOCH%20Order-of-Merit%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20%E2%80%98Jan%20Suvidha%20(Toilet)%20Complex%20Monitoring%E2%80%99.%20In%20its%20%E2%80%98outcome%20budget%E2%80%99%20the%20following%20year%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Government%20boasted%20an%20increment%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fnews-ians%2Fpublic-toilets-use-in-delhi-up-431-sisodia-119022501243_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E431%25%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20use%20of%20public%20toilets%20in%202018-19%20over%202016-17%2C%20with%20over%20293%2C000%20people%20provided%20access%20to%20the%20Jan%20Suvidha%20Complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThis%20story%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fgovernance%2Fdelhis-jan-suvidha-complex-workers-remain-unp