F%20has%20lodged%20a%20case%20under%20the%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20IPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20arresting%20Javed%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20STF%20recovered%20four%20time%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interrogation%2C%20the%20arrested%20accused%20told%20the%20police%20that%20these%20four%20bottle%20bombs%20were%20improvised%20explosive%20devices%20(IEDs).%20The%20bottles%20were%20packed%20with%20gun%20powder-999%2C%20iron%20pellets%2C%20cotton%2C%20POP%20etc.%20Javed%20had%20made%20these%20bottle%20bombs%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20Imrana%2C%20wife%20of%20Azad%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Shamli%20currently%20residing%20in%20Muzaffarnagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20used%20to%20buy%20glucose%20bottles%20from%20doctors%20and%20iron%20pellets%20from%20cycle%20shops%2C%20besides%20arranging%20watches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20(Law%20and%20Order)%20and%20ADG%20STF%20Amitabh%20Yash%20said%20the%20STF%20team%20arrested%20Javed%20around%2011.45%20am%20on%20Friday%20and%20recovered%20four-timer%20bottle%20bombs%20(IEDs)%20from%20his%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20official%20said%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20STF%20had%20been%20receiving%20information%20for%20a%20long%20time%20about%20missing%20or%20reward-declared%20criminals%20being%20active.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20Javed%20at%20the%20Kotwali%20police%20station%20under%20the%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20the%20Explosive%20Substances%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20police%20said%20a%20bomb%20disposal%20squad%20took%20the%20four%20bottle%20bombs%20in%20their%20possession%20and%20defused%20them%20in%20the%20forest%20of%20Nyajupura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterrogation%20revealed%20that%20Imrana%20had%20given%20Javed%20Rs%2010%2C000%20in%20advance%20for%20making%20the%20bottle%20bombs%20and%20had%20told%20him%20that%20she%20would%20pay%20Rs%2040%2C000%20later%20at%20the%20time%20of%20delivery.%20He%20was%20arrested%20on%20Friday%20when%20he%20had%20come%20to%20deliver%20these%20bottle%20bombs%20to%20Imrana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20interrogated%20about%20making%20the%20bottle%20bombs%2C%20Javed%20said%20he%20learned%20to%20make%20gunpowder%20and%20bottle%20bombs%20by%20staying%20at%20the%20place%20of%20his%20uncle%20Arshi%2C%20a%20firecracker%20maker%2C%20and%20he%20had%20obtained%20some%20information%20through%20YouTube%20and%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708261080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F3dcdsfko_up-woman-arrested_625x300_18_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-woman-arrested-for-asking-man-to-prepare-time-bombs-using-bottles-cops-5081688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Special%20Task%20Force%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Police%20has%20arrested%20a%20woman%20who%20had%20allegedly%20asked%20a%20man%20to%20prepare%20time%20bombs%20using%20bottles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-woman-arrested-for-asking-man-to-prepare-time-bombs-using-bottles-cops-5081688%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-woman-arrested-for-asking-man-to-prepare-time-bombs-using-bottles-cops-5081688%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-woman-arrested-for-asking-man-to-prepare-time-bombs-using-bottles-cops-5081688%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Varun%20and%20Natasha%20announce%20their%20pregnancy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708261014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107798386%2C