EOne%20corner%20of%20the%20living%20room%20has%20been%20delegated%20to%20a%20workspace%20with%20a%20standing%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBrent%20created%20a%20rendering%20to%20show%20me%20the%20true%20potential%20of%20my%20living%20room.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lauren%20Edmonds%2FKiva%20Brent%20living%20room%20critique%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce74f7f533b039a88440e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKiva%20swapped%20the%20furniture%20around%20in%20her%20rendering%20of%20my%20living%20room.%20%3Cp%3EKiva%20Brent%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrent's%20rendering%20showed%20how%20I%20could%20maximize%20the%20space%20in%20my%20living%20room%20without%20spending%20much%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20look%20at%20what%20you%20already%20had%20and%20figure%20out%20how%20I%20could%20rearrange%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Brent%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20everything%20was%20really%20on%20the%20periphery%2C%20so%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20feel%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20cozy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20places%20like%20Facebook%20Marketplace%2C%20thrift%20shops%2C%20and%20utilizing%20small%20businesses%20with%20unique%20collections%20are%20great%20ways%20to%20find%20new%20decor.%20Online%20sites%20like%20Amazon%20also%20offer%20decor%20with%20luxury%20aesthetics%20for%20affordable%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20great%20way%20to%20get%20funky%20pieces%20of%20furniture%20or%20pieces%20of%20art%20and%20small%20decorative%20accents%2C%26quot%3B%20Brent%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFirst%2C%20Brent%20suggested%20I%20move%20the%20sectional%20and%20fully%20incorporate%20the%20kitchen%20island%20into%20the%20room.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lauren%20Edmonds%2FKiva%20Brent%20living%20room%20critique%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce7516f533b039a88440f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKiva%20Brent%20suggested%20I%20ditch%20my%20wooden%20dining%20room%20table.%20%3Cp%3EKiva%20Brent%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20rendering%2C%20Brent%20moved%20the%20black%20sectional%20across%20the%20room%20and%20added%20two%20chairs%20to%20the%20kitchen%20island.%20According%20to%20her%2C%20the%20added%20island%20chairs%20are%20as%20much%20about%20community%20as%20they%20are%20aesthetics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20island%20chairs%20are%20great%20because%20two%20people%20can%20sit%20down%20and%20have%20dinner%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20you%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20eliminated%20the%20wooden%20dining%20room%20table%20in%20the%20corner%2C%20which%20she%20said%20was%20%26quot%3Btaking%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20space%26quot%3B%20and%20would%20be%20redundant%20with%20the%20island%20chairs.%20Brent%20added%20that%20she%20moved%20the%20couch%20across%20the%20room%2C%20creating%20a%20%26quot%3Bcozy%26quot%3B%20vibe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENext%2C%20Brent%20used%20the%20artwork%20on%20my%20walls%20to%20choose%20a%20rug%2C%20which%20she%20said%20is%20instrumental%20to%20pulling%20the%20living%20room%20together.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lauren%20Edmonds%2FKiva%20Brent%20living%20room%20critique%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce75e3a610a9069d59874c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20green%20in%20the%20painting%20inspired%20the%20rug%20and%20couch%20cushion's%20color%20palette.%20%3Cp%3EKiva%20Brent%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrent%20said%20she%20chose%20the%20white%20and%20green%20rug%20by%20referring%20to%20the%20paintings%20on%20my%20walls.%20She%20also%20used%20the%20painting's%20purple%20accents%20to%20influence%20the%20couch%20cushions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20art%20tends%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20things%20if%20you%20want%20to%20get%20something%20original%2C%20so%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20the%20art%20you%20already%20had%20as%20inspiration%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrent%20added%20that%20rugs%20help%20make%20a%20room%20feel%20grounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rug%20is%20the%20anchor%20because%20you%20put%20it%20down%20and%20all%20of%20your%20living%20room%20furniture%20at%20least%20touches%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20draws%20your%20eyes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20noted%20that%20my%20living%20room%2C%20in%20its%20current%20state%2C%20feels%20like%20a%20place%20of%20furniture%20rather%20than%20a%20cohesive%20space%20with%20designated%20spots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBrent%20also%20added%20a%20round%20coffee%20table%20to%20the%20rendering%2C%20saying%20it's%20functional%20without%20being%20overbearing.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lauren%20Edmonds%2FKiva%20Brent%20living%20room%20critique%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce75c9a610a9069d598741%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKiva%20Brent%20said%20glass%20tables%20are%20a%20stylish%20and%20affordable%20purchase.%20%3Cp%3EKiva%20Brent%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20conversation%20with%20BI%2C%20Brent%20said%20that%20using%20a%20coffee%20table%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%20glass%20%E2%80%94%20can%20upgrade%20the%20living%20room.%20Choosing%20a%20round%20table%20instead%20of%20a%20square%20or%20rectangle%20option%20also%20adds%20a%20new%20shape%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%2C%20glass%20coffee%20tables%20tend%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20more%20affordable%20ones.%20You%20can%20get%20them%20from%20Amazon%20or%20Target%2C%26quot%3B%20Brent%20said.%20%26quot%3BTwo%2C%20glass%20creates%20the%20illusion%20that%20a%20piece%20of%20furniture%20isn't%20there.%20You%20can%20put%20your%20feet%20up%2C%20play%20games%2C%20whatever%2C%20but%20it%20won't%20look%20big.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20the%20glass%20table%20she%20selected%20is%20tiered%20to%20allow%20extra%20storage%20space%2C%20which%20will%20surely%20come%20in%20handy%20with%20a%20one-bedroom%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFinally%2C%20Brent%20said%20small%20tweaks%20could%20fix%20the%20living%20room's%20tiny%20office%20area.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lauren%20Edmonds%2FKiva%20Brent%20living%20room%20critique%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce7747a610a9069d5987de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKiva%20Brent%20said%20acrylic%20floating%20shelves%C2%A0can%20also%20add%20space.%20%3Cp%3EKiva%20Brent%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Brent%20said%20she%20liked%20the%20standing%20desk%2C%20she%20suggested%20I%20look%20for%20an%20option%20with%20more%20storage%20options.%20She%20said%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ikea.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fp%2Falex-drawer-unit-white-00473546%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIkea's%20ALEX%20drawer%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0could%20also%20help%20maximize%20the%20living%20room's%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20desk%20with%20built-in%20shelving%20is%20always%20going%20to%20be%20useful%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BUnless%20you%20have%20a%20bad%20back%2C%20get%20a%20desk%20chair%20that%20looks%20like%20an%20accent%20chair.%20If%20someone%20comes%20over%20and%20you%20need%20additional%20seating%2C%20someone%20can%20sit%20on%20that%20chair%2C%20which%20feels%20natural.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20including%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D1161edbc746dbd26892546cb1f62fde05d97ae2ea2a9b570aaa137cd4079b1