ontent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20made%20a%20mockery%20of%20England%20in%20the%20third%20Test%20of%20the%20five-match%20series%2C%20smashing%20the%20visitors%20by%20434%20runs%20in%20Rajkot%20on%20Sunday.%20This%20is%20their%20biggest%20win%20in%20terms%20of%20runs%20in%20their%20577%20Test%20history%2C%20and%20also%20the%20first%20time%20that%20they've%20won%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20400%20runs%20or%20more.%20India%20surpassed%20their%20372-run%20victory%20over%20New%20Zealand%20in%202021.%20The%20win%20allowed%20India%20to%20go%202-1%20up%20in%20the%20series%20and%20leapfrog%20Australia%20in%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20points%20table.%20The%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20side%20are%20now%20second%20in%20the%20WTC%20points%20table.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Zealand%20remain%20on%20top%20with%20a%20point%20percentage%20of%2075%25%20after%20four%20Tests%20in%20the%20cycle.%20India%20are%20second%20with%2059.52%25%20while%20Australia%20are%20just%20behind%20with%2055%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20back%20to%20the%20match%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal's%20unbeaten%20double%20century%20and%20five%20wickets%20by%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20helped%20India%20crush%20England%20by%20a%20record%20434%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChasing%20557%20for%20victory%2C%20England%20batting%20fell%20like%20a%20pack%20of%20cards%20to%20lose%20eight%20wickets%20in%20the%20final%20session%20and%20get%20bundled%20out%20for%20122%20on%20day%20four%20in%20Rajkot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJadeja%20got%20Mark%20Wood%20out%20for%2033%20as%20the%20final%20wicket%2C%20and%20he%20kissed%20the%20pitch%20as%20India's%20registered%20their%20biggest%20ever%20win%20in%20terms%20of%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland%20lost%20their%20openers%20including%20first-innings%20centurion%20Ben%20Duckett%2C%20run%20out%20on%20four%20before%20tea%2C%20and%20Jadeja%20rattled%20the%20middle-order%20with%20his%20left-arm%20spin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJonny%20Bairstow%20and%20Joe%20Root%20extended%20their%20poor%20run%20in