adimir%20Putin%20triggered%20a%20full-scale%20war%20by%20ordering%20the%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20defence%20ministry%20said%20its%20troops%20had%20advanced%208.6%20km%20(5.3%20miles)%20in%20that%20part%20of%20the%201%2C000-km%20(620-mile)%20front%20line%2C%20and%20that%20Russian%20troops%20were%20pressing%20forward%20after%20a%20deadly%20urban%20battle%20that%20has%20left%20the%20town%20an%20almost%20completely%20depopulated%20wreck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine%20said%20it%20had%20withdrawn%20its%20soldiers%20to%20save%20troops%20from%20being%20fully%20surrounded%20after%20months%20of%20fierce%20fighting.%20Putin%20hailed%20the%20fall%20of%20Avdiivka%20as%20an%20important%20victory%20and%20congratulated%20Russian%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20failure%20of%20Ukraine%20to%20pierce%20Russian%20lines%20last%20year%2C%20Moscow%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20grind%20down%20Ukrainian%20forces%20just%20as%20Kyiv%20ponders%20a%20major%20new%20mobilisation%20and%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskiy%20appoints%20a%20new%20commander%20to%20run%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20head%20of%20state%20congratulated%20Russian%20soldiers%20on%20this%20success%2C%20an%20important%20victory%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Kremlin%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Russia%20said%20some%20Ukrainian%20forces%20were%20still%20holed%20up%20at%20the%20Soviet-era%20coke%20plant%2C%20once%20one%20of%20Europe's%20biggest%2C%20in%20Avdiivka%2C%20which%20is%20key%20to%20Russia's%20aim%20of%20securing%20full%20control%20of%20the%20industrial%20Donbas%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeasures%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20completely%20clear%20the%20town%20of%20militants%20and%20to%20block%20Ukrainian%20units%20that%20have%20left%20the%20town%20and%20are%20entrenched%20at%20the%20Avdiivka%20Coke%20and%20Chemical%20Plant%2C%26quot%3B%20Russian%20Defence%20Ministry%20spokesman%20Igor%20Konashenkov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20public%20comment%20yet%20by%20Ukrainian%20authorities%20on%20this.%20Russian%20state%20television%20showed%20blue%20and%20yellow%20Ukrainian%20flags%20being%20taken%20down%20in%20Avdiivka%20and%20Russia's%20white%2C%20blue%20and%20red%20tricolour%20flag%20raised%2C%20including%20over%20the%20coke%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20cast%20the%20Ukrainian%20withdrawal%20as%20rushed%20and%20chaotic%2C%20with%20some%20soldiers%20and%20weapons%20left%20behind.%20The%20Ukrainian%20military%20said%20there%20had%20been%20casualties%20but%20that%20the%20situation%20had%20stabilised%20somewhat%20after%20the%20retreat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20sent%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20troops%20into%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022%2C%20triggering%20the%20full-scale%20war%20after%20eight%20years%20of%20conflict%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%20between%20Ukrainian%20forces%20on%20the%20one%20side%20and%20pro-Russian%20Ukrainians%20and%20Russian%20proxies%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvdiivka%2C%20which%20is%20called%20Avdeyevka%20by%20Russians%2C%20has%20endured%20a%20decade%20of%20conflict.%20It%20holds%20particular%20symbolism%20for%20Russia%20as%20it%20was%20briefly%20taken%20in%202014%20by%20Moscow-backed%20separatists%20who%20seized%20a%20swathe%20of%20eastern%20Ukraine%20but%20was%20then%20recaptured%20by%20Ukrainian%20troops%20who%20built%20extensive%20fortifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeapons%20Shortages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EU.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20had%20warned%20that%20Avdiivka%20could%20fall%20to%20Russian%20forces%20because%20of%20ammunition%20shortages%20following%20months%20of%20Republican%20congressional%20opposition%20to%20a%20new%20U.S.%20military%20aid%20package%20for%20Kyiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20White%20House%20statement%20said%20Biden%20called%20Zelenskiy%20on%20Saturday%20to%20underscore%20the%20U.S.%20commitment%20to%20continue%20supporting%20Ukraine%20and%20reiterated%20the%20need%20for%20Congress%20to%20urgently%20pass%20the%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20said%20the%20withdrawal%20had%20been%20forced%20upon%20Ukraine%20%26quot%3Bby%20dwindling%20supplies%20as%20a%20result%20of%20congressional%20inaction%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20had%20forced%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20to%20ration%20ammunition%20and%20resulted%20in%20%26quot%3BRussia's%20first%20notable%20gains%20in%20months%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelenskiy%20urged%20allies%20at%20a%20global%20security%20conference%20in%20Munich%20on%20Saturday%20to%20plug%20an%20%26quot%3Bartificial%26quot%3B%20shortage%20of%20weapons%20and%20said%20stalled%20U.S.%20aid%20was%20imperative.%20He%20praised%20his%20troops%20for%20%26quot%3Bexhausting%26quot%3B%20Russian%20forces%20in%20Avdiivka%2C%20and%20suggested%20the%20withdrawal%20was%20partly%20caused%20by%20a%20lack%20of%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20(the%20military)%20will%20replenish%2C%20they%20will%20wait%20for%20the%20relevant%20weapons%2C%20of%20which%20there%20simply%20weren't%20enough%2C%20simply%20aren't%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BRussia%20has%20long-range%20weapons%2C%20while%20we%20simply%20don't%20have%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoost%20For%20Russia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECapturing%20Avdiivka%20is%20likely%20to%20provide%20a%20morale%20boost%20for%20Russia%20ahead%20of%20Putin's%20bid%20for%20re-election%20next%20month%2C%20which%20he%20is%20almost%20certain%20to%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20seen%20as%20another%20step%20towards%20securing%20Moscow's%20hold%20on%20the%20regional%20centre%20of%20Donetsk%2C%20about%2020%20km%20(12%20miles)%20to%20the%20east%2C%20held%20by%20Russian%20and%20pro-Russian%20forces%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20Russia%20nor%20Ukraine%20have%20given%20details%20of%20their%20losses%20in%20the%20war%20or%20in%20the%20intense%20battle%20for%20Avdiivka.%20Western%20intelligence%20assessments%20say%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20men%20on%20both%20sides%20have%20been%20killed%20or%20wounded%20in%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20congratulated%20the%20Russian%20commander%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20assault%20on%20Avdiivka%2C%20Colonel-General%20Andrei%20Mordvichev.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEternal%20glory%20to%20the%20heroes%20who%20fell%20in%20fulfilling%20the%20tasks%20of%20the%20special%20military%20operation!%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said%20in%20a%20telegram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20Defence%20Minister%20Rustem%20Umerov%20said%20Avdiivka%20showed%20the%20need%20for%20modern%20air%20defence%20systems%20to%20counter%20guided%20bombs%20and%20long-range%20weapons%20to%20destroy%20enemy%20formations.%20He%20said%20artillery%20shells%20were%20also%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColonel-General%20Oleksandr%20Syrskyi%2C%20who%20took%20command%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20military%20in%20a%20major%20shake-up%20last%20week%2C%20said%20Ukrainian%20forces%20had%20moved%20back%20to%20more%20secure%20positions%20outside%20the%20town%20%26quot%3Bto%20avoid%20encirclement%20and%20preserve%20the%20lives%20and%20health%20of%20servicemen%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine's%203rd%20Assault%20Brigade%2C%20which%20officials%20say%20was%20deployed%20to%20Avdiivka%20this%20week%2C%20said%20on%20Telegram%20that%20it%20had%20pulled%20back%20to%20prepared%20positions%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Avdiivka%20and%20evened%20out%20the%20front%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20time%2C%20the%20Russians%20are%20not%20slowing%20down%20their%20assault.%20We%20keep%20holding%20the%20line%20in%20the%20area%20of%20Avdiivka%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20Ukrainian%20forces%20repelled%20a%20Russian%20offensive%20on%20the%20southern%20front%20in%20the%20area%20of%20Zaporizhzhia%2C%20the%20Ukrainian%20military%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20comment%20on%20that%20yet%20from%20the%20Russian%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708258500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F3nqlabo8_ukraine-avdiivka-afp_625x300_05_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-in-full-control-of-ukraines-avdiivka-biggest-win-in-9-months-5081515%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20on%20Sunday%20said%20it%20had%20full%20control%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20town%20of%20Avdiivka%20after%20Ukraine%20withdrew%20though%20Moscow%20said%20that%20some%20Ukrainian%20troops%20were%20still%20holed%20up%20in%20a%20vast%20Soviet-era%20coke%20plant%20after%20one%20of%20the%20most%20intense%20battles%20of%20the%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-in-full-control-of-ukraines-avdiivka-biggest-win-in-9-months-5081515%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-in-full-control-of-ukraines-avdiivka-biggest-win-in-9-months-5081515%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-in-full-control-of-ukraines-avdiivka-biggest-win-in-9-months-5081515%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WHO%20says%20Gaza%20hospital%20raided%20by%20IDF%20not%20functional%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708258490000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F11B95%2Fproduction%2F_132679527_b96a1ca344bf66fc110fbab026d25b7d7484de9b121_679_4392_24701000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68330579%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli%20forces%20say%20intelligence%20suggested%20hostages%20were%20being%20held%20at%20the%20Nasser%20site%20by%20Hamas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22en