0of%20owning%20the%20Vision%20Pro%2C%20I'm%20still%20impressed%20by%20the%20movie-watching%20experience%20that%20blew%20me%20away%20during%20my%20Apple%20store%20demo%20%E2%80%94%20though%20it's%20not%20perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusing-apple-vision-pro-for-the-day-productivity-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVision%20Pro%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20places%20you%20can%20watch%20a%20movie%20are%20endless%20as%20long%20as%20you%20have%20WiFi.%20Naturally%2C%20I%20was%20eager%20to%20find%20the%20coziest%20way%20to%20have%20a%20movie%20night%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20place%20to%20watch%20a%20movie%20or%20show%20is%20from%20my%20bed%2C%20so%20my%20instincts%20led%20me%20there%20for%20my%20first%20experience.%20It%20was%20almost%20as%20cozy%20as%20I'd%20imagined%2C%20but%20it%20was%20isolating%20to%20watch%20something%20by%20myself%20instead%20of%20with%20my%20boyfriend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20bed%2C%20I%20found%20it's%20easier%20to%20find%20a%20comfortable%20position%20and%20stay%20there%20throughout%20a%20movie%20rather%20than%20the%20fidgeting%20and%20turning%20over%20I%20usually%20do%20when%20watching%20TV.%20Doing%20so%20while%20wearing%20the%20Vision%20Pro%20would%20require%20me%20to%20reposition%20my%20window%20to%20keep%20it%20in%20my%20line%20of%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20some%20time%2C%20the%20coziness%20wore%20off%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-vision-pro-headset-lightweight-reviewers-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweight%20of%20the%20Vision%20Pro%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20to%20make%20laying%20down%20feel%20awkward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2022.9-ounce%20headset%20isn't%20exactly%20comfortable%20after%20a%20few%20hours%20of%20wearing%20it%2C%20but%20supporting%20my%20neck%20with%20a%20pillow%20alleviated%20some%20of%20that%20discomfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20weight%20also%20made%20watching%20in%20my%20living%20room%20trickier%20than%20in%20the%20bedroom.%20Sitting%20up%20in%20the%20Vision%20Pro%20for%20over%2090%20minutes%20made%20watching%20a%20Marvel%20movie%20on%20Disney%2B%20nearly%20impossible.%20The%20position%20is%20more%20suitable%20for%2030-minute%20episodes%20than%20three-hour%20films.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20laying%20back%20on%20my%20couch%20to%20get%20some%20extra%20neck%20support%2C%20but%20that%20didn't%20solve%20the%20fact%20there%20was%20a%20bright%20display%20inches%20from%20my%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20I%20felt%20fine%20after%20watching%20a%20movie%20or%20a%20couple%20of%2045-minute%20show%20episodes%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20do%20a%20movie%20marathon%20or%20binge%20hourlong%20%26quot%3BLove%20Island%26quot%3B%20episodes%20as%20I'd%20normally%20do%20on%20my%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20most%20streaming%20services%20still%20don't%20have%20an%20app%20for%20the%20Vision%20Pro.%20There%20are%20some%20sites%20that%20you%20can%20log%20into%20on%20Safari%2C%20but%20others%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Peacock%20%E2%80%94%20prompt%20you%20to%20watch%20%26quot%3Bon%20your%20phone%20on%20a%20tablet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Peacock%20on%20the%20Vision%20Pro%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce90346fcb546d2d50778e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeacock%20requires%20you%20to%20download%20an%20app%20to%20watch%20shows.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-cook-behind-the-scenes-video-apple-vision-pro-manufacturing-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInside%20the%20Vision%20Pro%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20can%20bring%20my%20windows%20close%20up%20to%20my%20eyes%20or%20watch%20from%20across%20the%20room%20if%20I%20want.%20For%20my%20movies%2C%20I%20went%20for%20a%20distance%20somewhere%20in%20the%20middle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%2055-inch%204K%20smart%20TV%2C%20and%20that%20size%20is%20usually%20perfect%20for%20me%20to%20watch.%20But%20my%20motto%20while%20watching%20through%20the%20Vision%20Pro%20was%20%26quot%3BGo%20big%20or%20go%20home.%26quot%3B%20The%20Vision%20Pro%20can%20project%20a%20jumbotron-like%20big%20screen%20onto%20my%20ceiling%2C%20so%20of%20course%20I%20had%20to%20do%20just%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20a%20stickler%20for%20super%20high-definition%20displays%2C%20but%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20Vision%20Pro's%20micro-OLED%20screen%20didn't%20look%20much%20different%20from%20my%204K%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20easy%20to%20have%20a%20snack%20while%20watching%20my%20shows%2C%20but%20the%20headset%20felt%20like%20ski%20goggles%20that%20forced%20me%20to%20physically%20turn%20my%20head%20to%20see%20my%20bowl%20of%20popcorn%20instead%20of%20just%20glancing%20at%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20drinking%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20when%20my%20glass%20audibly%20clinked%20the%20front%20of%20my%20Vision%20Pro%20as%20I%20took%20a%20sip.%20The%20device%20didn't%20stop%20me%20from%20having%20a%20drink%2C%20but%20its%20presence%20was%20certainly%20felt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Disney%2B%20on%20the%20Apple%20Vision%20Pro%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce8e3d6fcb546d2d5076b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20could%20watch%20shows%20in%20a%20completely%20dark%20environment%20despite%20the%20real%20world%20being%20bright.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20immersion%20capabilities%20of%20the%20Vision%20Pro%2C%20I%20could%20watch%20a%20film%20in%20a%20dark%20theater%20or%20a%20forest%20at%20night%20even%20if%20it%20was%20bright%20noon%20in%20my%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20full%20advantage%20of%20those%20features%20when%20I%20wanted%20to%20zone%20out%20from%20the%20world%20around%20me%2C%20and%20it%20was%20convenient%20to%20step%20out%20of%20those%20environments%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20people%20around%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20know%20I%20needed%20to%20be%20able%20to%20watch%20a%20movie%20from%20the%20side%20of%20a%20lake%20with%20the%20starry%20sky%20above%20me%20before%20getting%20the%20Vision%20Pro%2C%20but%20it's%20become%20my%20favorite%20way%20to%20have%20some%20alone%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwatching-movies-on-apple-vision-pro-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708257841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce91abf533b039a88457fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwatching-movies-on-apple-vision-pro-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Apple%20Vision%20Pro%20transformed%20how%20I%20watch%20movies%20in%20my%20first%20week%20of%20using%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwatching-movies-on-apple-vision-pro-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biggest%20In%20577%20Tests%3A%20India%20Achieve%20Historic%20High%20By%20Drubbing%20England%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal's%20sensational%20double%20hundred%20found%20harmonious%20co-existence%20with%20the%20stunning%20craftiness%20of%20five-wicket%20man%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20as%20ruthless%20India%20demolished%20wasteful%20England%20by%20a%20record%20434%20runs%20on%20the%20fourth%20day%20of%20the%20third%20Test%20in%20Rajkot%20on%20Sunday.%20England%20resisted%20their%20desire%20to%20play%20'Bazball'%20but%20the%20Indian%20bowlers%20led%20by%20Jadeja%20(5%2F41)%20were%20an%20irresistible%20force%2C%20as%20they%20hustled%20out%20the%20tourists%20for%20122%20in%20their%20second%20innings%20while%20chasing%20an%20improbable%20557-run%20target.%20India%2C%20now%2C%20lead%20the%20five-match%20series%202-1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20India%20has%20won%20by%20over%20400%20runs%20in%20Tests.%20This%20is%20the%20their%20biggest%20win%20in%20terms%20of%20runs%20in%20their%20577%20Test%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20also%20India's%20biggest%20win%20in%20Test%20cricket%20in%20terms%20of%20runs%2C%20bettering%20the%20previous%20372-run%20win%20over%20New%20Zealand%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal's%20unbeaten%20214%20off%20236%20balls%2C%20in%20which%20he%20equalled%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20sixes%20(12)%20in%20a%20Test%20innings%2C%20was%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20India's%20second%20innings%20total%20of%20430%20for%20four%20declared%2C%20which%20gave%20them%20a%20massive%20lead%20of%20556%20runs%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20a%20perfect%20platform%20for%20Jadeja%20to%20weave%20his%20magic%20as%20England's%20claims%20of%20fancying%20themselves%20in%20big%20chases%20through%20an%20aggressive%20approach%20came%20to%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20plan%20of%20attacking%20the%20wickets%20took%20the%20wind%20away%20from%20the%20sails%20of%20England%2C%20whose%20top%20order%20crumbled%20without%20any%20significant%20contribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Jadeja%20finding%20ample%20support%20from%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20(2%2F19)%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20(1%2F18)%20and%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20(1%2F19)%2C%20who%20rejoined%20the%20match%20on%20this%20day%20after%20attending%20a%20medical%20emergency%20at%20home%2C%20England%20found%20no%20way%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBen%20Duckett%20(4)%20ran%20himself%20out%2C%20Zak%20Crawley%20(11)%20was%20trapped%20leg-before%20by%20Bumrah%20and%20Jadeja%20struck%20twice%20in%20quick%20succession%20to%20see%20the%20back%20of%20Ollie%20Pope%20(3)%20and%20extended%20Jonny%20Bairstow's%20(4)%20misery%20on%20this%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStruggling%20desperately%20for%20runs%20on%20this%20tour%2C%20Bairstow%20was%20trapped%20leg-before%20while%20trying%20to%20sweep%20Jadeja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland's%20hero%20of%20the%20win%20in%20the%20first%20Test%2C%20Pope%20cut%20one%20straight%20to%20Rohit%20Sharma%20at%20first%20slip%20as%20Jadeja%20shook%20their%20top-order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20brief%20period%20of%20resistance%2C%20Joe%20Root%20(7)%20missed%20a%20sweep%20with%20the%20umpire%20declaring%20him%20out%20leg-before%20off%20Jadeja%2C%20and%20the%20replays%20confirmed%20that%20the%20ball%20would%20have%20flicked%20the%20top%20of%20off-stump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Ben%20Stokes%20(15)%20had%20a%20similar%20fate%2C%20missing%20a%20sweep%20off%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20as%20England%20slumped%20to%2050%20for%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20took%20the%20field%20in%20the%20post%20tea%20session%20and%20contributed%20his%20bit%20with%20the%20scalp%20of%20Tom%20Hartley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20while%2C%20it%20seemed%20England%20would%20fold%20for%20one%20of%20their%20lowest-ever%20totals%20against%20India%2C%20but%20a%20late%20burst%20from%20Mark%20Wood%20(33%2C%2015%20balls%2C%206x4s%2C%201x6s)%20took%20them%20to%20122%20from%2082%20for%20eight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20Jadeja%20and%20his%20horsemen%20of%20apocalypse%20ran%20through%20England%2C%20Jaiswal%20and%20debutant%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20showcased%20their%20brilliance%20in%20no%20little%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubman%20Gill%20too%20displayed%20his%20class%20with%20a%2091%20after%20India%20resumed%20the%20fourth%20day%20from%20196%20for%20two.%20The%20knock%20combined%20with%20his%20hundred%20in%20the%20previous%20Test%20might%20have%20brought%20him%20considerable%20time%20and%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20none%20shone%20as%20bright%20as%20Jaiswal.%20Having%20notched%20up%20his%20overall%20third%20century%20and%20second%20of%20the%20series%2C%20Jaiswal%20continued%20with%20his%20red-hot%20form%20to%20become%20the%20first%20player%20to%20hit%2020%20sixes%20in%20a%20series%20with%20two%20more%20matches%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal's%20six-hitting%20spree%20so%20far%20has%20resulted%20in%20India%20bettering%20their%20own%20record%20of%20most%20sixes%20(48)%20in%20a%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20left-handed%20opener%20also%20entered%20record%20books%20to%20join%20Pakistan%20legend%20Wasim%20Akram%20for%20most%20sixes%20(12)%20for%20any%20batter%20in%20a%20Test%20innings%2C%20while%20resetting%20the%20same%20statistical%20high%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%20joined%20Vinod%20Kambli%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20as%20only%20the%20third%20Indian%20ever%20to%20have%20scored%20two%20consecutive%20double%20centuries%20in%20as%20many%20games%2C%20while%20becoming%20the%20seventh%20Indian%20ever%20to%20have%20scored%20in%20excess%20of%20200%20in%20the%20second%20essay%20of%20a%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20the%2022-year-old%20Jaiswal%20also%20breached%20the%20500-run%20mark%20in%20only%20the%20third%20Test%20of%20this%20series%2C%20reaching%20545%20runs%20in%20six%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%20109%20with%20two%20tons%20and%20a%20fifty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Jaiswal%20is%20now%20the%20leading%20run-scorer%20in%20the%20current%20cycle%20of%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%2C%20going%20past%20Australia's%20Usman%20Khawaja%20with%20861%20runs%20in%20seven%20Tests%20at%2071.75%2C%20studded%20with%20three%20centuries%20and%20two%20fifties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Sarfaraz%20too%20gave%20a%20shining%20portent%20with%20two%20fifties%20in%20his%20maiden%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20unbeaten%2068%20was%20laced%20with%20class%20and%20that%20customary%20disdain%20for%20spinners%2C%20something%20England%20will%20be%20worrying%20a%20lot%20ahead%20of%20the%20fourth%20Test%20beginning%20in%20Ranchi%20from%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708257840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F85abp4vo_team-india-afp_625x300_18_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbiggest-in-577-tests-india-achieve-historic-high-by-drubbing-england-cricket-comprehensively-5081283%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravindra%20Jadeja%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20India%2C%20taking%20five%20wickets%20for%2041%20runs%20in%2012.4%20overs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Editors%20Guild%20Expresses%20'Grave%20Concerns'%20on%20Data%20Protection%20Act%20in%20Representation%20to%20IT%20Ministry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F23203159%2FScreen-Shot-2020-10-23-at-8.31.43-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20has%20submitted%20a%20representation%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20expressing%20%E2%80%9Cgrave%20concerns%20on%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20recently%20enacted%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%202023%20(DPDPA)%20on%20journalistic%20activities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20representation%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESh.%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20Government%20of%20India%3Cbr%3E%5CnElectronics%20Niketan%2C%206%2C%20CGO%20Complex%3Cbr%3E%5CnPragati%20Vihar%2C%20Lodhi%20Road%20New%20Delhi%20110003%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubject%3A%20Grave%20concerns%20over%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%202023%20on%20the%20continued%20existence%20of%20journalistic%20activities%20in%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERespected%20Sir%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20writing%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20(EGI)%2C%20to%20bring%20to%20your%20attention%20certain%20grave%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20recently%20enacted%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%202023%20(DPDPA)%20on%20journalistic%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20express%20below%20our%20concerns%20with%20respect%20to%20adverse%20implications%20of%20the%20Data%20Act%2C%20on%20journalistic%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20The%20enactment%20of%20the%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%202023%20inadvertently%20endangers%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.1%20%C2%A0The%20DPDPA%2C%20while%20a%20laudable%20initiative%20towards%20protecting%20the%20personal%20data%20of%20individuals%2C%20if%20applied%20indiscriminately%20to%20the%20processing%20of%20personal%20data%20in%20a%20journalistic%20context%2C%20will%20bring%20journalism%20in%20the%20country%20to%20a%20standstill.%20This%20will%20have%20a%20long-standing%20impact%20on%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%2C%20and%20the%20dissemination%20of%20information%20not%20just%20in%20reporting%20in%20print%2C%20TV%2C%20and%20the%20internet%2C%20but%20also%20the%20mere%20issuance%20of%20press%20releases%20by%20all%20parties%20including%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.2%20%C2%A0The%20continued%20existence%20of%20the%20press%20%E2%80%93%20the%20fourth%20pillar%20of%20democracy%20%E2%80%93%20enables%20the%20dissemination%20of%20news%2C%20thoughts%2C%20and%20opinions%20and%20ensures%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20democracy.%20It%20informs%20public%20opinion%2C%20promotes%20civic%20engagement%2C%20and%20empowers%20individuals%20to%20make%20informed%20decisions%20including%20political%20choices.%20Its%20centrality%20is%20recognised%20by%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20(Constitution)%2C%20which%20only%20permits%20reasonable%20restrictions%20on%20the%20exercise%20of%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEditors%20Guild%20of%20India%20%5B%E2%80%9CEGI%E2%80%9D%5D%20is%20an%20organisation%20established%20in%201978%20to%20protect%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%20and%20to%20raise%20the%20standards%20of%20editorial%20leadership%20of%20newspapers%C2%A0and%20magazines.%20Since%20our%20establishment%2C%20we%20have%20consistently%20defended%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%C2%A0expression%20of%20publishers%20and%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20the%20citizens%20of%20India.%20We%20have%20continued%20our%C2%A0efforts%20even%20after%20newspapers%20started%20publishing%20over%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.3%20While%20the%20DPDPA%20does%20not%20address%20journalists%20or%20their%20activities%2C%20it%20regulates%20the%20underlying%20processing%20(e.g.%2C%20collection%2C%20use%2C%20storage)%20of%20personal%20data%20that%20is%20inevitable%20in%20almost%20every%20instance%20of%20journalism.%20The%20DPDPA%20requires%20individuals%20or%20entities%20that%20determine%20the%20purpose%20and%20means%20of%20processing%20such%20personal%20data%20outside%20a%20personal%20or%20domestic%20context%2C%20i.e.%2C%20data%20fiduciaries%2C%20to%20meet%20various%20requirements%20(e.g.%2C%20provision%20of%20notice%20and%20obtaining%20consent%2C%20erasure%2C%20etc.).%20These%20requirements%20are%20undeniably%20onerous%20in%20the%20context%20of%20processing%20for%20journalistic%20purposes.%20Given%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20profession%20and%20the%20implications%20for%20fundamental%20rights%20involved%20processing%20personal%20data%20for%20journalistic%20purposes%20is%20an%20ideal%20case%20and%20must%20be%20an%20exemption%20from%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20DPDPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Specific%20challenges%20arising%20from%20the%20application%20of%20DPDPA%20to%20journalistic%20activities%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.1%20Consent%20(necessary%20under%20the%20DPDPA)%20may%20be%20withheld%20and%20may%20lead%20to%20selective%20dissemination%20of%20information%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.1.1.%20%C2%A0The%20DPDPA%20requires%20all%20processing%20of%20personal%20data%20to%20proceed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20either%20consent%20or%20certain%20legitimate%20uses%20(e.g.%2C%20for%20employment%20purposes%20or%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20medical%20emergency)%20under%20Section%207%20of%20the%20DPDPA%2C%20which%20is%20narrow%20and%20specific%20in%20nature.%20Processing%20personal%20data%20for%20journalistic%20activities%20will%20invariably%20fall%20outside%20these%20narrow%20buckets.%20While%20certain%20journalistic%20activities%20involving%20interviews%2C%20collecting%20responses%20to%20questionnaires%2C%20etc.%2C%20may%20be%20covered%20under%20Section%207(a)%20of%20the%20DPDPA%2C%20which%20recognises%20voluntary%20provision%20of%20personal%20data%20by%20the%20data%20principal%2C%20most%20other%20forms%20of%20journalism%2C%20such%20as%20investigative%20journalism%2C%20general%20news%20reporting%2C%20opinion%20pieces%2C%20analyses%2C%20etc.%2C%20are%20still%20largely%20dependent%20on%20private%20research%20and%20investigative%20study%20by%20journalists%2C%20which%20is%20remarkably%20absent%20in%20the%20current%20list%20of%20legitimate%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.1.2.%20%C2%A0Given%20this%2C%20journalists%20will%20invariably%20have%20to%20rely%20upon%20consent%20to%20process%20any%20personal%20data%20in%20the%20course%20of%20their%20journalistic%20activities.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20onerous%20nature%20of%20this%20requirement%20was%20critiqued%20in%20the%20Report%20published%20by%20the%20Committee%20of%20Experts%20under%20the%20Chairmanship%20of%20Justice%20B.N.%20Srikrishna%20(Srikrishna%20Committee)%20titled%20%E2%80%98A%20Free%20and%20Fair%20Digital%20Economy%3A%20Protecting%20Privacy%2C%20Empowering%20Indians%E2%80%99%20(Srikrishna%20Committee%20Report)%2F%20The%20Committee%2C%20which%20prepared%20the%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%2C%202018%2C%20noted%20that%20mandating%20consent%20for%20processing%20such%20personal%20data%20would%20be%20unfavourable%2C%20as%20the%20data%20principal%20could%20simply%20refuse%20to%20consent%20forestalling%20all%20such%20publishing.%20The%20fundamental%20role%20of%20the%20press%20and%20its%20ability%20to%20ensure%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20would%20thus%20be%20severely%20undermined%20by%20the%20data%20principal%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20simply%20refuse%20consent%20to%20the%20processing%20of%20their%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.2%20The%20infeasibility%20and%20impracticality%20of%20requiring%20journalists%20to%20adhere%20to%20other%20obligations%20under%20the%20DPDPA%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.2.1.%20As%20journalists%20and%20media%20organisations%20will%20likely%20be%20considered%20data%20fiduciaries%20under%20the%20DPDPA%2C%20they%20will%20be%20required%20to%20adhere%20to%20its%20provisions%2C%20including%20obligations%20to%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(a)%20Provide%20notice%20where%20processing%20is%20based%20on%20consent%20and%20obtain%20consent%3A%20Journalists%20and%20media%20organisations%20would%20consequently%20have%20to%20notify%20data%20principals%20of%20the%20proposed%20processing%20prior%20to%20or%20at%20the%20time%20of%20requesting%20consent.%20As%20indicated%20above%2C%20purpose%20specification%20(a%20necessary%20component%20of%20such%20a%20notice)%2C%20particularly%20at%20a%20nascent%20stage%20in%20a%20journalistic%20context%20is%20infeasible%2C%20and%20may%20(in%20the%20case%20of%20investigative%20journalism)%20even%20defeat%20the%20purpose%20of%20undertaking%20such%20processing.%20Obtaining%20consent%20(including%20obtaining%20verifiable%20consent%20from%20the%20parent%20or%20lawful%20guardian%20of%20a%20child%20or%20a%20person%20with%20a%20disability)%20presents%20similar%20problems.%20For%20instance%2C%20when%20a%20journalist%20is%20investigating%20the%20parties%20involved%20in%20a%20fraudulent%20%2F%20Ponzi%20scheme%2C%20reporting%20on%20road%20accidents%20in%20a%20particular%20city%2C%20or%20publishing%20information%20about%20the%20achievement%20of%20an%20individual%20who%20is%20a%20resident%20of%20another%20city%2C%20the%20requirement%20to%20provide%20notice%20and%20obtain%20consent%20would%20not%20only%20be%20impractical%20or%20infeasible%20but%20will%20likely%20defeat%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20journalistic%20endeavour%2C%20by%20causing%20inordinate%20delay%20or%20impeding%20the%20journalist%20from%20publishing%20the%20news%20report%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20(b)%20%C2%A0Requirement%20to%20process%20information%20only%20for%20specified%20purposes%3A%20The%20standards%20of%20specificity%20required%20for%20processing%20personal%20data%20should%20not%20apply%20to%20journalistic%20activities%2C%20which%20are%20often%20exploratory%20in%20nature.%20Often%2C%20uncovers%20new%20leads%20or%20directions%20through%20such%20research%20and%20processing%20of%20personal%20information.%20It%20would%20be%20impractical%20for%20a%20journalist%20to%20specify%20in%20exact%20terms%20the%20purposes%20for%20which%20the%20personal%20data%20is%20being%20collected%20at%20such%20a%20nascent%20stage%2C%20and%20unreasonably%20restrain%20journalists%20from%20fulfilling%20their%20professional%20activities.%20While%20the%20DPDPA%20contemplates%20an%20exemption%20for%20processing%20personal%20data%20for%20research%20purposes%2C%20this%20exemption%20is%20(i)%20open-ended%20and%20subject%20to%20standards%20that%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20prescribed%3B%20(ii)%20only%20available%20where%20the%20personal%20data%20is%20not%20used%20to%20%E2%80%98take%20a%20decision%20specific%20to%20the%20Data%20Principal%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20phrase%20that%20is%20not%20defined%20in%20the%20DPDPA%20and%20will%20likely%20encompass%20the%20decision%20to%20publish%20an%20article%20or%20news%20report%20about%20or%20involving%20a%20data%20principal.%20Accordingly%2C%20this%20exemption%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20available%20for%20processing%20personal%20data%20for%20journalistic%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20(c)%20%C2%A0Enable%20withdrawal%20of%20consent%20to%20continued%20processing%20and%20erasure%20upon%20request%3A%20The%20DPDPA%20mandates%20deletion%20of%20personal%20data%20where%20a%20data%20principal%20withdraws%20consent%20unless%20the%20retention%20is%20necessary%20for%20compliance%20with%20any%20other%20law.1%20Imposing%20this%20obligation%20on%20journalists%20would%20have%20wide-reaching%20implications%2C%20requiring%20them%20to%20even%20delete%20notes%20containing%20personal%20data.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20requirement%20to%20retain%20this%20personal%20data%2C%20journalists%20will%20be%20left%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20cease%20processing%20(which%20includes%20storage)%20and%20ultimately%20erase%20such%20personal%20data%2C%20making%20post-facto%20validation%20of%20a%20news%20report%20or%20article%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20(d)%20%C2%A0Power%20of%20Central%20Government%20to%20call%20for%20any%20information%3A%20Section%2036%20of%20the%20DPDPA%20empowers%20the%20Central%20Government%20to%20require%20the%20Board%20and%20any%20data%20fiduciary%20or%20intermediary%20to%20furnish%20any%20information%20that%20it%20may%20seek.%20Preserving%20the%20confidentiality%20of%20sources%20is%20integral%20to%20investigative%20journalism%2C%20as%20journalists%20often%20rely%20on%20such%20informants%20for%20sensitive%20information.%20Journalists%20acting%20as%20data%20fiduciaries%20are%20not%20exempted%20from%20this%20provision.%20This%20will%20likely%20deter%20potential%20informants%20from%20coming%20forward%20with%20necessary%20information%20for%20fear%20of%20their%20anonymity%20being%20compromised%2C%20thereby%20having%20a%20debilitating%20impact%20on%20journalism%20at%20large.%20%5BNote%3A%20We%20can%20drop%20this%20also%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.2.2.%20These%20requirements%20under%20the%20DPDPA%20when%20applied%20to%20journalists%20are%20unduly%20onerous%2C%20impractical%2C%20and%20infeasible%20for%20journalists%2C%20in%20light%20of%20the%20distinct%20practices%20involved%20in%20journalism%20when%20compared%20to%20other%20professions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Exemptions%20under%20previous%20iterations%20of%20the%20data%20protection%20law%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.1%20%C2%A0Save%20for%20the%20draft%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%2C%202022%2C%20all%20prior%20iterations%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20data%20protection%20law%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%2C%202018%2C%20the%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%2C%202019%2C%20and%20the%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%2C%202021%20%E2%80%93%20specifically%20exempted%20processing%20for%20journalistic%20purposes%20from%20complying%20with%20most%20of%20the%20corresponding%20provisions%20in%20those%20drafts%2C%20including%20the%20obligation%20to%20provide%20notice%20and%20obtain%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.2%20%C2%A0The%20Srikrishna%20Committee%20Report%20that%20accompanied%20the%202018%20Bill%2C2%20too%2C%20recognised%20that%20exempting%20journalistic%20activity%20from%20compliance%20with%20the%202018%20Bill%20was%20necessary%20for%20greater%20public%20interest.%20Accordingly%2C%20the%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%2C%202018%20(2018%20Bill)%2C%20prepared%20by%20the%20Srikrishna%20Committee%2C%20exempted%20processing%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98journalistic%20purpose%E2%80%99%20from%20complying%20with%20all%20provisions%20of%20the%202018%20Bill%2C%20except%20for%20the%20duty%20to%20process%20personal%20data%20in%20a%20fair%20and%20reasonable%20manner%20that%20respects%20the%20privacy%20of%20the%20data%20principal%2C%20and%20the%20obligation%20to%20implement%20reasonable%20security%20safeguards.3%20The%202018%20Bill%20defined%20%E2%80%98journalistic%20purpose%E2%80%99%20as%20any%20activity%20intended%20towards%20the%20dissemination%20through%20print%2C%20electronic%2C%20or%20any%20other%20media%20of%20factual%20reports%2C%20analysis%2C%20opinions%2C%20views%2C%20or%20documentaries%20regarding%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(i)%20%C2%A0news%2C%20recent%20or%20current%20events%3B%20or%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(ii)%20%C2%A0any%20other%20information%20that%20the%20data%20fiduciary%20believes%20the%20public%2C%20or%20any%20significantly%20discernible%20class%20of%20the%20public%2C%20to%20have%20an%20interest%20in%2C%20which%20would%20be%20absolved%20from%20obtaining%20consent%20from%20data%20principals.4%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.3%20%C2%A0The%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%2C%202019%20(introduced%20in%20the%20Parliament)%20and%20the%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%2C%202021%20(prepared%20by%20the%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20on%20data%20protection)%2C%20contained%20similar%20provisions%20to%20exempt%20processing%20for%20journalistic%20purposes.%20This%20position%20is%20notably%20consistent%20with%20other%20jurisdictions%20with%20data%20protection%20regimes%20that%20provide%20for%20exemptions%20from%20processing%20for%20journalistic%20purposes.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20European%20Union%E2%80%99s%20General%20Data%20Protection%20Regulation%20(GDPR)%20enables%20Member%20States%20to%20provide%20for%20exemptions%20or%20derogations%20from%20certain%20provisions%20(e.g.%2C%20have%20a%20lawful%20reason%20or%20basis%20for%20using%20data%2C%20provide%20privacy%20information%2C%20comply%20with%20individual%20rights%20that%20people%20have%20about%20their%20data%2C%20etc.)%20of%20the%20GDPR%20for%20journalistic%20purposes%20and%20freedom%20of%20expression.5%20Similarly%2C%20Singapore%E2%80%99s%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%202012%20provides%20an%20exception%20for%20news%20organizations%20to%20collect%2C%20use%2C%20and%20disclose%20personal%20data%20without%20consent%20solely%20for%20its%20news%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.4%20%C2%A0Despite%20this%2C%20processing%20for%20journalistic%20purposes%20is%20not%20exempt%20from%20the%20obligations%20under%20the%20DPDPA.%20It%20may%20be%20possible%20to%20argue%20that%20Section%2017(1)(c)%20of%20the%20DPDPA%2C%20which%20permits%20processing%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20prevention%2C%20detection%2C%20investigation%2C%20or%20prosecution%20of%20any%20offence%20or%20contravention%20of%20any%20law%2C%20would%20exempt%20processing%20for%20a%20specific%20kind%20of%20journalism%3A%20investigative%20journalism.%20However%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20broad%20exemption%20that%20applies%20to%20all%20journalistic%20activity%20(as%20envisaged%20under%20prior%20iterations%20of%20this%20law%20and%20international%20statutory%20frameworks)%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20clear%20guidance%20for%20this%20exemption%20severely%20hampers%20the%20ability%20of%20journalists%20to%20investigate%2C%20report%2C%20and%20publish%20any%20articles%20or%20reports%20of%20journalistic%20import.%20It%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20crucial%20that%20an%20exemption%20be%20made%20available%20to%20cover%20processing%20related%20to%20journalistic%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Unfortunately%2C%20India%20will%20be%20the%20sole%20modern%20democracy%20without%20an%20exemption%20for%20journalistic%20activities%2C%20which%20could%20severely%20impair%20the%20fourth%20pillar%20of%20democracy.%20Moreover%2C%20India%20is%20currently%20ranked%20161%20out%20of%20180%20countries%20in%20the%20World%20Press%20Freedom%20Index%20maintained%20by%20Reporters%20Without%20Borders%20below%20other%20Asian%20countries%20like%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20and%20Cambodia%2C%20and%20risks%20falling%20further%20down%20in%20the%20ranking%20if%20the%20DPDPA%20is%20enacted%20in%20its%20present%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Implications%20of%20the%20DPDPA%20on%20fundamental%20rights%20under%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20(Constitution)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.1%20%C2%A0The%20paramount%20legal%20obstacle%20posed%20by%20the%20DPDPA%20is%20to%20the%20fundamental%20freedoms%20of%20journalists%2C%20particularly%20to%20their%20freedom%20of%20occupation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20every%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20access%20information%20under%20Articles%2019(1)(g)%20and%2019(1)(a)%2C%20respectively%2C%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.2%20%C2%A0Violation%20of%20Article%2019(1)(g)%20of%20the%20ConstitutionArticle%2019(1)(g)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20protects%20the%20right%20to%20practise%20any%20profession%20or%20carry%20on%20any%20occupation%2C%20trade%2C%20or%20business.%20Journalists%20invariably%20handle%20personal%20data%20in%20the%20course%20of%20carrying%20out%20their%20occupation%2C%20be%20it%20through%20conducting%20research%2C%20investigating%20a%20lead%2C%20or%20publishing%20articles%20based%20on%20such%20personal%20data%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20These%20activities%20that%20lie%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20occupation%20are%20unreasonably%20restricted%20by%20the%20DPDPA%2C%20which%20imposes%20obligations%20upon%20them%20that%20are%20often%20impractical%20or%20infeasible%20or%20negate%20the%20very%20journalistic%20activity%20sought%20to%20be%20achieved%20through%20undertaking%20such%20processing%2C%20making%20the%20requirements%20under%20the%20DPDPA%20violative%20of%20every%20Article%2019(1)(g).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.3%20%C2%A0Violation%20of%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20of%20the%20ConstitutionIndia%20has%20recognised%20the%20right%20to%20receive%20information%20as%20a%20derivative%20of%20the%20fundamental%20right%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20guaranteed%20under%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20of%20the%20Constitution.7%20The%20exercise%20of%20these%20rights%20in%20the%20context%20of%20journalism%20involves%3A%20(i)%20every%20journalist%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20freedom%20and%20expression%2C%20including%20their%20right%20to%20receive%20information%3B%20and%20(ii)%20every%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20acquire%20information.%20Access%20to%20information%20is%20essential%20in%20a%20democratic%20nation%2C%20empowering%20citizens%20with%20critical%20information%2C%20and%20enabling%20them%20to%20consequently%20make%20informed%20choices.%20These%20rights%20are%20rendered%20meaningless%20if%20journalists%20are%20effectively%20forestalled%20from%20processing%20personal%20data%20without%20first%20complying%20with%20impractical%20and%20infeasible%20obligations%2C%20and%20thereby%20unable%20to%20either%20receive%20or%20disseminate%20information.%20citizens%20are%20well%20informed%20on%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20issues%20in%20respect%20of%20which%20they%20are%20called%20upon%20to%20express%20their%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.3.1.%20The%20press%20in%20India%20serves%20as%20a%20crucial%20bridge%20connecting%20citizens%20with%20information%2C%20ensuring%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20in%20governance%20as%20a%20watchdog%20of%20society.%20If%20journalists%20are%20required%20to%20adhere%20to%20the%20various%20prerequisites%20to%20processing%20personal%20data%20under%20the%20DPDPA%2C%20it%20would%20inevitably%20disrupt%20journalistic%20reporting%20in%20the%20country%20due%20to%20the%20highly%20onerous%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%20impossible%2C%20obligations%20this%20would%20entail.%20Such%20an%20impediment%20to%20journalistic%20reporting%20will%20necessarily%20violate%20journalists%E2%80%99%20and%20other%20citizens%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20information%20under%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.3.2.%20The%20Srikrishna%20Committee%20Report%20also%20recognised%20these%20consequences%20in%20noting%20that%20the%20untrammelled%20dissemination%20of%20news%2C%20current%20affairs%2C%20and%20documentaries%2C%20especially%20when%20they%20inform%2C%20criticise%2C%20and%20analyse%20issues%20of%20public%20importance%2C%20is%20in%20the%20public%20interest.8%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Existing%20frameworks%20that%20govern%20journalists%20provide%20sufficient%20safeguards%2C%20and%20processing%20for%20journalistic%20purposes%20should%20necessarily%20be%20exempted%20from%20complying%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20DPDPA%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.1%20%C2%A0The%20protection%20of%20personal%20data%20in%20the%20course%20of%20journalistic%20activities%20is%20built%20into%20journalistic%20conduct%2C%20such%20as%20those%20issued%20by%20the%20Press%20Council%20of%20India%20(PCI)%2C%20established%20under%20the%20Press%20Council%20Act%2C%201978%2C%20Code%20of%20Ethics%20and%20Broadcasting%20Standards%20released%20by%20the%20News%20Broadcasters%20and%20Digital%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.2%20%C2%A0Notably%2C%20the%20PCI%20prescribes%20safeguards%20in%20the%20context%20of%20communalism%20in%20the%20press%20and%20cautions%20against%20defamatory%20writings%20and%20objectionable%20investigative%20reporting%2C%20obscenity%2C%20and%20vulgarity%20in%2C%20for%20example%2C%20news%20stories%2C%20or%20feature%20reports.%20Journalists%20are%20barred%20from%20(i)%20intruding%20upon%20or%20invading%20the%20privacy%20of%20an%20individual%20unless%20outweighed%20by%20the%20genuine%20overriding%20public%20interest%3B%20(ii)%20tape-recording%20a%20conversation%20without%20that%20person%E2%80%99s%20knowledge%20or%20consent%2C%20except%20where%20the%20recording%20is%20necessary%20to%20protect%20the%20journalist%20in%20a%20legal%20action%2C%20or%20for%20other%20compelling%20good%20reason.%20Journalists%20are%20also%20required%20to%20(i)%20obtain%20the%20prior%20consent%20of%20a%20minor%E2%80%99s%20parent%2C%20if%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20interest%E2%80%9D%20overrides%20the%20minor%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20privacy%3B%20(iii)%20to%20apply%20due%20care%20by%20not%20disclosing%20the%20real%20names%20of%20persons%20involved%20in%20incidents%20affecting%20personal%20lives%3B%20and%20(iv)%20refrain%20from%20publishing%20inaccurate%2C%20baseless%2C%20graceless%2C%20misleading%20or%20distorted%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.3%20%C2%A0Given%20that%20these%20codes%20of%20conduct%2C%20which%20apply%20to%20all%20journalists%2C%20achieve%20a%20balance%20between%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20applying%20a%20second%20framework%20to%20the%20same%20processing%20activities%2C%20concerning%20the%20same%20personal%20data%20will%20only%20create%20duplicate%20compliance%20requirements%2C%20impose%20an%20unwarranted%20burden%20on%20journalists%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20impair%20free%20speech%20and%20expression.%20This%20is%20particularly%20true%20since%20these%20applicable%20codes%20of%20conduct%20for%20journalism%20provide%20a%20more%20tailored%20compliance%20regime%20in%20balancing%20the%20competing%20rights%20at%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20strongly%20urge%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20(Ministry)%20to%20ensure%20that%20processing%20for%20journalistic%20purposes%20is%20exempted%20from%20the%20application%20of%20the%20DPDPA.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20tools%20for%20doing%20so%20are%20built%20into%20the%20DPDPA%20itself.%20Under%20section%2017(5)%20of%20the%20DPDPA%2C%20the%20Government%20may%2C%20before%20the%20expiry%20of%20five%20years%20from%20the%20date%20of%20commencement%20of%20the%20DPDPA%2C%20by%20notification%2C%20declare%20that%20any%20provision%20of%20this%20DPDPA%20will%20not%20apply%20to%20any%20data%20fiduciary%20or%20classes%20of%20data%20fiduciaries%20for%20a%20period%20specified%20in%20the%20notification.%20An%20exemption%20may%20be%20necessary%20to%20stop%20harassment%20of%20journalists%20by%20inundating%20them%20with%20requests%20with%20a%20view%20of%20blocking%20or%20slowing%20down%20the%20investigation%20or%20publishing%20of%20a%20piece%20of%20news.%20The%20financial%20and%20human%20resource%20implications%20of%20compliance%20with%20such%20requests%20will%20also%20frustrate%20journalistic%20activity%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20case%20of%20independent%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20request%20that%20the%20Ministry%20provide%20a%20class%20exemption%20to%20data%20fiduciaries%20undertaking%20processing%20for%20journalistic%20purposes%20under%20section%2017(5)%20of%20the%20DPDPA%20for%20as%20long%20as%20such%20purposes%20subsist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20an%20exemption%20is%20particularly%20justified%20given%20that%20the%20absence%20of%20such%20a%20carve-out%20will%20have%20a%20necessarily%20adverse%20impact%20on%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%2C%20and%20the%20right%20of%20journalists%20to%20carry%20on%20their%20occupation.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20and%20as%20time%20is%20of%20the%20essence%2C%20we%20request%20the%20Ministry%20to%20frame%20this%20notification%20at%20the%20earliest%20before%20the%20DPDPA%20is%20brought%20into%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sincerely%20urge%20you%20to%20kindly%20take%20cognizance%20of%20the%20concerns%20expressed%20above%20and%20would%20further%20request%20an%20opportunity%20to%20take%20you%20through%20this%20submission%20in%20person%2C%20at%20your%20convenience.%20Until%20then%2C%20we%20await%20your%20valuable%20and%20informed%20guidance%20on%20this%20critical%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnant%20Nath%3Cbr%3E%5CnPresident%2C%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddress%3A%204%2F7-%20A%2C%20INS%20Building%2C%20Rafi%20Marg%2C%20New%20Delhi-11000%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708257636000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F23203159%2FScreen-Shot-2020-10-23-at-8.31.43-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Feditors-guild-expresses-grave-concerns-on-data-protection-act-in-representation-to-it-ministry%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20strongly%20urge%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20to%20ensure%20that%20processing%20for%20journalistic%20purposes%20is%20exempted%20from%20the%20application%20of%20the%20DPDPA.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Feditors-guild-expresses-grave-concerns-on-data-protection-act-in-representation-to-it-ministry%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NASA%20Shares%20Before%20And%20After%20Pics%20Of%20Rare%20Lake%20In%20World's%20Hottest%20Place%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENASA%20has%20shared%20before-and-after%20satellite%20pictures%20showing%20a%20temporary%20lake%20that%20recently%20formed%20in%20the%20US'%20Death%20Valley.%C2%A0As%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fearthobservatory.nasa.gov%2Fimages%2F152448%2Fbadwater-basin-refills%3Futm_source%3DTWITTER%26utm_medium%3DNASAEarth%26utm_campaign%3DNASASocial%26linkId%3D325812372%5C%22%3ENASA%20Earth%20observatory%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0the%20lake%20formed%20in%20August%202023%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Hurricane%20Hilary%2C%20and%20gradually%20shrank%20but%20persisted%20throughout%20the%20fall%20and%20winter.%20However%2C%20a%20potent%20atmospheric%20river%20filled%20it%20back%20up%20in%20February%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatellite%20imagery%20from%20NASA%20captured%20Death%20Valley's%20Badwater%20Basin%20before%C2%A0the%20hurricane%20and%20after%2C%20and%20again%20following%20the%20recent%20rainstorm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''This%20temporary%20lake%20in%20Death%20Valley%20is%20extending%20its%20stay.%20Rain%20from%20a%20potent%20atmospheric%20river%20filled%20up%20the%20Badwater%20Basin%20this%20month.%20These%20enhanced-color%20%23Landsat%20images%20show%20a%20shallow%20lake%20several%20kilometers%20across%2C%20with%20water%20emphasized%20in%20blue%2C''%20the%20post%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20temporary%20lake%20in%20Death%20Valley%20is%20extending%20its%20stay.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnRain%20from%20a%20potent%20atmospheric%20river%20filled%20up%20the%20Badwater%20Basin%20this%20month.%20These%20enhanced-color%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FLandsat%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Landsat%3C%2Fa%3E%20images%20show%20a%20shallow%20lake%20several%20kilometers%20across%2C%20with%20water%20emphasized%20in%20blue.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FYXeTZT6oGG%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FYXeTZT6oGG%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fh5vVfpQSjU%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fh5vVfpQSjU%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NASA%20Earth%20(%40NASAEarth)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNASAEarth%2Fstatus%2F1758525146900422848%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%C2%A0Death%20Valley%2C%C2%A0one%20of%20the%20hottest%20places%20on%20Earth%2C%C2%A0is%20the%20driest%20place%20in%20North%20America%20and%20typically%20receives%20about%202%20inches%20(51%20millimeters)%20of%20rain%20per%20year.%C2%A0However%2C%20in%20the%20past%20six%20months%20alone%2C%20more%20than%20double%20of%20that%20fell%20at%20the%20national%20park's%20official%20weather%20gauge%20at%20Furnace%20Creek.%C2%A0The%20remnants%20of%20Hurricane%20Hilary%20and%20an%20atmospheric%20river%20were%20responsible%20for%20most%20of%20that%20precipitation.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20see%20more%20frequent%20and%20intense%20rainfall%20as%20the%20planet%20warms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Based%20on%20satellite%20imagery%2C%20the%20lake%20appears%20to%20have%20grown%20to%20a%20similar%20size%20in%20February%202024%20as%20it%20did%20in%20August%202023%2C%20thereby%20extending%20its%20months-long%20tenure%2C''%20NASA%20said.%C2%A0As%20of%20February%2014%2C%20the%20lake%20is%201%20foot%20deep%20in%20places%2C%20according%20to%20park%20officials%2C%20and%20it%20is%20uncertain%20how%20long%20it%20will%20last.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Most%20of%20us%20thought%20the%20lake%20would%20be%20gone%20by%20October.%20We%20were%20shocked%20to%20see%20it%20still%20here%20after%20almost%20six%20months.%20This%20week's%20rain%20will%20extend%20how%20