3E%5CnThe%20recovery%20team%20has%20reached%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(%40IAF_MCC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIAF_MCC%2Fstatus%2F1759178371538268423%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20US%20Army%20grounded%20its%20Chinook%20fleet%20over%20engine%20fires.%20Boeing's%20India%20chief%2C%20Salil%20Hupte%2C%20said%20the%20Chinooks%20operated%20by%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20do%20not%20have%20any%20problems%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20impact%20on%20the%20helicopter%20operated%20by%20the%20Indian%20forces%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20had%20sought%20details%20from%20Boeing%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20of%20Chinook%2C%20about%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20grounding%20of%20the%20US%20Army's%20entire%20fleet%20of%20Chinook%20helicopters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinooks%20have%20served%20the%20US%20Army%20during%20its%20operation%20in%20Vietnam%2C%20the%20first%2C%20and%20second%20Gulf%20Wars%20and%20its%20operations%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChinook's%20Operational%20Capability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20fleet%20of%20Chinook%20choppers%20is%20based%20out%20of%20Chandigarh%20for%20operations%20in%20the%20north%20while%20another%20unit%20is%20located%20in%20Assam%20for%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20northeastern%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ch47%20Chinook%20Helicopters%20are%20heavy-lift%20helicopters%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20for%20strategic%20airlift%20and%20humanitarian%20efforts.%20The%20choppers%20were%20formally%20inducted%20into%20the%20force%20in%202019%20at%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20station%20in%20Chandigarh%20and%20the%20remaining%2011%20were%20delivered%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tandem-rotor%20design%20of%20the%20Chinook%20makes%20it%20a%20preferred%20choice%20for%20transporting%20troops%20and%20heavy%20cargo%20at%20high%20altitudes.%20It%20can%20transport%20tanks%2C%20relief%20aid%20and%20even%20artillery%20in%20underslung%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tandem%20rotor%20design%20of%20the%20Chinook%20provides%20increased%20stability%20and%20control%2C%20maximum%20agility%2C%20ease%20of%20loading%20and%20unloading%20and%20superior%20performance%20in%20the%20wind.%20The%20blades%20rotate%20in%20opposite%20directions%20to%20cancel%20out%20the%20torque%20generated%20by%20a%20blade%20and%20neutralize%20the%20yawing%20of%20the%20helicopter.%20In%20single-rotor%20helicopters%2C%20a%20tail%20rotor%20is%20used%20to%20counter%20the%20torque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chopper%20will%20spin%20on%20its%20vertical%20axis%20if%20the%20torque%20is%20not%20neutralised%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chopper%20has%20a%20service%20ceiling%20(height%20up%20to%20which%20it%20can%20fly)%20of%2020%2C000%20feet%20and%20Boeing%20says%20it's%20the%20only%20helicopter%20of%20this%20class%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708257360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F0q2i9ib8_chinook-landing-punjab-1200_625x300_18_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-forces-chinook-helicopter-makes-emergency-landing-in-punjabs-barnala-5081426%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Chinook%20helicopter%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20made%20a%20precautionary%20landing%20following%20a%20%26quot%3Btechnical%20snag%26quot%3B%20near%20Punjab's%20Barnala%20on%20Sunday%2C%20police%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-forces-chinook-helicopter-makes-emergency-landing-in-punjabs-barnala-5081426%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-forces-chinook-helicopter-makes-emergency-landing-in-punjabs-barnala-5081426%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%