must%20make%20India%20developed%2C%20and%20in%20this%2C%20the%20next%205%20years%20will%20play%20a%20significant%20role.%20In%20the%20next%205%20years%2C%20India%20must%20work%20at%20a%20much%20faster%20pace%20than%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20citing%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20%26quot%3Bab%20ki%20paar%2C%20400%20paar%26quot%3B%20gaffe%20in%20the%20Parliament%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20even%20opposition%20leaders%20are%20chanting%20slogans%20of%20the%20NDA%20government%20crossing%20the%20400-mark.%20And%20for%20NDA%20to%20cross%20400%2C%20BJP%20must%20surpass%20the%20milestone%20of%20370.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20coalition%20won%20more%20than%20350%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20election.%20But%20PM%20Modi%20and%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20proclaimed%20that%20this%20time%20they%20are%20looking%20beyond%20400%20seats%2C%20making%20it%20the%20most%20decisive%20victory%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20his%20tirade%20against%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20sin%20of%20Congress%20is%20that%20it%20has%20not%20hesitated%20to%20break%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20country's%20armed%20forces.%20Congress%20has%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20causing%20damage%20to%20India's%20national%20security%20and%20military%20strength%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20holding%20the%20two-day%20convention%20as%20part%20of%20its%20preparations%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20inaugural%20day%20of%20the%20national%20convention%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20BJP%20passed%20a%20political%20resolution%20titled%20'Viksit%20Bharat'%2C%20highlighting%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20Centre%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%20It%20asserted%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20return%20for%20a%20third%20term%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20carry%20forward%20its%20roadmap%20for%20%26quot%3