20It's%20Not%20AAP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECricketer-turned-politician%20Navjot%20Singh%20Sidhu's%20rallies%20and%20Punjab%20Congress's%20sharp%20response%20have%20yet%20again%20turned%20the%20spotlight%20on%20the%20infighting%20within%20the%20Congress%20that%20may%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20bigger%20challenge%20than%20political%20rivals%20AAP%20and%20BJP%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sidhu%20has%20been%20holding%20rallies%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Punjab%20without%20a%20clearance%20from%20the%20state%20party%20unit.%20Punjab%20Congress%20chief%20Amarinder%20Singh%20Raja%20Warring%20has%20warned%20that%20indiscipline%20will%20attract%20expulsion%20from%20the%20party.%20%26quot%3BNobody%20is%20above%20the%20party.%20Whoever%20wants%20to%20do%20something%20can%20do%20without%20Congress's%20symbol%20and%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20media%20query%20on%20the%20rallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20Partap%20Singh%20Bajwa%20has%20also%20taken%20a%20swipe%20at%20Mr%20Sidhu.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20(Sidhu)%20were%20the%20PPCC%20president%2C%20you%20brought%20(Congress)%20from%2078%20(seats%20in%202017)%20to%2018%20(seats%20in%202022).%20Now%2C%20what%20more%20does%20he%20want%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bajwa%20said.%20Urging%20the%20retired%20cricketer%20to%20join%20the%20party%20protests%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCome%20to%20that%20stage%20and%20speak%20what%20you%20want.%20Setting%20up%20'apna%20nawan%20akhara'%20(own%20stage)%20is%20not%20a%20good%20thing.%20No%20Punjab%20Congressman%20considers%20it%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sidhu%2C%20however%2C%20remains%20unfazed.%20%26quot%3BIf%205%2C000-7%2C000%20people%20gather%20at%20some%20place%2C%20why%20does%20someone%20have%20a%20stomach%20ache%3F%20For%20whom%20are%20we%20fighting%3F%20We%20are%20fighting%20to%20change%20this%20system%20in%20Punjab%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20recently.%20At%20his%20rallies%2C%20Mr%20Sidhu%20has%20been%20targeting%20both%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20dispensation%20in%20Punjab.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20face-off%20has%20also%20sparked%20speculation%20that%20Mr%20Sidhu%20may%20be%20planning%20a%20return%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20he%20left%20in%202017%20to%20join%20the%20Congress.%20If%20he%20eventually%20makes%20the%20switch%2C%20he%20will%20join%20the%20long%20list%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20who%20exited%20the%20party%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20This%20list%20of%20heavyweights%20includes%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Amarinder%20Singh%20and%20former%20minister%20and%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Sunil%20Jakhar%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress-to-BJP%20switchovers%20of%20Punjab%20leaders%20point%20to%20a%20weakening%20of%20Congress's%20organisational%20strength%20that%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20its%20ouster%20in%20the%202022%20polls.%20The%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20has%20decided%20to%20go%20solo%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20after%20months%20of%20tussle%20with%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP).%20The%20AAP%20is%20Congress's%20ally%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20but%20its%20arch-rival%20in%20Punjab.%20But%20as%20the%20polls%20draw%20close%2C%20it%20appears%20Congress's%20real%20fight%20is%20to%20set%20its%20house%20in%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrouble%20In%20Haryana%2C%20Himachal%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20infighting%20troubles%20are%20not%20limited%20to%20Punjab.%20In%20neighbouring%20Haryana%2C%20the%20power%20tussle%20between%20former%20Chief%20minister%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20and%20the%20troika%20of%20senior%20leaders%20Kumari%20Selja%2C%20Randeep%20Surjewala%20and%20Kiran%20Chaudhary%2C%20is%20out%20in%20the%20open.%20The%20three%20leaders%20--%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20SRK%20group%20--recently%20skipped%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20state%20Congress's%20election%20committee%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tension%20within%20the%20Congress%20has%20prompted%20the%20BJP%20to%20take%20a%20swipe.%20Haryana%20Home%20Minister%20Anil%20Vij%20said%20the%20Congress%20stands%20no%20chance%20against%20the%20BJP.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Haryana%2C%20first%20let%20these%20people%20come%20together.%20One%20day%2C%20Selja%20Kumari%20takes%20out%20a%20rally.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20Bhupinder%20Hooda%20takes%20out%20a%20rally.%20Selja%20does%20not%20go%20to%20Bhupinder%20Hooda's%20rally%20and%20Bhupinder%20Hooda%20does%20not%20go%20to%20Selja's%20rally.%20Can%20they%20fight%20with%20us%3F%20They%20cannot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20an%20ANI%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20too%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20on%20a%20bumpy%20road.%20State%20minister%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%2C%20son%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20late%20Virbhadra%20Singh%2C%20appeared%20to%20publicly%20criticise%20his%20party's%20government%20over%20the%20recently-tabled%20budget.%20In%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20said%20that%20he%20has%20noted%20how%20the%20mention%20of%20several%20social%20sections%20was%20missing%20from%20the%20budget%20and%20had%20raised%20the%20matter%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Vikramaditya%20Singh's%20mother%20and%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Pratibha%20Singh%20had%20congratulated%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20The%20minister%20also%20attended%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20despite%20the%20Congress%20high%20command's%20announcement%20that%20it%20will%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708255500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F25u6pin_navjot-sidhu_625x300_18_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2