20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYouTube%20has%20been%20the%20game%20changer%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20idea%20that%20it%20could%20pay%20this%20well%2C%20especially%20for%20someone%20like%20me%20who%20wasn't%20really%20anticipating%20it%20being%20a%20side%20hustle%2C%20and%20it's%20quickly%20turned%20into%20my%20one%20that%20I'm%20focusing%20on%20the%20most.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20original%20plan%20for%20YouTube%20was%20to%20use%20it%20as%20a%20way%20to%20be%20accountable%20for%20tracking%20his%20progress%20toward%20paying%20off%20his%20home%20where%20he%20would%20post%20updates%20on%20what%20he's%20earned%20and%20how.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20posts%20on%20his%20YouTube%20account%20with%20over%2017%2C000%20subscribers%20about%20side%20hustles%20he%20has%20tried.%20Other%20videos%20include%20a%20ranking%20of%20side%20hustles%20and%20talking%20about%20taxes%20for%20this%20kind%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20suggests%20others%20interested%20in%20YouTube%20to%20try%20it%20as%20he%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20expect%20for%20himself%20after%20he%20said%20he%20started%20with%20what%20he%20considered%20a%20low%20quality%20webcam%20and%20microphone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorst%20case%20scenario%2C%20you%20put%20yourself%20out%20there%2C%20you%20gave%20it%20your%20best%20shot%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20patient%20and%20you%20keep%20going%20at%20it%2C%20people%20will%20pick%20up%20on%20authenticity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDataAnnotation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20recommends%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dataannotation.tech%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDataAnnotation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20site%20where%20%26quot%3Byou%20will%20help%20train%20AI%20chatbots%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20development%20of%20sophisticated%20AI%20programs%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20site's%20FAQ%20page%2C%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20side%20hustle%20where%20you%20don't%20n