0he%20didn't%20put%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20several%20ways%20creators%20can%20earn%2C%20including%20linking%20to%20qualifying%20products%2C%20promoting%20Amazon%20services%20like%20Prime%20video%20and%20Amazon%20Music%2C%20curating%20shoppable%20photo%20and%20video%20content%20and%20livestreaming%20and%20recommending%20products%20through%20Amazon%20Live%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fside-hustle-ugc-delivery-make-money-flexible-time-easy-jobs-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20side%20hustle%20people%20end%20up%20doing%20could%20depend%20on%20their%20goal.%20Scott%20suggested%20surveys%20or%20work%20from%20DataAnnotation%20if%20you're%20interested%20in%20a%20few%20extra%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you%20want%20the%20ultimate%20goal%20of%20scaling%2C%20then%20you%20need%20to%20do%20something%20like%20YouTube%20where%20you%20can%20make%20it%20your%20own%20image%20and%20your%20own%20company%20almost%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Estuff%20like%20the%20Amazon%20Influencer%20Program%20that%20has%20passive%20income%20streams%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20depends%20what%20your%20end%20goal%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHow%20much%20have%20you%20made%20from%20side%20hustles%3F%20What%20are%20you%20doing%20to%20meet%20your%20financial%20goals%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20to%20share%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhoff%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Emhoff%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fside-hustle-recommendations-surveys-youtube-retirement-goal-house-truck-payment-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2F