2%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapans-naked-men-festival-succumbs-to-population-ageing%2Famp_articleshow%2F107795931.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Says%20Congress%2C%20AAP%20%26quot%3BMutually%20Agreed%26quot%3B%20To%20Go%20Solo%20In%20Punjab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20had%20%26quot%3Bmutually%20agreed%26quot%3B%20to%20contest%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Punjab%20separately%20and%20there%20is%20no%20bad%20blood%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20over%20this%20issue%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20today%20visited%20Congress%20leader%20and%20renowned%20lawyer%20Abhishek%20Singhvi's%20home%20for%20lunch.%20Speaking%20to%20reporters%20on%20the%20decision%20by%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20to%20go%20solo%20in%20Punjab%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20Punjab%2C%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20have%20mutually%20agreed%20to%20contest%20the%20polls%20separately.%20There%20is%20no%20hostility%20over%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tussle%20between%20Congress%20and%20AAP%2C%20rivals%20in%20Punjab%20but%20allies%20in%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20has%20made%20headlines%20for%20weeks%20now.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20the%20AAP%20is%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20Congress%20to%20finalise%20seat-sharing%20in%20Delhi.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20Congress%20over%20an%20alliance%20in%20Delhi.%20We%20are%20discussing%20seat-sharing%20arrangements.%20The%20BJP%20will%20have%20it%20easy%20if%20there%20is%20no%20alliance%20(between%20Congress%20and%20AAP)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20won%20all%20seven%20parliamentary%20seats%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20They%20had%20achieved%20the%20same%20feat%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20remark%20suggests%20that%20the%20INDIA%20allies%20have%20decided%20to%20balance%20their%20national%20objective%20of%20taking%20on%20the%20BJP%20and%20their%20regional%20goal%20of%20holding%20on%20to%20their%20strongholds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20had%20announced%20that%20AAP%20had%20decided%20to%20contest%20all%2013%20seats%20in%20Punjab%20alone.%20Partap%20Singh%20Bajwa%2C%20one%20of%20the%20Congress's%20top%20leaders%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20had%20'thanked'%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20said%20this%20is%20exactly%20what%20the%20Congress%20wants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20Punjab%20and%20other%20states.%20Here%2C%20they%20(AAP)%20are%20in%20the%20government%20and%20we%20are%20the%20principal%20opposition.%20How%20can%20both%20of%20us%20get%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bajwa%20had%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20get%20together%2C%20the%20anti-incumbency%20vote%20is%20going%20to%20shift%2C%20either%20to%20the%20BJP%20or%20to%20the%20Akali%20Dal.%20How%20can%20we%20relinquish%20our%20position%3F%20Congress%20is%20on%20the%20comeback%20train.%20This%20way%2C%20we%20will%20finish%20our%20existence.%20We%20have%20to%20preserve%20our%20vote%20bank%2C%20and%20build%20on%20it.%20This%20is%20much%20better%20for%20both%20(Congress%20and%20AAP)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20understanding%20between%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20has%20drawn%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20the%20BJP.%20Top%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20its%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20have%20termed%20the%20alliance%20%26quot%3Bopportunistic%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708251120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fvu8dmsjo_arvind-kejriwal-rahul-gandhi-rahul-kejriwal-650_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-aap-congress-arvind-kejriwal-says-congress-aap-mutually-agreed-