ays-lalu-prasad-yadav%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22R%20Ashwin%20Returns%20To%20Field%20Without%20'Penalty%20Time'.%20ICC%20Rule%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESenior%20India%20off-spinner%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20was%20back%20in%20action%20during%20the%20post-tea%20session%20on%20the%20fourth%20day%20of%20the%20third%20Test%20against%20England%20after%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20leave%20for%20Chennai%20to%20attend%20to%20his%20ailing%20mother.%20Ashwin%20had%20left%20for%20Chennai%20hours%20after%20reaching%20the%20coveted%20milestone%20of%20500%20Test%20wickets%20on%20the%20second%20day%20of%20the%20match.%20Ashwin%20did%20not%20incur%20any%20'Penalty%20time'%20for%20his%20absence%20on%20the%20third%20day%20as%20per%20the%20ICC's%20Playing%20Conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20ICC's%20clause%2024.3.2%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20nominated%20player's%20absence%20will%20not%20incur%20Penalty%20time%20if%2C%20in%20the%20opinion%20of%20umpires%2C%20if%20the%20player%20has%20left%20the%20field%20for%20other%20wholly%20acceptable%20reason%2C%20which%20shall%20not%20include%20illness%20or%20internal%20injury.%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20arrived%20in%20Rajkot%20on%20Sunday%20afternoon%2C%20was%20seen%20going%20through%20the%20drills%20during%20the%20tea%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20BCCI%20confirmed%20during%20the%20first%20session%20of%20the%20fourth%20day%20about%20Ashwin%20rejoining%20national%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20is%20pleased%20to%20announce%20the%20return%20of%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20to%20the%20squad%20after%20a%20brief%20absence%20due%20to%20a%20family%20emergency.%20Ashwin%20had%20to%20temporarily%20withdraw%20from%20the%20squad%20after%20Day%202%20of%20the%203rd%20Test%20in%20Rajkot%20to%20attend%20to%20a%20family%20emergency%2C%26quot%3B%20BCCI%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3