%20donors%20who%20used%20the%20opaque%20scheme.%20The%20finance%20ministry%20and%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20%E2%80%93%20both%20of%20which%20had%20key%20roles%20in%20drafting%20the%20scheme%20%E2%80%93%20have%20said%20nothing%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20its%20affidavit%20to%20the%20top%20court%2C%20the%20commission%20said%20it%20is%20in%20favour%20of%20transparency%20and%20when%20the%20order%20is%20issued%2C%20it%20will%20take%20action%20as%20directed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-to-follow-top-court-order-on-electoral-bonds-cec-rajiv-kumar-101708184521890.html%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20Saturday%20(February%2017)%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felection-commission-has-no-comments-on-landmark-verdict-on-electoral-bonds-how-it-changed-its-stance%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20EC%20had%20taken%20contradictory%20positions%20on%20the%20schemes%20at%20different%20times.%20While%20it%20had%20expressed%20serious%20reservations%20initially%2C%20even%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cretrograde%20step%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20then%20went%20on%20to%20back%20the%20scheme%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20argue%20that%20it%20should%20not%20be%20stayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20response%20from%20the%20Modi%20government%20%E2%80%93%20which%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpart-of-secret-ballot-how-the-modi-govt-backed-electoral-bonds-in-the-supreme-court%5C%22%3Evehemently%20argued%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%E2%80%93%20so%20far%20has%20come%20from%20Union%20law%20minister%20Arjun%20Meghwal.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20government%20is%20%E2%80%9Cexamining%E2%80%9D%20the%20verdict%20and%20will%20decide%20whether%20to%20challenge%20the%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20total%20number%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2012%2C008%20crore%20sold%20between%202017-2018%20and%202022-2023%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felectoral-bonds-are-illegal-now-but-who-benefited-for-the-6-years-they-lasted%5C%22%3EBJP%20received%20nearly%2055%25%20or%20Rs%206%2C564%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Congress%20has%20received%20just%209.5%25%20of%20all%20bonds%20sold%20in%20the%20five-year%20period%20at%20Rs%201%2C135%20crore.%20The%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20received%20Rs%201%2C096%20crore%20from%20electoral%20bonds%20in%20this%20same%20time%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708233793000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25220532%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-10.04.47%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-will-follow-supreme-courts-directions-on-electoral-bonds-cec%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIn%20its%20affidavit%20to%20the%20top%20court%2C%20the%20commission%20said%20it%20is%20in%20favour%20of%20transparency%20and%20when%20the%20order%20is%20issued%2C%20it%20will%20take%20action%20as%20directed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-will-follow-supreme-courts-directions-on-electoral-bonds-cec%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Priyanka%20shares%20cute%20video%20of%20daughter%20Malti%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708233221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107790796%2Cimgsize-283885.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpriyanka-chopra-nick-jonas-daughter-malti-playing-in-ball-pit-cutest-thing-youll-see-today%2Farticleshow