C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20reporters%20in%20Srinagar%20on%20Thursday%2C%20February%2015%2C%20Abdullah%20said%20that%20there%20are%20%E2%80%9Cno%20two%20opinions%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20NC%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20was%20going%20to%20contest%20the%202024%20general%20election%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20%E2%80%9Con%20the%20basis%20of%20our%20strength%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20triggered%20speculations%20that%20after%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20NC%20president%20could%20be%20the%20latest%20addition%20to%20the%20list%20of%20political%20leaders%20who%20have%20deserted%20the%20fledgling%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20Abdullah%2C%20the%20NC%20vice-president%2C%20however%2C%20clarified%20that%20his%20party%20%E2%80%9Ccontinues%20to%20remain%20a%20member%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%9D.%20He%20claimed%20that%20the%20NC%20has%20had%20%E2%80%9Cinformal%20talks%E2%80%9D%20on%20seat-sharing%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20leads%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20while%20asserting%20that%20his%20party%20was%20going%20to%20contest%20on%20three%20out%20of%20six%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Ladakh%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20constituencies%20%E2%80%93%20Srinagar-Budgam%2C%20Baramulla-Kupwara%20and%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20%E2%80%93%20were%20won%20by%20the%20NC%20in%20the%202019%20parliamentary%20election.%20%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20the%20seats%20that%20are%20to%20be%20discussed%20are%20those%20held%20by%20the%20BJP%20(Jammu%2C%20Udhampur%20and%20Ladakh).%20We%20are%20firm%20on%20that%20position%2C%E2%80%9D%20Omar%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20are%20spread%20over%2012%20districts%20of%20the%20Kashmir%20valley%20and%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20where%20all%20the%20three%20major%20constituents%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20%E2%80%93%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%2C%20NC%20and%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20have%20had%20a%20significant%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202014%20assembly%20election%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20the%20PDP%20had%20emerged%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20with%2028%20seats%20(including%20three%20seats%20in%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20and%20the%20rest%20from%20Kashmir%20Valley)%20followed%20by%20the%20National%20Conference%20with%2015%20seats%20and%20the%20Congress%20with%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu-based%20editor%20and%20political%20analyst%20Zafar%20Choudhary%20said%20that%20the%20NC%E2%80%99s%20decision%20was%20unlikely%20to%20be%20acceptable%20to%20the%20allies%20of%20INDIA%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20%E2%80%93%20PDP%20and%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20which%20could%20force%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfight%20to%20the%20finish%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20three%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20BJP%20looks%20confident%20on%20its%20two%20traditional%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20(Jammu%20and%20Udhampur)%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20an%20NC-PDP-Congress%20alliance%20would%20clearly%20put%20the%20BJP%20in%20a%20position%20of%20advantage%20in%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20and%20Ladakh%20seats.%20An%20unofficial%20BJP%20ally%20could%20even%20emerge%20as%20a%20key%20competitor%20in%20north%20Kashmir%2C%E2%80%9D%20Choudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERekha%20Chowdhary%2C%20former%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Jammu%2C%20believes%20that%20the%20NC%20is%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbetter%20position%E2%80%9D%20electorally%20in%20Kashmir%20than%20other%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20main%20rival%20of%20the%20National%20Conference%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20is%20the%20PDP%2C%20has%20become%20quite%20weak%20because%20of%20the%20exodus%20of%20some%20of%20its%20leaders%20and%20other%20factors.%20The%20PDP%20has%20lost%20its%20confidence%20and%20the%20party%20is%20not%20in%20a%20position%20where%20it%20can%20negotiate%20seat-sharing%20with%20other%20INDIA%20partners%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZafar%20Choudhary%20agreed%20that%20the%20PDP%20has%20been%20suffering%20politically%20because%20of%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%202015.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20subsequent%20events%20including%20government%20formation%20crisis%20following%20Mufti%20Sayeed%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%202016%20civilian%20unrest%2C%20fall%20of%20government%20in%202018%20and%20the%20casual%20handling%20of%20the%20dismissal%20of%20assembly%20project%20the%20PDP%20in%20a%20poor%20light%20and%2C%20consequently%2C%20the%20NC%20in%20a%20better%20position%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20senior%20PDP%20leader%20said%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cno%20question%E2%80%9D%20that%20his%20party%20was%20going%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20contest%20but%20%E2%80%9Cour%20foremost%20goal%20is%20unity%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20party%20was%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cconsultation%20process%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20won%E2%80%99t%20take%20a%20decision%20under%20pressure%20or%20in%20a%20hurry%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20question%20of%20just%20the%20elections%20but%20how%20to%20strengthen%20our%20voice%20at%20the%20national%20level%20and%20in%20the%20parliament%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20PDP%20leader%2C%20who%20served%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20PDP-BJP%20coalition%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PDP%20leader%20said%20that%20the%20party%20will%20%E2%80%9Cideally%20want%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20a%20united%20voice%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20BJP%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20if%20one%20of%20the%20constituents%20does%20not%20want%20to%20yield%20space%20to%20others%2C%20we%20would%20feel%20our%20attempts%20from%202019%20to%20forge%20unity%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20first%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Gupkar%20Alliance%20and%20then%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20have%20failed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZafar%20Choudhary%20said%20that%20the%20Gupkar%20alliance%20between%20the%20three%20parties%20did%20not%20work%20electorally%20as%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%202020%20District%20Development%20Council%20(DDC)%20elections%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20parties%20also%20realised%20that%20they%20compete%20on%20the%20same%20electoral%20landscape%20for%20their%20individual%20survival%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20then%2C%20Omar%20has%20believed%20in%20separating%20the%20electoral%20and%20ideological%20agenda%20within%20the%20Gupkar%20alliance.%20In%20November%202022%2C%20the%20NC%20released%20a%20list%20of%2046%20leaders%20for%20as%20many%20constituencies%20in%20Kashmir%20calling%20them%20Constituency-Incharge.%20This%20was%20a%20clear%20message%20to%20the%20allies%20that%20there%20was%20no%20scope%20for%20alliance%20whenever%20assembly%20elections%20are%20held.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Dr%20Abdullah%20and%20Omar%20have%20%E2%80%9Cconsistently%20held%20divergent%20views%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20alliance%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20Dr%20Abdullah%20has%20always%20reiterated%20the%20primacy%20of%20the%20Gupkar%20Alliance%2C%20Omar%20has%20taken%20more%20practical%20actions%20to%20consolidate%20on%20a%20post-2019%20advantage%20uniquely%20available%20to%20the%20National%20Conference.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERekha%20Chowdharyy%20said%20that%20the%20NC%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20the%20DDC%20election%20may%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cconfidence%E2%80%9D%20about%20its%20performance%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20commitment%20(to%20INDIA%20alliance)%20is%20not%20entrenched%20in%20the%20political%20parties%20in%20Kashmir.%20No%20party%20will%20sacrifice%20its%20interests%20for%20the%20interests%20of%20any%20alliance.%20While%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20is%20more%20committed%20to%20the%20INDIA%20and%20Gupkar%20alliances%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20her%20party%2C%20NC%20is%20not%20dependent%20on%20either%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20Omar%20said%20that%20political%20parties%20have%20to%20make%20%E2%80%9Csmall%20sacrifices%20%E2%80%A6%20for%20a%20bigger%20objective%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20objective%20of%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20to%20weaken%20each%20other%2C%20the%20National%20Conference%20is%20ready%20for%20negotiations.%20What%20purpose%20will%20a%20weakened%20National%20Conference%20serve%20if%20the%20aim%20is%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708231397000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18101256%2Findia-jandk.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdifficult-conversations-await-the-india-alliance-in-jk%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20National%20Conference%20declaring%20that%20it%20intends%20to%20contest%20in%20the%20three%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20it%20currently%20holds%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Ladakh%2C%20seat-sharing%20talks%20may%20be%20a%20tricky%20affair.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdifficult-conversations-await-the-india-alliance-in-jk%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20Thai%20Prime%20Minister%20Thaksin%20freed%20on%20parole%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708230556000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FA20F%2Fproduction%2F_132678414_thaksin_getty.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68329953%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thaksin%20Shinawatra%2C%20one%20of%20Thailand's%20most%20divisive%20figures%2C%20was%20convicted%20last%20year%20on%20corruption%20charges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A73%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-6