he%20following%20is%20an%20excerpt%20from%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Practices%20of%20the%20State%3A%20Muslims%2C%20Law%20and%20Violence%20in%20India%3Cem%3E%20by%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%20%3Cem%3ETanweer%20Fazal%20(Three%20Essays%20Collective%2C%202024).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20year%202019%20marked%20a%20watershed%20in%20the%20biography%20of%20the%20Indian%20state.%20The%20resounding%20victory%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Right%20in%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%20second%20one%20in%20continuation%2C%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20series%20of%20parliamentary%20amendments%20and%20enactments%20directed%20towards%20inverting%20constitutional%20guarantees%20and%20protections%20that%20the%20polity%20had%20until%20now%20offered%20to%20its%20minority%20citizens.%20The%20criminalisation%20of%20triple%20talaq%2C%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20the%20enactment%20of%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(2019)%E2%80%94patently%20contentious%20and%20perilous%E2%80%94were%20expeditiously%20executed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20judicial%20challenges%20nor%20the%20wave%20of%20protests%20that%20sprung%20up%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20deterred%20the%20government.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20judiciary%20too%20joined%20in%20this%20new%20drift%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20Republic%20by%20two%20pronouncements%20of%20far-reaching%20consequences.%20The%20Supreme%20Court-directed%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20published%20the%20final%20list%20of%20citizens%20in%20Assam%2C%20which%20ultimately%20left%20nearly%20two%20million%20residents%20of%20the%20state%2C%20mostly%20Bengalis%2C%20stateless.%20In%20addition%2C%20a%20five-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Apex%20Court%20handed%20over%20the%20title%20of%20the%20site%20of%20the%20demolished%20Babri%20mosque%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20In%20August%202020%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20the%20company%20of%20the%20RSS%20chief%2C%20an%20organisation%20indicted%20for%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20mosque%20in%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18090619%2FTF-COVER_page-0001.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18090619%2FTF-COVER_page-0001.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18090619%2FTF-COVER_page-0001-300x236.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18090619%2FTF-COVER_page-0001-1024x806.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697671%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22944%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECover%20page%20of%20the%20book%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EThe%20Practices%20of%20the%20State%3A%20Muslims%2C%20Law%20and%20Violence%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20by%C2%A0Tanweer%20Fazal%20(Three%20Essays%20Collective%2C%202024)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20%E2%80%98new%20normal%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20illusive%20%E2%80%98idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98new%20normal%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20is%20argued%2C%20militates%20against%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20%E2%80%94%20the%20vision%20of%20a%20plural%20society%2C%20of%20a%20non-denominational%20secular%20republic%20that%20its%20founders%20embraced%20and%20set%20out%20to%20realise%20once%20unfettered%20of%20colonial%20chains.%20For%20many%20commentators%2C%20this%20plummeting%20of%20the%20Indian%20core%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98monochromatic%20nationalism%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20new%20one%2C%20and%20certainly%20%E2%80%98un-Indian%E2%80%99.%20In%20the%20late%201990s%2C%20Sunil%20Khilnani%2C%20in%20his%20treatise%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20saw%20a%20diversity%20of%20opinions%2C%20ideas%20and%20styles%20as%20constitutive%20of%20Indian%20nationalism%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98a%20dhoti%20with%20endless%20folds%E2%80%99.%20A%20decade%20later%2C%20when%20the%20politics%20of%20Hindutva%20had%20begun%20baying%20for%20blood%2C%20Khilnani%20clarified%20that%20the%20plural%20idea%20of%20India%20had%20within%20its%20store%2C%20%E2%80%98conceptions%20that%20sought%20to%20singularise%E2%80%99%20Indian%20diversity%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98make%20it%20a%20narrower%20place%E2%80%99.%20This%20politics%20had%20made%20Gujarat%20the%20%E2%80%98calendar%20girl%20of%20big%20business%E2%80%99%2C%20also%20the%20%E2%80%98purveyor%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98most%20chauvinistic%20and%20poisonous%20politics%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20argued%20(2012%2C%20p.%203).%20He%2C%20however%2C%20still%20continued%20to%20rest%20his%20hopes%20on%20democracy%20%E2%80%94%20an%20accomplishment%20of%20the%20founders%20of%20the%20founders%20that%20still%20stood%20tall%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20broken%2C%20ragged%20histories%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20contrast%20was%20invariably%20drawn%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20owed%20its%20genesis%20to%20religious%20nationalism%2C%20and%20had%20miserably%20failed%20to%20hold%20together.%20Khilnani%20feared%20that%20India%20might%20turn%20into%20a%20Hindu%20Pakistan%20if%20a%20politics%20centred%20on%20cultural%20supremacy%20was%20allowed%20to%20prevail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20years%20later%20when%20the%20liberal%20icon%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20echoed%20the%20same%20fear%2C%20he%20received%20a%20terrible%20backlash%20from%20the%20Hindu%20public%2C%20purportedly%2C%20for%20uttering%20the%20words%20Hindu%20and%20Pakistan%20in%20a%20single%20breath.%20But%20such%20comparisons%20with%20Pakistan%20or%20Taliban%20are%20not%20so%20uncommon%20in%20India%20today.%20The%20allegory%20is%20invoked%20to%20contrast%20the%20intrinsic%20Indian%20ethos%20of%20tolerance%20as%20against%20the%20fanaticism%20of%20its%20neighbour.%20The%20roots%20of%20an%20archetypal%20Indian%20tolerance%20are%20then%20traced%20to%20the%20ancient%20philosophy%20and%20Hindu%20view%20of%20the%20self%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20celebrated%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Argumentative%20Indian%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2005)%2C%20Amartya%20Sen%20traces%20the%20roots%20of%20Indian%20pluralism%20to%20the%20co-existence%20of%20competing%20paths%20to%20truth%20in%20the%20Rig%20Veda.%20The%20crux%20of%20Tharoor%E2%80%99s%20critique%20of%20Hindutva%20in%20%3Cem%3EWhy%20I%20am%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2018)%20is%20how%20the%20former%20defies%20the%20inherent%20diversity%20of%20thought%20and%20plurality%20of%20practices%20that%20is%20characteristic%20of%20Hinduism.%20Far%20from%20embarrassing%20the%20proponents%20of%20militant%20Hindutva%2C%20this%20project%20ends%20up%20reinforcing%20the%20distortions%20that%20imaginaries%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%20hinge%20on%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tolerant%20and%20accommodating%20Hindu%20whose%20Hinduness%20is%20intrinsic%20to%20Indian%20tolerance.%20This%20imaginary%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Indian%20then%20stands%20in%20contrast%20to%20portrayals%20of%20the%20treacherous%20and%20bigoted%20Muslim.%20The%20source%20of%20violence%2C%20the%20agent%20provocateur%20is%20then%20the%20Muslim%20%E2%80%94%20the%20sword-bearing%2C%20beef-eating%20Jihadist.%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20vision%20of%20a%20plural%20and%20diverse%20India%20was%20so%20deeply%20embedded%20in%20its%20heart%20and%20soul%2C%20how%20did%20the%20idea%20unravel%20in%20no%20time%3F%20How%20come%20the%20institutions%20that%20it%20founded%20fell%20in%20line%2C%20offering%20not%20a%20modicum%20of%20resistance%3F%20Of%20all%20the%20recent%20breaches%20in%20the%20foundational%20idea%20of%20India%2C%20one%20with%20the%20most%20far-reaching%20ramifications%20is%20the%20alteration%20in%20the%20citizenship%20law%20that%20allows%20faith%20to%20make%20a%20surreptitious%20entry%20in%20the%20provisions%20for%20according%20citizenship%20to%20immigrants.%20It%20despatches%20a%20message%20loud%20and%20clear%2C%20that%20blood%20and%20belongingness%20will%20be%20a%20determinant%20of%20Indian%20nationality%20%E2%80%94%20jus%20sanguinus%20as%20against%20jus%20solis%20(the%20right%20of%20soil%20determined%20by%20birth).%20Undoubtedly%2C%20the%20secular%20foundation%20of%20Indian%20nationhood%20is%20at%20stake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20loud%20and%20vociferous%20protests%20that%20followed%20its%20enactment%20remained%20confined%20to%20Muslim%20localities%20where%20too%20the%20repression%20of%20the%20state%20machinery%20was%20felt%20most%20viscerally.%20Even%20though%20a%20section%20of%20the%20intelligentsia%20and%20the%20secular%20civil%20society%20enlisted%20its%20support%2C%20a%20cross-sectional%20participation%20was%20evidently%20absent.%20Why%20is%20there%20no%20popular%20outcry%20when%20the%20very%20foundational%20principle%20of%20post-ndependent%20India%20is%20in%20tatters%20today%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20what%20is%20discernible%20is%20virtually%20an%20endorsement%20from%20large%20sections%20of%20the%20old%20and%20new%20middle%20classes%2C%20as%20much%20as%20from%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20rich.%20The%20%E2%80%98principal%20carrier%E2%80%99%20of%20this%20%E2%80%98idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20that%20revels%20in%20old%20glories%20drawn%20from%20the%20mythical%20Hindu%20past%20is%20not%20only%20the%20liberal%20mainstream%20of%20Indian%20intellectual%20life%2C%20but%20%E2%80%98extends%20much%20further%20%E2%80%A6%20to%20the%20left%20of%20this%20mainstream%E2%80%99%20(Perry%20Anderson%2C%202015%2C%20p.%209).%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%A6%3Cbr%3E%5CnInstead%20of%20lamenting%20the%20loss%20of%20good%20old%20days%2C%20a%20much%20more%20rewarding%20experience%20would%20be%20to%20excavate%20the%20past%20in%20order%20to%20comprehend%20the%20present.%20What%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20processes%2C%20relics%20and%20forces%20of%20history%20abetted%20the%20rise