%20cap.%20He%20sang%20for%20another%20regional%20film%2C%20this%20time%20in%20Telugu.%20The%20film%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20%3Cem%3EManorama%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1959).%20He%20sang%20three%20songs%20with%20music%20composed%20by%20Ramesh%20Naidu.%20This%20is%20Talat%E2%80%99s%20solo%20song%20in%20the%20film%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Andala%20seema%20sudha%20nilayam%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EEe%20lokame%20Divya%20Prema%20mayam%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(This%20beautiful%20sweet%20abode%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20world%20is%20filled%20with%20divine%20love)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20music%20composer%20Ramesh%20Naidu%20knew%20Talat%20from%20his%20Calcutta%20days%20and%20he%20wanted%20all%20songs%20of%20the%20main%20lead%20sung%20by%20Talat.%20He%20was%20called%20to%20Chennai%20and%20rehearsals%20of%20all%20the%20songs%20would%20happen%20at%20the%20Taj%20Connemara%20Hotel%20where%20Talat%20was%20staying.%20It%20is%20often%20said%20that%20out%20of%20all%20the%20languages%20of%20South%20India%2C%20Telugu%20is%20the%20hardest.%20Despite%20Talat%20not%20knowing%20the%20language%20at%20all%2C%20Naidu%20was%20confident%20of%20his%20ability%20to%20sing%20comfortably%20in%20it.%20After%20all%2C%20he%20had%20witnessed%20how%20Talat%20had%20completely%20blended%20as%20a%20native%20speaker%20while%20singing%20in%20Bengali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20pronunciation%20was%20perfect.%20There%20was%20no%20hint%20of%20any%20non-native%20accent.%20It%20is%20especially%20difficult%20to%20do%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emurki%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(inverted%20mordent%20in%20music)%20on%20the%20right%20word%20to%20evoke%20the%20right%20feeling%2C%20when%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20the%20language.%20But%20he%20sang%20his%20%E2%80%98murki%E2%80%99%20just%20at%20the%20apt%20moment%E2%80%9D%2C%20adds%20his%20co-singer%2C%20P.%20Susheela.%20She%20is%20known%20as%20one%20of%20the%20tallest%20singing%20legends%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20a%20career%20spanning%20six%20decades%20across%20South%20Indian%20cinema.%20She%20has%20sung%20one%20duet%20with%20Talat%20in%20this%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20fortunately%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20speak%20with%20her%2C%20despite%20her%20frail%20condition%20but%20the%20mention%20of%20Talat%20brought%20in%20a%20rush%20of%20fond%20memories%20about%20him.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20ability%20to%20sing%20on%20the%20key%20was%20amazing.%20His%20voice%20never%20wavered%20in%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eshruti%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(musical%20pitches).%20When%20he%20hit%20the%20note%20on%20his%20harmonium%2C%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20differentiate%20his%20voice%20from%20the%20harmonium%20key%20because%20his%20voice%20was%20in%20perfect%20alignment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalat%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EMarachi%20poyevemo%20mayani%20bhasalu%2C%20mankideyo%20sakhi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Did%20you%20forget%20our%20promises%2C%20hard%20to%20get%20over%20o%E2%80%99%20dear)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESusheela%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMarachi%20poradoyi%20cheysina%20vhaasalu%2C%20aashalu%20masina%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Should%20not%20forget%20the%20promises%20made%2C%20even%20if%20hopes%20dwindle)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CHis%20control%20over%20emotions%20was%20remarkable.%20It%20would%20never%20overflow.%20You%20never%20felt%20he%20was%20overtly%20weeping%20or%20wailing%20because%20if%20emotions%20overflow%2C%20the%20listeners%20lose%20touch%20with%20song.%20My%20favourite%20song%20of%20his%20has%20been%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EJaayen%20to%20jaayen%20kahaan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20which%20he%20sang%20in%20absolute%20perfection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalat%E2%80%99s%20personality%20had%20the%20gift%20of%20making%20personal%20connections%20and%20fond%20friendships%20with%20colleagues%20very%20soon.%20People%20would%20feel%20the%20warmth%20of%20his%20affection%20and%20genuine%20care.%20Another%20great%20singer%20of%20that%20time%20from%20the%20South%20Indian%20music%20industry%20was%20P.%20B.%20Sreenivas%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20PBS.%20He%20had%20once%20gone%20to%20visit%20Talat%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Bandra.%20Susheela%20recalls%20how%20PBS%20would%20often%20talk%20about%20that%20evening%20spent%20with%20Talat%20who%20sat%20with%20his%20harmonium%20and%20sang%20Ghazals%20for%20at%20least%20half%20an%20hour%20in%20honour%20of%20his%20visiting%20guest.%20PBS%20was%20mesmerised%20by%20his%20voice%20and%20touched%20by%20the%20gesture.%20He%20believed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20greater%20crooner%20than%20Talat%2C%20he%20was%20a%20natural%20in%20this%20genre%20and%20never%20required%20to%20scream%20out%20any%20emotions.%20Subtlety%20was%20his%20forte.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2050s%20was%20the%20most%20successful%20and%20significant%20decade%20in%20Talat%E2%80%99s%20career.%20The%2050s%20made%20him%20a%20superstar%20singer%20and%20a%20filmstar%20to%20the%20outside%20world%20and%20a%20complete%20family%20man%20at%20home.%20But%20there%20was%20never%20any%20time%20to%20take%20a%20breath%20and%20rest%20on%20some%20laurels.%20Talat%20didn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20in%20that.%20He%20was%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%201960s%20with%20more%20gusto%20and%20fervour.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Frank%20Sinatra%20of%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%201968%2C%20Talat%20received%20an%20invitation%20for%20a%20recording%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20Times%20Square%20at%201481%20Broadway%20Studio.%20But%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20for%20recording%20a%20song.%20He%20had%20been%20invited%20as%20a%20guest%20on%20the%20popular%20talk%20show%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Joe%20Franklin%20Show%E2%80%99.%20The%20channel%20where%20this%20show%20was%20aired%20for%20decades%20was%20called%20WOR-TV%20with%20its%20recording%20studio%20called%20STUDIO-4%2C%20on%20the%20upper%20floor%20of%20the%20art%20deco%20Rialto%20Theatre.%20Nothing%20can%20beat%20the%20historic%20importance%20of%20this%20place%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20charming%20past%20of%20old%20Times%20Square.%20The%20show%20host%20Joe%20Franklin%20is%20credited%20for%20having%20the%20first%20ever%20talk%20show%20and%20was%20a%20pioneer%20in%20inventing%20the%20format%20of%20these%20one-on-one%20chats%20on%20television.%20The%20formula%20he%20created%20was%20about%20a%20curious%20show%20host%20sitting%20behind%20the%20desk%2C%20quizzing%20a%20range%20of%20personalities%20from%20varied%20professional%20fields.%20His%20show%20had%20an%20uninterrupted%20run%20from%201951%20to%201993%2C%20with%20stars%20ranging%20from%20Bing%20Crosby%2C%20Paul%20Newman%2C%20Al%20Pacino%2C%20Barbra%20Streisand%2C%20Michael%20Jackson%20and%20Woody%20Allen%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few.%20His%20envious%20list%20of%20guests%20also%20included%20Andy%20Warhol%2C%20Muhammad%20Ali%20and%20US%20Presidents%20like%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20and%20Richard%20Nixon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20picture%20of%20Talat%20standing%20with%20Franklin%20in%20his%20studio%20set%20with%20a%20background%20of%20abstract%20white%20and%20purple%20Mondrianesque%20triangles%20outlined%20in%20strong%2C%20black%20strokes.%20The%20audience%20immediately%20took%20note%20of%20this%20gentle%20legend%20from%20India%20when%20Franklin%20introduced%20him%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Frank%20Sinatra%20of%20India%E2%80%99.%20This%20was%20a%20comparison%20which%20stuck%20on%20for%20long%2C%20especially%20when%20both%20crooning%20legends%20passed%20away%20barely%20five%20days%20apart%20in%20the%20same%20year%20in%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recording%20time%20of%20this%20episode%20with%20Franklin%20was%20about%20one%20hour%20long.%20His%20studio%20team%20had%20purchased%20a%20record%20of%20Talat%E2%80%99s%20songs%20to%20play%20out%20for%20the%20audience%20in%20between%20the%20interview.%20It%20was%20an%20amazing%20moment%20when%20an%20all%20American%20audience%20watched%20their%20favourite%20talk%20show%20host%20speak%20to%20a%20suave%20singer%20from%20India%2C%20while%20his%20songs%20in%20Urdu%20played%20out%20in%20between%20their%20conversation.%20Talat%20spoke%20about%20his%20music%20journey%20that%20had%20taken%20the%20Asian%20Diaspora%20by%20storm!%20The%20show%20was%20aired%20on%20August%2029%2C%201968.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20America%2C%20Talat%20heard%20about%20a%20new%20concept%20of%20film%20tourism%20that%20had%20gained%20popularity%20in%20the%20U.S.%20This%20was%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Universal%20City%20Studio%20Tours%E2%80%99%20which%20was%20a%20ticketed%20trip%20inside%20the%20Universal%20Studios%20in%20California.%20This%20is%20that%20part%20of%20history%20in%20which%20tourism%20and%20cinema%20were%20linked%20together%20with%20ticket%20sales.%20Universal%20showed%20how%20a%20film%20tourist%20gaze%20can%20bring%20immediate%20commercial%20benefit.%20Actor%2C%20singer%20and%20radio%20artist%20Bob%20Hastings%20used%20to%20be%20a%20regular%20at%20the%20Universal%20Studios.%20It%20was%20one%20such%20day%20that%20Hastings%20found%20out%20about%20a%20big%20star%20visiting%20from%20India.%20He%20was%20eager%20to%20talk%20to%20him%20about%20the%20workings%20of%20showbiz%20in%20India.%20He%20was%20delighted%20to%20know%20that%20Talat%20was%20a%20singer%20too%20and%20shared%20his%20newly%20released%20music%20album%20called%20%E2%80%98Bob%20Hastings%20Sings%20for%20the%20Family%E2%80%99.%20Hastings%20recorded%20an%20impromptu%20chat%20with%20Talat%20about%20his%20career%20and%20some%20pictures%20of%20them%20were%20clicked%20together%20for%20the%20local%20press.%20This%20trip%20to%20the%20U.S.%20worked%20as%20a%20great%20teaser.%20There%20were%20bigger%20concerts%20by%20Talat%20coming%20up%20in%20the%20USA%20and%20UK%20for%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20the%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoyal%20Albert%20Hall%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20unstinting%20love%20and%20accolades%20that%20kept%20Talat%20going.%20Refusing%20to%20rest%20on%20his%20laurels%2C%20he%20was%20still%20on%20the%20move.%20He%20was%20touring%20and%20performing%20and%20winning%20hearts%2C%20gaining%20new%20fans%20across%20the%20globe.%20His%20tour%20to%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20was%20landmark%2C%20just%20like%20the%20United%20States.%20The%20highlight%20of%20this%20tour%20was%20performing%20at%20the%20esteemed%20Royal%20Albert%20Hall%20(RAH)%20in%20London%20in%201979.%20Ever%20since%20its%20launch%20by%20Queen%20Victoria%20in%201871%2C%20it%20has%20remained%20a%20coveted%20venue%20with%20a%20seating%20of%20more%20than%206%2C000.%20Leading%20artists%20of%20different%20genres%20from%20across%20the%20world%20wait%20for%20a%20chance%20to%20be%20approved%20for%20the%20venue%2C%20the%20calendar%20of%20which%20remains%20packed%20every%20year.%20281%20Speeches%20have%20been%20given%20by%20Albert%20Einstein%2C%20events%20by%20boxer%20Muhammad%20Ali%2C%20performances%20by%20Eric%20Clapton%2C%20Pink%20Floyd%2C%20Andrew%20Lloyd%20Webber%E2%80%99s%20Phantom%20of%20the%20Opera%2C%20Beth%20Hart%2C%20Adele%2C%20PlayStation%20music%20concert%2C%2060%20years%20of%20James%20Bond%2C%20Hollywood%20film%20premiers%2C%20awards%20nights%2C%20just%20to%20name%20a%20few%20from%20a%20very%20long%20list%20of%20prestigious%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2027%2C%201979%2C%20as%20Talat%20walked%20down%20the%20maroon-coloured%20carpeted%20and%20circular%20corridor%20backstage%2C%20looking%20at%20all%20the%20framed%20images%20on%20the%20walls%20of%20previous%20performers%2C%20he%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20historicity%20of%20this%20moment.%20It%20is%20a%20dream%20come%20true%20for%20any%20performing%20artist%20worth%20his%2Fher%20salt.%20The%20majestic%20interiors%20of%20the%20amphitheatre%20under%20the%20glass%20dome%20designed%20in%20the%20Italian%20Renaissance%20style%20have%20been%20witness%20to%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20significant%20cultural%20events.%20To%20date%2C%20there%20are%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20Indian%20musicians%20and%20singers%20who%20have%20performed%20at%20the%20RAH.%20Talat%20stepped%20on%20stage%20to%20thunderous%20applause%2C%20waving%20to%20the%20crowd%20which%20was%20occupying%20the%20maroon%20swivel%20seats%20and%20balconies%20with%20little%20arches%20clad%20in%20maroon%20velvet%20curtains.%20All%20of%20this%20grandeur%20was%20placed%20180%20degrees%20around%20the%20singer%20while%20his%20back%20faced%20the%20grand%20pipe%20organ%20in%20the%20hall.%20Talat%20was%20always%20there%20to%20help%20his%20friends%20however%20possible.%20Work%20had%20entirely%20dried%20up%20for%20popular%20comedian%20actor%20Agha.%20Many%20would%20recall%20his%20roles%20in%20old%20films%20like%20Patita%2C%20Jugnu%2C%20etc.%20He%20decided%20to%20take%20Agha%20along%20as%20part%20of%20his%20troupe%20who%20became%20a%20popular%20presenter%20with%20the%20crowd%20for%20all%20his%20shows%20in%20the%20UK.%20After%20being%20introduced%20on%20stage%20by%20actor%20Agha%20as%20the%20King%20of%20Hearts%2C%20Talat%20stepped%20in%20and%20addressed%20the%20audience%20with%20a%20warm%20note%2C%20%E2%80%9CAapse%20mera%20purana%20rishta%20hai.%20Aapke%20saamne%20main%20ghair%20to%20nahin%20hoon.%3Cem%3E%20Aap%20ka%20purana%20gaane%20wala%20hoon%20jisko%20aap%20ne%20hamesha%20pasand%20kiya%20hai%2C%20shukriya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(I%20have%20an%20old%20connection%20with%20you.%20I%20am%20no%20stranger%20to%20you.%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20singer%20familiar%20to%20you%2C%20whom%20you%20have%20always%20liked%2C%20thank%20you).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalat%20gave%20an%20interesting%20insight%20on%20how%20he%20connected%20with%20different%20generations%20through%20his%20stage%20concerts.%20He%20reminisced%20about%20the%20audience%20that%20he%20had%20met%20during%20his%20East%20Africa%20tour%20in%201956.%20After%20their%20forced%20exodus%20from%20Uganda%20and%20Kenya%20under%20the%20Idi%20Amin%20dictatorship%2C%20many%20of%20them%20settled%20in%20the%20UK.%20Many%20children%20who%20were%20part%20of%20his%20audience%20in%20East%20Africa%20were%20today%20attending%20Talat%E2%80%99s%20concert%20at%20the%20RAH%20as%20adults.%20One%20wonders%2C%20could%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20youngest%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Saunak%E2%80%99s%20parents%20have%20been%20in%20this%20audience%3F%20Quite%20possibly%2C%20yes!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20the%20show%20with%20one%20of%20his%20favourite%20songs%20to%20set%20the%20mood%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EHain%20sabse%20madhur%20woh%20geet%20jinhe%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20film%20Patita%20(1953).%20Incredibly%2C%20despite%20all%20his%20film%20songs%20which%20were%20iconic%20hits%20and%20had%20become%20timeless%20classics%20by%20the%201970s%2C%20his%20foremost%20and%20first%20ever%20blockbuster%20of%20his%20career%20was%20a%20non-%20film%20ghazal%20which%20never%20failed%20to%20give%20Talat%20the%20loudest%20claps.%20Talat%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20Ghazal%20was%20released%20in%201944%20and%20it%20still%20sells%20like%20hot%20cakes%20to%20date%E2%80%9D.%20This%20ghazal%20was%20%E2%80%98Tasveer%20teri%20dil%20mera%20behla%20na%20sakegi%E2%80%99.%20The%20audience%20at%20the%20RAH%20wanted%20an%20encore%20after%20the%20ghazal%20but%20Talat%20apologised%20in%20order%20to%20move%20on%20to%20other%20songs.%20The%20restless%20audience%20always%20had%20to%20be%20pacified%20by%20Talat%20that%20their%20%E2%80%98farmaaish%E2%80%99%20(requested%20songs)%20would%20be%20sung%20by%20him%20as%20well%20but%20he%20would%20be%20unable%20to%20accommodate%20an%20encore%20for%20any%20song.%20But%20then%20guess%20what%3F%20The%20persuasive%20audience%20eventually%20got%20their%20way!%20Amidst%20the%20whistles%20and%20claps%2C%20Talat%20repeated%20the%20stanza%20of%20this%20song%20from%20the%20film%20Dil-e-Nadan%20(1953)%2C%20which%20was%20also%20his%20film%20as%20an%20actor%20in%20the%20main%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Bekhata%20tune%20mujh%20se%20khushi%20chheen%20li%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EZinda%20rakha%20magar%20zindagi%20chheen%20li%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EKar%20diya%20dil%20ka%20khun%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EChup%20kahaan%20tak%20rahun%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ESaaf%20kyu%20na%20kahun%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ETu%20khushi%20se%20meri%20dar%20gaya%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EZindagi%20dene%20wale%20sun%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EWhy%20have%20you%20snatched%20away%20my%20happiness%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EI%E2%80%99m%20alive%20but%20breathing%20without%20a%20soul%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EMy%20heart%20swims%20in%20blood%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ETo%20what%20avail%20is%20my%20silence%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EIsn%E2%80%99t%20it%20crystal%20clear%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EYou%20are%20envious%20of%20my%20happiness%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EO%2C%20Giver%20of%20Life%2C%20hear%20me%20out%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20ovation%20for%20him%20thundered%20down%2C%20he%20had%20just%20launched%20the%20musical%20equivalent%20of%20a%20grand%20slam.%20The%20audience%20joined%20in%20with%20a%20fresh%20jolt%20of%20delighted%20cheers.%20In%20the%20alchemy%20that%20a%20great%20performance%20can%20produce%2C%20Talat%20had%20united%20a%20houseful%20of%20strangers%20into%20celebrants%20in%20the%20borderless%20nation%20of%20music.%20His%20final%20song%20for%20the%20evening%20was%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EJhoome%20re%2C%20neela%20ambar%20jhoome%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20the%20film%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EEk%20Gaon%20Ki%20Kahani%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99(1957).%20As%20Talat%20hummed%20away%20the%20last%20line%20of%20this%20peppy%20song%2C%20the%20applause%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop.%20The%20crowd%20cheered%20louder%20for%20an%20encore.%20The%20British%20official%20from%20the%20RAH%20took%20over%20the%20mike%2C%20profusely%20apologising%20to%20the%20audience%20that%20the%20time%20is%20up%2C%20thanking%20Talat%20for%20the%20brilliant%20success%20of%20his%20show.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20tickets%20to%20this%20concert%20were%20entirely%20sold%20out%20two%20weeks%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708176256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17184624%2FFotoJet-5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fwhen-iconic-singer-talat-mahmood-mesmerised-telugu-audience-crowds-at-royal-albert-hall%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sahar%20Zaman's%20latest%20book%20--%20Talat%20Mahmood%3A%20The%20Definitive%20Biography%20--%20explores%20the%20unknown%20facets%20of%20yesteryear%20singer's%20professional%20and%20personal%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fwhen-iconic-singer-talat-mahmood-mesmerised-telugu-audience-crowds-at-royal-albert-hall%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Election%20Commission's%20FAQs%20on%20EVM-VVPATs%20Don't%20Clear%20Cloud%20of%20Suspicion%20Over%20Electoral%20Process%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10211621%2FEffect-2024-02-10T202212.238.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20refused%20to%20grant%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20of%20its%202021%20petition%20about%20a%20host%20of%20matters%20relating%20to%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20One%20of%20the%20major%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20petitioner%20as%20the%20basis%20for%20seeking%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20is%20the%20suitability%20of%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20and%20voter%20verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trail%20(VVPAT)%20units%20for%20ascertaining%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20mandate.%20The%20Bench%20seemed%20visibly%20exasperated%20by%20what%20it%20called%20%E2%80%93%20the%20repeated%20filing%20of%20petitions%20which%20cast%20aspersions%20on%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20layperson%2C%20these%20remarks%20hint%20at%20the%20Bench%E2%80%99s%20faith%20in%20the%20infallibility%20of%20the%20machine-based%20voting%20system%20based%20on%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20(ECI)%20claims%20as%20the%20respondent%20to%20the%20petition.%20A%20few%20weeks%20before%20this%20hearing%20took%20place%2C%20the%20ECI%20had%20released%20a%20revised%20set%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Fevm-faq-new%5C%22%3E100%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Fevm-faq-new%5C%22%3E%20FAQs%3C%2Fa%3E%20(frequently%20asked%20questions)%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20clarifying%20all%20doubts%20about%20these%20electoral%20machines.%20Several%20experts%20have%20commented%20about%20these%20FAQs%20in%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felection-commissions-faqs-on-evms-dont-really-address-major-design-deficiencies%5C%22%3Ecolumns%3C%2Fa%3E%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20upon%20a%20time%2C%20I%20would%20also%20press%20the%20EVM%20button%20(both%20before%20and%20after%20the%20introduction%20of%20VVPATs)%20with%20full%20confidence%20in%20the%20reliability%20and%20infallibility%20of%20the%20electronic%20voting%20system.%20Having%20witnessed%20a%20demonstration%20of%20the%20electronic%20voting%20system%20at%20Nirvachan%20Sadan%2C%20several%20years%20ago%2C%20where%20a%20senior%20officer%20showed%20how%20these%20machines%20work%20and%20what%20fool-proof%20administrative%20measures%20are%20put%20in%20place%20to%20ensure%20their%20safe%20custody%20and%20transport%2C%20before%2C%20during%2C%20and%20after%20parliamentary%20and%20assembly%20elections%2C%20there%20was%20reason%20to%20entertain%20any%20kind%20of%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20this%20is%20what%20the%20ECI%20proudly%20claims%20in%20its%20FAQ%202%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6no%20technical%20knowledge%20is%20required%20for%20casting%20a%20vote%20on%20the%20EVM%20and%20ordinary%20citizens%20can%20easily%20cast%20their%20votes%20on%20ECI%20EVMs%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20public%20education%20campaigns%20the%20ECI%20launches%20prior%20to%20every%20general%20or%20bye-election%20are%20limited%20to%20such%20demonstrations%20only.%20One%20such%20awareness%20drive%20is%20going%20on%20across%20the%20country%20even%20as%20I%20write%20this%20piece.%20We%20are%20expected%20to%20take%20the%20reliability%20of%20EVMs%20as%20an%20article%20of%20faith%20based%20on%20what%20the%20ECI%20shows%20and%20tells%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668180%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20building%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40PIB_INDIA.%20November%205%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20also%20a%20tricky%20thing%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98voters%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20know%E2%80%99%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20discovered%20more%20than%2022%20years%20ago.%20The%20court%20recognised%20every%20voter%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20receive%20information%20about%20the%20educational%20qualifications%2C%20financial%20background%2C%20and%20criminal%20antecedents%2C%20if%20any%2C%20of%20every%20electoral%20candidate%2C%20so%20that%20they%20choose%20wisely%20between%20those%20with%20a%20clean%20and%20tainted%20background.%20Incidentally%2C%20it%20was%20ADR%20that%20had%20moved%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20not%20once%2C%20but%20twice%2C%20to%20have%20this%20right%20read%20into%20Article%2019%20(1)(a)%20of%20the%20constitution%20which%20guarantees%20free%20speech%20and%20expression%20to%20every%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20it%20then%20be%20said%20that%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20know%20is%20limited%20to%20accessing%20details%20about%20the%20public%20character%20of%20electoral%20candidates%20and%20nothing%20more%20relating%20to%20the%20electoral%20process%3F%20Does%20it%20not%20extend%20to%20seeking%20adequate%20knowledge%20about%20the%20current%20voting%20system%20which%20is%20facilitated%20through%20machines%2C%20unlike%20the%20paper-based%20system%20that%20was%20the%20primary%20balloting%20method%20until%20a%20decade%20ago%3F%20Prior%20to%20pressing%20the%20EVM%20button%20of%20choice%2C%20voters%20play%20another%20equally%20important%20role.%20As%20taxpayers%2C%20we%20provide%20the%20funds%20with%20which%20the%20ECI%20buys%20these%20machines.%20So%2C%20these%20machines%20are%20made%20for%20our%20use%20and%20we%20have%20the%20right%20to%20ask%20questions%20to%20resolve%20every%20one%20of%20our%20doubts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20ask%20questions%20about%20these%20machines%20above%20and%20beyond%20what%20the%20ECI%20already%20tells%20us%3F%20A%20comparison%20between%20paper-based%20and%20electronic%20voting%20systems%20will%20reveal%20the%20foundation%20on%20which%20these%20doubts%20start%20to%20crop%20up.%20In%20a%20paper-based%20system%2C%20the%20ECI%20through%20its%20appointed%20functionaries%20gets%20a%20ballot%20paper%20printed%20with%20the%20names%20of%20all%20independent%20and%20political%20party-ticketed%20candidates%20along%20with%20their%20allotted%20symbols.%20All%20that%20the%20registered%20voter%20%E2%80%93%20literate%20and%20unlettered%2C%20both%20%E2%80%93%20had%20to%20do%20was%20simply%20take%20a%20ballot%20paper%20and%20a%20rubber%20stamp%20from%20the%20Presiding%20Officer%2C%20go%20to%20the%20polling%20booth%2C%20stamp%20the%20cross%20mark%20against%20the%20preferred%20candidate%20and%20drop%20it%20in%20the%20ballot%20box%20oneself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ballot%20paper%20was%20even%20pre-folded%20while%20being%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20voter.%20The%20voter%20was%20able%20to%20see%20every%20step%20of%20this%20action%20sequence%20with%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20eyes%20or%20with%20the%20help%20of%20an%20assistant%20if%20the%20person%20was%20blind.%20On%20counting%20day%2C%20the%20counting%20agents%20of%20candidates%20could%20see%20every%20ballot%20paper%20%E2%80%93%20both%20valid%20and%20invalid%20%E2%80%93%20while%20it%20was%20being%20counted%20before%20the%20results%20were%20announced.%20Nothing%20was%20hidden%20from%20the%20naked%20eye%20(with%20or%20without%20prescription%20glasses)%20as%20everything%20except%20the%20recording%20of%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20choice%20on%20the%20ballot%20was%20clearly%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20contrast%20this%20with%20the%20electronic%20voting%20system.%20There%20is%20a%20Ballot%20Unit%20(BU)%20with%20the%20names%20of%20candidates%20displayed%20on%20a%20printed%20label%20affixed%20on%20top%20of%20it.%20The%20voter%20presses%20the%20button%20next%20to%20the%20name%20and%20symbol%20of%20the%20preferred%20candidate%20in%20the%20polling%20booth%20and%20after%20it%20beeps%20something%20happens%20(we%20will%20explain%20below%20why%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20say%20anything%20more%20specific%20than%20this).%20Then%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20gets%20into%20action%20and%20prints%20out%20a%20slip%20which%20is%20visible%20to%20the%20voter%20for%20seven%20seconds%20through%20an%20illuminated%20window.%20This%20slip%20contains%20the%20name%2C%20serial%20number%20and%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidate%20in%20favour%20of%20whom%20the%20voter%20pressed%20the%20button.%20Then%20it%20automatically%20gets%20cut%20and%20falls%20down%20into%20the%20VVPAT%E2%80%99s%20drop%20box%20and%20the%20light%20is%20turned%20off.%20Next%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98loud%20beep%20is%20heard%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20according%20to%20the%20ECI%2C%20completes%20the%20action%20sequence%20of%20voting%20from%20casting%20to%20its%20registration%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo.%20Only%20one%20stage%20of%20this%20process%20is%20visible%20to%20the%20voter%2C%20namely%2C%20the%20printed%20VVPAT%20slip%2C%20to%20satisfy%20oneself%20that%20the%20vote%20has%20been%20printed%20as%20per%20one%E2%80%99s%20choice.%20What%20gets%20recorded%20on%20the%20Control%20Unit%20(CU)%20is%20not%20visible%20at%20all%2C%20the%20voter%20has%20to%20be%20satisfied%20by%20the%20mere%20sound%20of%20a%20beep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20counting%20day%2C%20only%20the%20CUs%20are%20brought%20to%20the%20counting%20hall%20and%20the%20tally%20of%20votes%20is%20calculated%20by%20pressing%20the%20relevant%20button%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20candidates.%20Only%20the%20serial%20numbers%2C%20not%20the%20names%20of%20the%20candidates%20are%20visible%20on%20the%20CU.%20Further%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directives%2C%20VVPAT%20slips%20are%20counted%20from%20only%20five%20randomly%20selected%20units%20in%20Assembly%20elections.%20For%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%20five%20units%20are%20chosen%20randomly%20from%20the%20Assembly%20segments%20of%20the%20constituency%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20tallying%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20count%20with%20the%20candidate-wise%20totals%20that%20the%20CU%20calculates.%20This%20random%20selection%20process%20is%20not%20visible%20to%20the%20counting%20agents%20(having%20served%20as%20a%20counting%20agent%20to%20an%20independent%20candidate%20in%20the%202020%20Delhi%20assembly%20elections%2C%20I%20know%20this%20for%20a%20fact).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20the%20transition%20is%20made%20from%20the%20starkly%20visual%20attributes%20of%20a%20paper-based%20voting%20and%20counting%20system%20to%20the%20present%20machine-mediated%20system%20(with%20only%20two%20very%20limited%20visual%20and%20even%20shorter%20audio%20feedback-%20beep!%20beep!%20Beep!)%2C%20the%20ECI%20has%20a%20more%20onerous%20duty%20of%20transparency%20towards%20the%20electorate.%20Convincing%20the%20voter%20places%20a%20much%20higher%20burden%20of%20proof%20than%20what%20the%20ECI%20is%20currently%20willing%20to%20discharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20answers%20to%20several%20of%20the%20100%20FAQs%20do%20not%20satisfactorily%20discharge%20this%20burden.%20Let%20us%20start%20with%20the%20most%20basic%20FAQs%20where%20the%20ECI%20has%20tried%20to%20explain%20how%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo%20works%2C%20internally.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20FAQs%20relating%20to%20signal%20flow%20(FAQs%20%232%2C%2039%2C%20and%2086)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20response%20to%20FAQ%20%232-%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIn%20what%20way%20functioning%20of%20EVMs%20is%20different%20from%20conventional%20voting%20through%20paper%20ballots%3F%20Whether%20technical%20knowledge%20is%20required%20for%20casting%20vote%20through%20the%20EVM%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20ECI%20explains%20the%20process%20of%20electronic%20voting%20that%20I%20have%20summarised%20above%20and%20says%20that%20it%20is%20better%20than%20a%20paper%20ballot-based%20system%20which%20had%20problems%20like%20improper%20marking%20or%20smudging%20of%20ink.%20Further%2C%20the%20ECI%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EWhen%20the%20voter%20presses%20a%20button%20against%20the%20candidate%20of%20his%2Fher%20choice%20on%20Ballot%20Unit%2C%20a%20red%20LED%20glows%20against%20the%20chosen%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20button%20on%20BU.%20A%20paper%20slip%20showing%20the%20serial%20number%2C%20name%20and%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidate%20of%20his%2Fher%20choice%20is%20generated%20and%20is%20visible%20for%20about%207%20seconds%20through%20transparent%20window%20of%20VVPAT.%20Hence%20the%20voter%20is%20able%20to%20see%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprinted%20slip%E2%80%9D%20and%20verify%20that%20vote%20is%20cast%20as%20per%20his%2Fher%20choice.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20printed%20paper%20slip%20gets%20cut%20automatically%20and%20stored%20in%20sealed%20Drop%20box%20of%20VVPAT.%20A%20%3Cu%3Eloud%20BEEP%20is%20heard%20from%20the%20Control%20Unit%20which%20confirms%20that%20the%20vote%20is%20registered%20successfully%3C%2Fu%3E.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20FAQ%20%2339%20in%20response%20to%20the%20query-%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIs%20it%20possible%20to%20vote%20more%20than%20once%20on%20an%20EVM%20by%20pressing%20the%20button%20again%20and%20again%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20explanation%20(reproduced%20below)%20about%20how%20the%20EVM%20behaves%20is%20at%20complete%20variance%20with%20the%20explanation%20given%20against%20FAQ%20%232%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ENo%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20vote%20more%20than%20once%20on%20an%20ECI-EVM%20by%20a%20particular%20voter.%20As%20soon%20as%20a%20particular%20button%20on%20the%20Ballot%20Unit%20is%20pressed%2C%20the%20vote%20is%20recorded%20for%20that%20particular%20candidate%20and%20a%20loud%20beep%20is%20emitted%20for%20officials%20and%20election%20agents%20to%20note%20that%20the%20vote%20%3Cu%3Ehas%20been%20completed%3C%2Fu%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20the%20complete%20absence%20of%20any%20reference%20to%20the%20VVPAT%20stage%20of%20the%20voting%20process%20in%20this%20reply.%20Those%20with%20unshakeable%20faith%20in%20the%20electronic%20voting%20system%20may%20claim%20this%20is%20just%20a%20legacy%20response%20from%20the%20times%20when%20EVMs%20were%20not%20paired%20with%20VVPATs%20at%20all%20and%20it%20must%20not%20be%20seen%20in%20isolation%20from%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20reply%20to%20FAQ%20%232.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20deployment%20of%20VVPAT%20units%20became%20mandatory%20only%20after%20the%202013%20directive%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20%3Cem%3EDr.%20Subramanian%20Swamy%20vs%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Let%20us%20accept%20that%20reasoning%20temporarily%20and%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFAQ%20%2386%20is%20a%20recent%20addition%20(January%202024)%2C%20not%20found%20in%20the%20much%20shorter%20FAQs%20list%20the%20ECI%20released%20in%20August%202023.%20The%20query%20is%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EHow%20does%20signal%2Fcommand%20flow%20between%20various%20units%20of%20EVM%20viz.%20BU%2C%20CU%20and%20VVPAT%3F%20Since%20the%20VVPAT%20is%20kept%20along%20with%20BU%20inside%20the%20voting%20compartment%20of%20the%20voter%2C%20does%20VVPAT%20receive%20any%20signal%2Fcommand%20from%20BU%20and%20vice-versa%3F%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3ETo%20this%2C%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20elaborate%20reply%20is%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIn%20M3%20EVMs%2C%20CU%20always%20acts%20as%20Master%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20position%20in%20which%20it%20is%20placed%20or%20connected.%20BU%20and%20VVPAT%20act%20as%20Slave%20units%20in%20the%20connected%20network%2C%20which%20receive%20commands%20from%20CU%20to%20act%20as%20per%20the%20application%20programme.%20%3Cu%3EBU%20and%20VVPAT%20do%20not%20communicate%20with%20each%20other.%20It%20is%20the%20CU%20that%20communicates%20with%20both%20the%20BU%20and%20VVPAT%3C%2Fu%3E.%20%3Cu%3EWhen%20a%20voter%20presses%20a%20candidate%20button%20on%20BU%2C%20the%20BU%20sends%20the%20button%20number%20to%20CU%20and%20in%20turn%2C%20the%20CU%20communicates%20to%20VVPAT%20to%20print%20the%20slip%20of%20the%20corresponding%20button%20number%3C%2Fu%3E.%20%3Cu%3EOnly%20after%20printing%20and%20cutting%20of%20the%20printed%20VVPAT%20slip%2C%20the%20CU%20registers%20the%20vote%3C%2Fu%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EVotes%20are%20recorded%20only%20in%20CUs%20and%20not%20in%20BUs%20or%20VVPATs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E.%20When%20a%20particular%20Candidate%E2%80%99s%20button%20in%20BU%20is%20pressed%20by%20the%20voters%2C%20BU%20sends%20the%20button%20number%20to%20CU%20and%20CU%20commands%20printing%20of%20slip%20related%20to%20that%20button%20number%20to%20VVPAT.%20The%20VVPAT%20slip%20so%20printed%20remains%20visible%20to%20the%20voters%20for%20about%20seven%20seconds%20to%20verify%20their%20votes%20cast%20through%20the%20VVPAT%20display%20window.%20VVPAT%20then%20sends%20an%20acknowledgment%20to%20the%20CU%20to%20mark%20completion%20of%20printing%20of%20slip.%20The%20CU%20then%20initiates%20the%20cut%20of%20the%20printed%20slip%20and%20the%20slip%20falls%20in%20the%20sealed%20drop%20box%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20(Rules%2049A%20and%2049M%2C%20The%20Conduct%20of%20Elections%20Rules%2C%201961).%20After%20the%20successful%20completion%20of%20all%20these%20steps%2C%20i.e.%20printing%20and%20cutting%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20slips%2C%20the%20VVPAT%20sends%20an%20acknowledgement%20to%20the%20CU.%20Upon%20receiving%20the%20message%20from%20VVPAT%2C%20the%20CU%20records%20the%20vote%20electronically%20and%20emits%20a%20long%20BEEP.%20The%20BEEP%20marks%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20voting%20process%20for%20the%20voter.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20M3%20model%2C%20Master-Slave%20bus%20architecture%20is%20used.%20%3Cu%3EVVPAT%20can%20be%20connected%20anywhere%20in%20the%20EVM%20M3%20bus%3C%2Fu%3E.%20The%20Control%20Unit%20(CU)%20implements%20communication%2C%20command%20processing%2C%20handling%20of%20key%20operations%20and%20handling%20of%20all%20the%20commands%2Fresponses%20to%2Ffrom%20BU%20and%20VVPAT.%20The%20Master-Slave%20protocol%20is%20used%20to%20control%20access%20to%20the%20communication%20bus.%20Communication%20on%20the%20bus%20is%20initiated%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9CMaster%E2%80%9D%20(CU)%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9CCommand%E2%80%9D%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9CSlave%E2%80%9D%20(BU%20%26amp%3B%20VVPAT).%20%3Cu%3EThe%20%E2%80%9CSlave%E2%80%9D%20which%20is%20constantly%20monitoring%20the%20bus%20for%20%E2%80%9CCommands%E2%80%9D%20will%20recognize%20only%20the%20%E2%80%9CCommands%E2%80%9D%20addressed%20to%20it%20and%20will%20respond%20by%20performing%20an%20action%20and%20by%20returning%20a%20%E2%80%9CResponse%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fu%3E.%20Only%20the%20Master%20can%20initiate%20a%20command.%20%3Cu%3ECU%20is%20always%20the%20Master%20in%20the%20ECI%20M3%20EVM%20system%20setup.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20to%20FAQ%20%2386%20ends%20with%20a%20signal%20flow%20schematic%20and%20suggests%20that%20readers%20refer%20to%20Annexure-I%20as%20well%20for%20further%20clarity.%20Annexure-I%20contains%20a%20signal%20flow%20diagram%20(see%20%3Cem%3EImages%201%20%26amp%3B%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20below)%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20475px)%2085vw%2C%20475px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165011%2FImage-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22475%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165011%2FImage-1.jpg%20475w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165011%2FImage-1-300x220.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697650%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22349%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%201%3A%20Signal%20flow%20schematic%20under%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20answer%20to%20FAQ%20%2386%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165126%2Fimage-2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22716%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165126%2Fimage-2.png%20716w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165126%2Fimage-2-300x163.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697651%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22388%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%202%3A%20Signal%20flow%20diagram%20at%20Annexure-I%20to%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20FAQs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EII.%20What%20is%20problematic%20with%20these%20answers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20common%20knowledge%20that%20only%20two%20Union%20Government-owned%20public%20sector%20undertakings%20(CPSUs)%20namely%2C%20BEL%20(under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence)%20and%20ECIL%20(under%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy)%20have%20been%20manufacturing%20the%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs.%20According%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20answer%20to%20FAQ%20%237%20they%20have%20a%20duopoly%20on%20the%20supply%20of%20these%20machines%20for%20parliamentary%20and%20assembly%20elections.%20However%2C%20few%20people%20know%20two%20related%20facts%20which%20the%20ECI%20has%20not%20bothered%20to%20mention%20in%20any%20of%20its%20FAQs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20in%202001%2C%20both%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20applied%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20exclusive%20patent%20rights%20under%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Patents%20Act%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3E1970%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20claiming%20that%20their%20EVMs%20are%20their%20unique%20invention%2Finnovation%20markedly%20different%20from%20the%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20that%20were%20in%20use%20in%20other%20countries.%20After%20due%20examination%20of%20their%20claims%20the%20Patent%20Office%2C%20Chennai%20granted%20patent%20rights%20to%20both%20CPSUs%20in%202006%20for%20a%20period%20of%2020%20years%20%E2%80%93%20the%20maximum%20duration%20permissible%20under%20the%20law.%20These%20patents%20expired%20in%202021%20(as%20per%20law%20the%2020-year%20period%20is%20calculated%20from%20the%20date%20of%20the%20patent%20application%20and%20not%20the%20date%20of%20the%20order%20granting%20the%20patent).%20How%20is%20exclusivity%20being%20maintained%20by%20the%20two%20CPSUs%20after%20the%20lapse%20of%20the%20EVM%20patents%20is%20a%20mystery%20because%20there%20is%20no%20provision%20in%20the%20patents%20law%20for%20extending%20the%20validity%20of%20a%20patent%20beyond%2020%20years%20(evergreening%20of%20a%20patent%20is%20not%20permitted%20under%20our%20law).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20patent-related%20documents%20are%20required%20to%20be%20publicly%20accessible%20to%20any%20person%20by%20law%2C%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Controller%20General%20of%20Patents%2C%20Designs%20and%20Trademarks%20under%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20publishes%20all%20documents%20from%20the%20application%20stage%20to%20the%20stage%20of%20grant%20of%20the%20patent%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fipindia.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3Ededicated%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20patent%20application%2C%20complete%20specifications%20of%20and%20claims%20related%20to%20the%20invention%2Finnovation%20(what%20it%20is%20capable%20of%20doing%20and%20how)%20for%20which%20an%20applicant%20is%20seeking%20the%20patent%2C%20the%20drawings%20which%20visually%20portray%20the%20looks%20of%20the%20invention%2C%20corporate%20data%20about%20the%20applicant%20entity%2C%20details%20of%20the%20patent%20agent%20through%20whom%20the%20applicant%20interacts%20with%20the%20Patent%20Office%2C%20the%20report%20of%20the%20examiner%20who%20studies%20the%20claims%20and%20any%20amendments%20to%20the%20original%20documents%20submitted%20by%20the%20applicant%20etc.%20are%20all%20available%20through%20a%20very%20utilitarian%20database.%20If%20the%20patent%20is%20granted%20that%20order%20is%20also%20uploaded%20on%20this%20database%20along%20with%20a%20copy%20of%20its%20communication%20to%20the%20applicant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20transparency%20is%20an%20essential%20to%20enable%20any%20person%20to%20file%20an%20objection%20against%20the%20patent%20application%20or%20claim%20on%20the%20grounds%20permissible%20under%20the%20%3Cem%3EPatents%20Act%3C%2Fem%3E.%20If%20the%20objection%20is%20upheld%2C%20the%20patent%20application%20will%20be%20rejected.%20EVM%20patent-related%20documents%20continue%20to%20be%20accessible%20on%20this%20database%20despite%20the%20expiry%20of%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20patents.%20After%20the%20successful%20completion%20of%20the%20application%20process%2C%20the%20patent%20holder%20may%20deploy%20his%2Fher%2Ftheir%20invention%2Finnovation%20exclusively%20for%20commercial%20use%20unless%20he%2Fshe%2Fit%20voluntarily%20grants%20a%20license%20to%20any%20other%20entity%20for%20a%20similar%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20only%20BEL%20applied%20for%20a%20patent%20for%20the%20VVPAT%20machine%20in%20March%202018%20and%20received%20the%20patent%20order%20from%20the%20Chennai%20Patent%20Office%20in%20May%202022%20(after%20the%20completion%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections).%20To%20the%20best%20of%20my%20knowledge%2C%20ECIL%E2%80%99s%20patent%20application%20for%20a%20VVPAT%20machine%20is%20not%20available%20on%20this%20database%2C%20so%20it%20may%20be%20presumed%20that%20there%20is%20some%20working%20arrangement%20between%20the%20two%20CPSUs%20for%20manufacturing%20the%20VVPAT%20machines.%20All%20the%20aforementioned%20documents%20and%20many%20more%20relating%20to%20the%20VVPAT%20patent%20which%20BEL%20secured%20are%20downloadable%20free%20of%20charge%20from%20this%20database%20(no%20you%20do%20not%20need%20an%20RTI%20application%20to%20seek%20access%20to%20these%20documents!).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20extract%20from%20the%20detailed%20drawings%20BEL%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patent%20Office%20in%20March%202019%20which%20shows%20the%20backend%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20machine%20is%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165428%2Fimage-3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165428%2Fimage-3.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165428%2Fimage-3-300x255.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165428%2Fimage-3-1024x871.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697653%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221021%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%203%3A%20Backend%20view%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20as%20per%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20drawing%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patent%20Office%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20above%20image%20clearly%20shows%20two%20ports%20that%20permit%20connection%20of%20the%20CU%20and%20BU%20units%20of%20the%20EVM%20to%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%E2%80%99s%20backend.%20In%20the%20early%20versions%20of%20VVPAT%20machines%2C%20there%20were%20two%20units-%20a%20printer%20that%20printed%20the%20choice%20of%20the%20voter%20on%20paper%20slips%20and%20the%20VSDU%20(visual%20status%20display%20unit)%20which%20would%20display%20the%20functional%20status%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20especially%20any%20errors%20detected%20in%20the%20printer.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20ECI%E2%80%99s%202018%20Status%20Paper%20on%20EVMs%2C%20in%20M3%20model%20of%20EVMs%20(which%20are%20currently%20in%20use%20all%20over%20the%20country)%2C%20VSDUs%20were%20integrated%20into%20the%20CU%20itself.%20This%20version%20of%20the%20EVM%20Manual%20has%20been%20replaced%20with%20subsequent%20versions%20and%20is%20unfortunately%20no%20longer%20displayed%20on%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20website.%20As%20I%20happened%20to%20download%20a%20copy%20in%202018%20itself%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20cite%20from%20this%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20according%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feci.gov.in%2Ffiles%2Ffile%2F13911-manual-on-electronic-voting-machine-and-vvpat-edition-7-december-2022%2F%5C%22%3Elatest%20Manual%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%2C%20engineers%20of%20the%20two%20CPSUs%20who%20are%20tasked%20with%20the%20job%20of%20candidate-setting%20are%20instructed%20to%20connect%20the%20VVPAT%20with%20CU%20and%20BU%20with%20separate%20cables%20for%20this%20purpose%20(see%20%3Cem%3EImage%204%3C%2Fem%3E%20below).%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fcoochbehar.nic.in%2FAElection2021%2FTrainingModules%2FonEVMnVVPAT_tillDC.pdf%5C%22%3EBEL%E2%80%99s%20MSPPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20says%20that%20in%20order%20to%20commission%20the%20VVPAT%20it%20must%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20CU%20and%20BU%20individually%20(see%20%3Cem%3EImage%205%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebelow).%20So%2C%20there%20is%20no%20cable%20connection%20between%20the%20CU%20and%20BU%20at%20all.%20All%20communication%20is%20mediated%20through%20the%20bus%20architecture%20which%20is%20physically%20housed%20in%20the%20VVPAT%20unit.%20This%20is%20the%20inevitable%20and%20logical%20conclusion%20that%20one%20arrives%20at%20based%20on%20the%20information%20contained%20in%20the%20drawings%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20and%20the%20instructions%20of%20ECI%20and%20BEL%20mentioned%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165537%2FImage-4.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22908%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165537%2FImage-4.jpg%20908w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165537%2FImage-4-227x300.jpg%20227w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165537%2FImage-4-775x1024.jpg%20775w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697654%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165918%2FImage-5.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165918%2FImage-5.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165918%2FImage-5-300x208.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165918%2FImage-5-1024x710.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22832%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%204%20%26amp%3B%205%3A%20Instructions%20for%20Engineers%20for%20candidate-setting%20in%20VVPATs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20logical%20conclusion%2C%20what%20do%20we%20make%20of%20this%20portion%20of%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20answer%20to%20FAQ%20%2386%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%3Cem%3EBU%20and%20VVPAT%20do%20not%20communicate%20with%20each%20other.%20It%20is%20the%20CU%20that%20communicates%20with%20both%20the%20BU%20and%20VVPAT.%20When%20a%20voter%20presses%20a%20candidate%20button%20on%20BU%2C%20the%20BU%20sends%20the%20button%20number%20to%20CU%20and%20in%20turn%2C%20the%20CU%20communicates%20to%20VVPAT%20to%20print%20the%20slip%20of%20the%20corresponding%20button%20number.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20then%20do%20the%20BU%20and%20CU%20communicate%20with%20each%20other%20when%20both%20are%20required%20to%20be%20connected%20only%20to%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20and%20not%20to%20each%20other%3F%20Is%20the%20%E2%80%98bus%20architecture%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20something%20like%20the%20bypass%20routes%20that%20are%20constructed%20on%20National%20Highways%20(like%20Agra%20bypass%2C%20Lucknow%20bypass%2C%20Chennai%20bypass%20etc.)%20to%20skirt%20around%20major%20cities%20and%20towns%20and%20travel%20faster%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20destination%3F%20After%20the%20voter%20presses%20the%20button%20of%20choice%20on%20the%20BU%20is%20that%20signal%20somehow%20flowing%20to%20the%20CU%20unbeknownst%20to%20the%20VVPAT%20even%20though%20this%20communication%20is%20happening%20between%20the%20two%20units%20on%20the%20real%20estate%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%3F%20The%20ECI%20ought%20to%20explain%20how%20this%20magical%20signal%20flow%20takes%20place%20to%20lay%20voters%20like%20me%20who%20are%20neither%20hardware%20nor%20software%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20ending%20this%20writeup%2C%20another%20element%20of%20the%20answer%20to%20FAQs%20%232%20and%20%2386%20deserve%20critical%20examination.%20In%20response%20to%20FAQ%20%232%20the%20ECI%20says%2C%20after%20the%20voter%20presses%20the%20button%20of%20choice%20on%20the%20BU%2C%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20gets%20into%20action%2C%20prints%20the%20slip%2C%20turns%20its%20light%20on%20for%20the%20voter%20to%20see%20and%20verify%20that%20his%2Fher%20choice%20has%20been%20correctly%20printed%2C%20cuts%20it%20and%20drops%20it%20into%20the%20drop%20box%20before%20switching%20the%20light%20off.%20Then%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ea%20loud%20BEEP%20is%20heard%20from%20the%20Control%20Unit%20which%20confirms%20that%20the%20vote%20is%20registered%20successfully%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20In%20response%20to%20FAQ%20%2386%2C%20the%20ECI%20explains%20how%20the%20CU%20is%20the%20Master%20and%20the%20BU%20and%20VVPATs%20are%20Slave%20units%20which%20receive%20commands%20from%20CU%20to%20act%20as%20per%20the%20application%20programme.%20Further%20the%20explanation%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%3Cem%3EThe%20Master-Slave%20protocol%20is%20used%20to%20control%20access%20to%20the%20communication%20bus.%20Communication%20on%20the%20bus%20is%20initiated%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9CMaster%E2%80%9D%20(CU)%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9CCommand%E2%80%9D%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9CSlave%E2%80%9D%20(BU%20%26amp%3B%20VVPAT).%20%3Cu%3EThe%20%E2%80%9CSlave%E2%80%9D%20which%20is%20constantly%20monitoring%20the%20bus%20for%20%E2%80%9CCommands%E2%80%9D%20will%20recognize%20only%20the%20%E2%80%9CCommands%E2%80%9D%20addressed%20to%20it%20and%20will%20respond%20by%20performing%20an%20action%20and%20by%20returning%20a%20%E2%80%9CResponse%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fu%3E.%20Only%20the%20Master%20can%20initiate%20a%20command.%20%3Cu%3ECU%20is%20always%20the%20Master%20in%20the%20ECI%20M3%20EVM%20system%20setup.%3C%2Fu%3E%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20is%20the%20set%20protocol%2C%20what%20do%20we%20make%20of%20these%20assertions%20of%20BEL%20before%20the%20Patents%20Office%3F%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%5B0030%5D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20an%20aspect%2C%20%3Cu%3Ethe%20apparatus%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cu%3E%5BVVPAT%5D%20%3Cem%3Ecan%20be%20functionally%20or%20physically%20integrated%20with%20the%20ballot%20unit%20of%20EVM%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20the%20physical%20artefact%20of%20which%20provides%20the%20functionality%20of%20both%20the%20units.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%5B0031%5D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20an%20aspect%2C%20%3Cu%3Ethe%20apparatus%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cu%3E%5BVVPAT%5D%20%3Cem%3Ecan%20be%20functionally%20or%20physically%20integrated%20as%20a%20single%20unit%20providing%20functionality%20of%20VVPAT%2C%20control%20unit%20and%20ballot%20unit%20of%20EVM%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%5B00120%5D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20an%20aspect%2C%20%3Cu%3Eif%20the%20printing%20is%20not%20successful%20for%20any%20reason%2C%20then%20the%20vote%20cast%20cannot%20be%20stored%3C%2Fu%3E%2C%20and%20the%20VVPAT%20system%20can%20be%20put%20in%20an%20error%20mode%20and%20prevented%20from%20further%20use%20in%20the%20election%20process.%20This%20ensures%20number%20of%20votes%20stored%20in%20the%20CU%20and%20the%20number%20of%20slips%20in%20the%20VVPAT%20is%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%5B00125%5D%20In%20an%20aspect%2C%20proposed%20system%20%5BVVPAT%5D%20can%2C%20after%20successful%20printing%2C%20displaying%20and%20storing%20a%20ballot%20slip%20can%20%3Cu%3Esend%20an%20acknowledgement%20of%20successful%20operation%20to%20the%20corresponding%20EVM%3C%2Fu%3E.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParagraphs%20%230030%20and%200031%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Complete%20Specifications%20submitted%20while%20seeking%20grant%20of%20a%20patent%20and%20paragraphs%20%2300120%20and%2000125%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Detailed%20description%20of%20the%20VVPAT-related%20drawings%20attached%20to%20these%20Complete%20Specifications%20(see%20%3Cem%3EImages%206%2C%207%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%20%26amp%3B%208%3C%2Fem%3E%20below).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20BEL%20claimed%20before%20the%20Patents%20Office%20that%20the%20VVPAT%20can%20be%20integrated%20with%20the%20BU%20physically%20and%20not%20the%20CU%20(as%20is%20the%20case%20from%20the%20evidence%20presented%20above).%20Second%2C%20even%20though%20according%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20reply%20to%20FAQ%20%2386%20the%20CU%20is%20initially%20aware%20of%20the%20choice%20made%20by%20the%20voter%2C%20according%20to%20BEL%20it%20can%20record%20the%20same%20only%20if%20the%20printing%20process%20is%20successful.%20If%20the%20printing%20process%20is%20unsuccessful%2C%20the%20CU%20cannot%20record%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20choice%20even%20if%20it%20somehow%20had%20prior%20knowledge%20of%20the%20same.%20In%20this%20respect%20at%20least%2C%20the%20VVPAT%20must%20be%20seen%20as%20acting%20like%20a%20Master%20and%20the%20CU%20as%20a%20Slave%20which%20records%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20choice%20digitally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170054%2FImage-6.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22849%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170054%2FImage-6.jpg%20849w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170054%2FImage-6-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170054%2FImage-6-724x1024.jpg%20724w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697656%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170238%2FImage-8-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22849%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170238%2FImage-8-1.jpg%20849w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170238%2FImage-8-1-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170238%2FImage-8-1-724x1024.jpg%20724w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697659%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%206%3A%20Extract%20from%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20Complete%20Specifications%20of%20VVPAT%20machine%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170153%2FImage-8.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22849%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170153%2FImage-8.jpg%20849w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170153%2FImage-8-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170153%2FImage-8-724x1024.jpg%20724w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697658%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%207%3A%20Extracts%20from%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20Complete%20Specifications%20of%20VVPAT%20machine%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170120%2FImage-7.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22849%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170120%2FImage-7.jpg%20849w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170120%2FImage-7-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170120%2FImage-7-724x1024.jpg%20724w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%208%3A%20Extract%20from%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20Complete%20Specifications%20of%20VVPAT%20machine%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20is%20the%20vote%20that%20must%20be%20counted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReaders%2C%20wearied%20by%20all%20these%20technical%20details%2C%20may%20ask-%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20is%20the%20point%20of%20all%20this%20argumentation%20and%20evidence-splashing%3F%E2%80%9D%20Well%2C%20the%20point%20is%20very%20simple%20and%20goes%20to%20the%20very%20heart%20of%20the%20demand%20made%20by%20several%20opposition%20political%20parties%20and%20civil%20society%20groups%20like%20the%20Citizens%20Commission%20on%20Elections%20(CCE)-%20all%20VVPAT%20slips%20must%20be%20counted%20rather%20than%20a%20small%20sample%20of%20five%20randomly%20chosen%20VVPAT%20units%20which%20the%20ECI%20has%20defended%20to%20be%20scientifically%20of%20adequate%20size%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20in%20its%20reply%20to%20FAQ%20%2362.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20electronic%20voting%20which%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvote%E2%80%9D%20that%20must%20be%20counted%20on%20counting%20day%20after%20polling%20is%20over-%20is%20it%20the%20candidates%E2%80%99%20tally%20of%20votes%20as%20calculated%20by%20the%20CU%20or%20the%20VVPAT%20slips%20which%20the%20voters%20see%20and%20verify%20to%20their%20satisfaction%3F%20This%20is%20the%20question%20that%20many%20opposition%20leaders%20and%20CCE%20have%20posed%20to%20the%20ECI.%20ECI%20deals%20with%20this%20issue%20at%20FAQ%20%2363%20in%20this%20manner%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CQ63.%20The%20ECI%20has%20to%20define%20which%20one%20is%20true%20representation%20of%20the%20will%20of%20the%20voter%3F%20Vote%20recorded%20on%20Control%20Unit%20or%20voter%20verified%20SLIP%20in%20VVPAT%3F%20If%20Counting%20is%20based%20on%20the%20Control%20Unit%20count%20what%20is%20the%20use%20of%20Verifiable%20paper%20SLIP%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EAns.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20system%20of%20VVPAT%20has%20been%20introduced%20only%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20greater%20transparency%20and%20enhancing%20the%20confidence%20of%20voters%20by%20way%20of%20immediate%20verification%20of%20the%20printed%20ballot%20slip%20having%20the%20chosen%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20Name%2C%20Serial%20Number%20and%20Symbol%20and%20recording%20of%20vote%20in%20the%20Control%20Unit.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20per%20existing%20legislation%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3ERule%2056C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eof%20the%20Conduct%20of%20Elections%20(Amendment)%20Rules%20clearly%20states%20that%20after%20the%20returning%20officer%20is%20satisfied%20that%20a%20voting%20machine%20has%20not%20been%20tampered%20with%2C%20he%20shall%20have%20the%20votes%20counted%20by%20pressing%20the%20appropriate%20button%20marked%20%E2%80%9CResult%E2%80%9D%20provided%20in%20the%20control%20unit%20whereby%20the%20total%20votes%20polled%20and%20votes%20polled%20by%20each%20candidate%20shall%20be%20displayed%20in%20respect%20of%20each%20candidate%20on%20the%20display%20panel%20provided%20for%20the%20purpose%20in%20the%20unit.%20The%20candidate%20wise%20result%20so%20obtained%20from%20all%20control%20units%20used%20in%20the%20election%20is%20to%20be%20tabulated%20in%20a%20result%20sheet%20in%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EForm%2020%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eand%20the%20particulars%20so%20entered%20in%20the%20result%20sheet%20announced.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EContesting%20candidates%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20request%20for%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20count%20under%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3ERule%2056D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eof%20the%20Conduct%20of%20Elections%20Rules%2C%201961%20after%20completion%20of%20counting%20of%20votes%20from%20the%20EVMs.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3ERule%2056D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E(4)%20(b)%20clearly%20states%20that%20in%20case%20of%20a%20discrepancy%20between%20the%20Electronic%20Count%20in%20the%20Control%20Unit%20and%20the%20ballot%20slip%20count%20of%20the%20VVPAT%2C%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20count%20shall%20prevail.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20at%20paragraph%20%3Cstrong%3Eno.%2000116%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20of%20the%20Complete%20Specifications%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Office%20BEL%20makes%20the%20following%20assertion%20about%20what%20is%20the%20vote%20(see%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EImage%209%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebelow)%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%5B00116%5D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20this%20manner%2C%20proposed%20system%20can%20faithfully%20record%20the%20%3Cu%3Edigital%20choice%20(vote%20being%20cast)%20of%20the%20voter%20(using%20the%20BU%20of%20the%20associated%20EVM)%3C%2Fu%3E%20%3Cu%3Ein%20form%20of%20a%20printed%20ballot%20slip%20that%20is%20directly%20and%20easily%20understood%20by%20the%20voter%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20voter%20has%20exercised%20his%2Fher%20digital%20choice%3C%2Fu%3E%3B%20and%20thereafter%20store%20the%20printed%20ballot%20slip%20at%20a%20secure%20location%20for%20further%20audit%20if%20required.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20not%20the%20digital%20choice%20of%20the%20voter%20as%20recorded%20by%20the%20VVPAT%20on%20paper%20which%20must%20be%20counted%2C%20and%20not%20merely%20the%20electronic%20data%20recorded%20in%20the%20CU%20which%20the%20voter%20will%20never%20get%20to%20see%20at%20the%20polling%20booth%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170454%2FImage-9.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22849%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170454%2FImage-9.jpg%20849w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170454%2FImage-9-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170454%2FImage-9-724x1024.jpg%20724w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697660%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3A%20Extract%20from%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20Complete%20Specifications%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20machine%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20piece%2C%20I%20raised%20these%20questions-%20%E2%80%9Ccan%20it%20then%20be%20said%20that%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20know%20is%20limited%20to%20accessing%20details%20about%20the%20public%20character%20of%20electoral%20candidates%20and%20nothing%20more%20relating%20to%20the%20electoral%20process%3F%20Does%20it%20not%20extend%20to%20seeking%20adequate%20knowledge%20about%20the%20current%20voting%20system%20which%20is%20facilitated%20through%20machines%20unlike%20the%20paper-based%20system%20that%20was%20the%20primary%20balloting%20method%20until%20a%20decade%20ago%3F%20When%20I%20began%20writing%20this%20piece%2C%20these%20questions%20were%20open-ended.%20However%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Constitution%20Bench%20which%20struck%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20route%20of%20funding%20political%20parties%20has%20answered%20them%20conclusively.%20While%20concurring%20with%20the%20judgement%20(%3Cem%3EAssociation%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20%26amp%3B%20Ar.%2C%20vs%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E)%20authored%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20D%20Y%20Chandrachud%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Bench%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20in%20his%20separate%20opinion%20says-%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C19.%20%3Cu%3EThe%20right%20to%20vote%20is%20a%20constitutional%20and%20statutory%20right%2C%E2%80%A6%20grounded%20in%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20as%20the%20casting%20of%20a%20vote%20amounts%20to%20expression%20of%20an%20opinion%20by%20the%20voter%E2%80%A6%20The%20citizens%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20know%20stems%20from%20this%20very%20right%2C%20as%20meaningfully%20exercising%20choice%20by%20voting%20requires%20information%3C%2Fu%3E.%20Representatives%20elected%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20votes%20cast%20in%20their%20favour%2C%20enact%20new%2C%20and%20amend%20existing%20laws%2C%20and%20when%20in%20power%2C%20take%20policy%20decisions.%20%3Cu%3EAccess%20to%20information%20which%20can%20materially%20shape%20the%20citizens%E2%80%99%20choice%20is%20necessary%20for%20them%20to%20have%20a%20say%20in%20how%20their%20lives%20are%20affected%3C%2Fu%3E.%20%3Cu%3EThus%2C%20the%20right%20to%20know%20is%20paramount%20for%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20and%20democracy%3C%2Fu%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20records%20the%20views%20of%20the%20Constitution%20Bench%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20voters%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20know%20in%20the%20following%20words%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C77.%20The%20following%20principles%20can%20be%20deduced%20from%20the%20decisions%20of%20this%20Court%20in%20ADR%20(supra)%20and%20PUCL%20(supra)%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3E%20The%20right%20to%20information%20of%20voters%20which%20is%20traced%20to%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20is%20built%20upon%20the%20jurisprudence%20of%20both%20the%20first%20and%20the%20second%20phases%20in%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20doctrine%2C%20identified%20above.%20%3Cu%3EThe%20common%20thread%20of%20reasoning%20which%20runs%20through%20both%20the%20first%20and%20the%20second%20phases%20is%20that%20information%20which%20furthers%20democratic%20participation%20must%20be%20provided%20to%20citizens.%20Voters%20have%20a%20right%20to%20information%20which%20would%20enable%20them%20to%20cast%20their%20votes%20rationally%20and%20intelligently%20because%20voting%20is%20one%20of%20the%20foremost%20forms%20of%20democratic%20participation%3C%2Fu%3E%3B%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20issues%20discussed%20above%20are%20just%20a%20sample%20of%20the%20multiple%20doubts%20that%20crop%20up%20when%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20answers%20to%20FAQs%20are%20compared%20with%20the%20contents%20of%20other%20publicly%20available%20documents%20about%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20must%20be%20said%2C%20our%20doubts%20will%20not%20go%20away%20by%20simply%20admonishing%20or%20ignoring%20them.%20The%20levels%20of%20transparency%20that%20the%20ECI%20has%20adopted%20are%20hopelessly%20inadequate%20to%20meet%20the%20very%20high%20standards%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20has%20set%20for%20our%20right%20to%20know%2C%20as%20citizen-voters.%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVenkatesh%20Nayak%20is%20Director%2C%20Commonwealth%20Human%20Rights%20Initiative%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20All%20facts%20narrated%20above%20are%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708172596000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10211621%2FEffect-2024-02-10T202212.238.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-election-commissions-faqs-on-evm-vvpats-dont-clear-cloud-of-suspicion-over-electoral-process%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20levels%20of%20transparency%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20have%20adopted%20are%20hopelessly%20inadequate%20to%20meet%20the%20very%20high%20standards%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20has%20set%20for%20our%20right%20to%20know%2C%20as%20citizen-voters.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-election-commissions-faqs-on-evm-vvpats-dont-clear-cloud-of-suspicion-over-electoral-process%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'No%20preparation'%20for%20influx%20of%20Palestinians%20at%20Rafah%20border%20-%20Egypt's%20foreign%20minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708171860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-rafah-palestinians_6458781.jpg%3F20240217134902%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisrael-hamas-war-no-preparation-whatsoever-for-influx-of-palestinian-civilians-at-gazas-rafah-border-crossing-says-egypts-foreign-minister-13073667%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Egyptian%20foreign%20minister%20has%20denied%20reports%20his%20country%20is%20preparing%20for%20an%20influx%20of%20refugees%20as%20Palestinians%20in%20Rafah%20face%20an%20expected%20Israeli%20ground%20offensive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A883%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisrael-hamas-war-no-preparation-whatsoever-for-influx-of-palestinian-civilians-at-gazas-rafah-border-crossing-says-egypts-foreign-minister-13073667%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-hamas-war-no-preparation-whatsoever-for-influx-of-palestinian-civilians-at-gazas-rafah-border-crossing-says-egypts-foreign-minister-13073667%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-hamas-war-no-preparation-whatsoever-for-influx-of-palestinian-civilians-at-gazas-rafah-border-crossing-says-egypts-foreign-minister-13073667%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Backstory%20%7C%20Moral%20of%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20Story%3A%20Information%20Is%20Essential%20for%20Democracy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F30183824%2FIMG_4397-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ETurning%20points%20have%20come%20but%20rarely%20in%20the%20ten%20years%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20given%20its%20astounding%20success%20in%20maintaining%20an%20iron-clad%2C%20surveillance-driven%20grip%20on%20every%20institution%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20of%20February%2015%20that%20outlawed%20electoral%20bonds%20is%20emphatically%20one%20of%20them%2C%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20recognised%20as%20another%20chance%20that%20has%20been%20given%20to%20us%2C%20as%20Indians%2C%20to%20redeem%20our%20besmirched%20republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20moment%20stands%20as%20testimony%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20to%20assert%20itself%2C%20something%20we%20felt%20it%20had%20become%20incapable%20of%20doing.%C2%A0%20It%20remembered%20its%20obligations%20to%20the%20Constitution%20and%20to%20one%20of%20its%20foundational%20principles%20%E2%80%93%20Article%2019%201(a)%20guaranteeing%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20as%20well%20as%20the%20concomitant%20right%20to%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%2C%20would%20the%20court%20have%20done%20the%20right%20thing%20and%20outlawed%20electoral%20bonds%20if%20it%20had%20not%20been%20for%20the%20dogged%20resistance%20of%20an%20unsung%2C%20often%20attacked%20and%20abused%20tribe%2C%20sometimes%20derided%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CRTI-%3Cem%3Ewallahs%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3F%20It%20is%20these%20women%20and%20men%20who%20kept%20up%20their%20date%20with%20the%20courts%2C%20%3Cem%3Etarikh-pe-tarikh%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20along%20with%20their%20praetorian%20guard%20of%20constitutional%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20journalist%20Nitin%20Sethi%2C%20tweeted%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%201%20or%202%20people%20or%20organisations.%20Many%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSauravDassss%5C%22%3E%40SauravDas%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Common%20Cause%2C%20Anjali%20B%20and%20her%20colleagues%2C%20Venkatesh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmediatrack_in%5C%22%3E%40mediatrack%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpoonamjourno%5C%22%3E%40poonamjourno%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmannama%5C%22%3E%40Amannama%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSharanyaHK%5C%22%3E%40SharanyaHK%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCommodoreBatra%5C%22%3E%40CommodoreBatra%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26amp%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fadrspeaks%5C%22%3E%40adrspeaks%3C%2Fa%3E%20leading.%20It%20took%20a%20village.%20But%20it%20ain%E2%80%99t%20over%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20did%20this%20right%20from%20the%20days%20when%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20was%20introduced%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Finance%20Bill%20in%20the%20Budget%20of%20February%202017.%20Within%20a%20span%20of%20six%20months%2C%20the%20lead%20petitioners%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20and%20Common%20Cause%2C%20were%20already%20knocking%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Altogether%20in%20the%20final%20hearing%20of%20the%20case%20there%20were%20five%20petitioners%20%E2%80%93%20apart%20from%20the%20lead%20petitioners%2C%20there%20were%20three%20tagged%20petitions%20representing%20the%20CPI(M)%2C%20Dr%20Jaya%20Thakur%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20banking%20lawyer%20Spandan%20Biswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20mainstream%20media%20generally%20preferring%20to%20look%20the%20other%20way%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20could%20drive%20a%20truck%20through%20the%20objections%20raised%20by%20various%20authorities%20to%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme.%20The%20Reserve%20Bank%2C%20as%20the%20recent%20apex%20court%20judgment%20noted%2C%20had%20as%20early%20as%20January%202017%20written%20to%20the%20Finance%20Ministry%20objecting%20to%20the%20proposal%20which%20it%20argued%20militated%20against%20its%20own%20authority%20to%20issue%20bearer%20instruments.%20Later%20Urjit%20Patel%2C%20who%20was%20then%20governor%20of%20the%20apex%20bank%2C%20conveyed%20to%20the%20finance%20ministry%20his%20views%20on%20the%20risks%20of%20money%20laundering%2C%20forgery%20and%20cross%20border%20counterfeiting%20that%20could%20emanate%20from%20the%20issuance%20of%20the%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20also%20displayed%20some%20spine%20in%20those%20early%20days.%20The%20judgment%20observed%20that%20on%20May%2026%2C%202017%2C%20the%20ECI%20wrote%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Law%20%26amp%3B%20Justice%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20amendments%20to%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20RPA%2C%20and%20Companies%20Act%20introduced%20by%20the%20Finance%20Act%202017%2C%20will%20have%20a%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20impact%20on%20transparency%20of%20political%20finance%2Ffunding%20of%20political%20parties%E2%80%9D.%20The%20ECI%20also%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20negative%20impacts%20that%20removing%20the%20cap%20on%20corporate%20donations%20would%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20one%20by%20one%2C%20these%20institutions%20fell%20silent%2C%20with%20the%20Modi%20government%20displaying%20extraordinary%20gumption%20and%20persisting%20with%20the%20scheme.%20And%20why%20would%20it%20not%3F%20The%20electoral%20bonds%20arrangement%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20cornucopia%20that%20the%20late%20finance%20minister%2C%20Arun%20Jaitley%2C%20had%20bequeathed%20his%20party%2C%20which%20gave%20and%20gave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20group%20that%20kept%20pushing%20back%20against%20it%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9CRTI-wallahs%E2%80%9D.%20It%20was%20their%20persistence%20which%20led%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20admitting%20in%20its%20order%20of%20April%2013%2C%202019%2C%20that%20the%20scheme%20gave%20rise%20to%20%E2%80%9Cweighty%20issues%20which%20have%20a%20bearing%20on%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20bench%2C%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20Ranjan%20Gogoi%2C%20refused%20to%20grant%20interim%20relief.%20A%20month%20later%2C%20in%20the%20general%20election%20that%20followed%2C%20the%20BJP%20emerged%20with%20an%20even%20bigger%20margin%20of%20votes%20than%20it%20had%20notched%20earlier%20(assisted%20undoubtedly%20by%20the%20generous%20flow%20of%20funds%20in%20its%20direction).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20discouraging%20trajectory%2C%20the%20petitioners%20kept%20filing%20petitions%2C%20time%20and%20again%2C%20but%20to%20little%20avail.%20On%20occasion%20the%20petitioners%20even%20met%20with%20hostility%20from%20their%20lordships.%20When%20the%20petition%20came%20up%20before%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20then%20chief%20justice%2C%20S.A.%20Bobde%2C%20it%20was%20not%20only%20rejected%20but%20firmly%20rebuffed%20with%20the%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20cannot%20be%20repeated%20applications%20seeking%20the%20same%20relief%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20days%20passed.%20In%20October%202023%2C%20with%20a%20new%20general%20election%20on%20the%20horizon%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20was%20once%20again%20approached%20by%20the%20petitioners.%20The%20bench%20led%20by%20the%20present%20chief%20justice%20saw%20the%20issue%20as%20one%20of%20%E2%80%9Cimportance%E2%80%9D%20and%20referred%20it%20to%20a%20constitution%20bench.%20A%20couple%20of%20hearings%20took%20place%20and%20a%20judgment%20was%20arrived%20at%20on%20November%202%2C%202023%2C%20which%20was%20reserved.%20The%20rest%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20this%20back%20story%20important%20for%20journalists%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20all%20about%20information%2C%20the%20life%20force%20of%20the%20profession.%20Many%20serious%20journalists%20%E2%80%93%20not%20of%20course%20the%20bejewelled%20and%20suited%20types%20inhabiting%20prime%20time%20%E2%80%93%20realised%20its%20worth%20and%20the%20value%20of%20chasing%20this%20story.%20They%20went%20on%20to%20unearth%20the%20unique%20alphanumeric%20number%20on%20the%20bond%20certificates%3B%20access%20file%20notings%3B%20and%20keep%20a%20river%20of%20information%20flowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20argument%20that%20the%20petitioners%20made%20to%20the%20court%20was%20straightforward%3A%20the%20opacity%20that%20marked%20the%20scheme%20%E2%80%9Cdefeats%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20know%20about%20the%20funding%20of%20political%20parties%20and%20promotes%20corruption.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Modi%20government%2C%20in%20its%20response%20was%20having%20none%20of%20that.%20It%20actually%20put%20forward%20the%20mind-blowing%20counter-argument%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccitizens%20did%20not%20have%20a%20%E2%80%98general%20right%20to%20know%20regarding%20the%20funding%20of%20political%20parties%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20emphasised%20that%20%E2%80%98right%20to%20know%E2%80%99%20itself%20is%20not%20a%20general%20right%20available%20to%20citizens%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpart-of-secret-ballot-how-the-modi-govt-backed-electoral-bonds-in-the-supreme-court%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNew%2520Delhi%253A%2520The%2520Supreme%2520Court%2Canonymous%2520donations%2520to%2520political%2520parties.%5C%22%3EPart%20of%20Secret%20Ballot%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20the%20Modi%20Govt%20Backed%20Electoral%20Bonds%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20February%2016).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20arguments%20did%20not%20fortunately%20convince%20the%20bench.%20There%20was%20no%20getting%20away%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20%E2%80%9Canonymity%E2%80%9D%20was%20crucial%20to%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%2C%20yet%20this%20very%20non-disclosure%20of%20information%20on%20electoral%20contributions%20was%20clearly%20violative%20of%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20the%20voter%20and%20therefore%20the%20freedom%20of%20expression%20guarantee%20in%20the%20constitution.%20This%20was%20the%20line%20the%20petitioners%20chose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20when%20it%20weighed%20in%2C%20cited%20two%20phases%20of%20court%20rulings%20on%20Article%2019%20(1)(a).%20The%20first%20linked%20the%20%E2%80%9Cright%20to%20information%20to%20the%20values%20of%20good%20governance%2C%20transparency%20and%20accountability%E2%80%9D%20and%20recognised%20the%20role%20of%20citizens%20in%20holding%20the%20state%20accountable%20for%20its%20actions%20and%20inactions%20and%20argued%20that%20they%20must%20possess%20relevant%20information%20in%20order%20to%20do%20this.%20In%20the%20second%20phase%2C%20the%20focus%20was%20on%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20jurisprudence%20on%20the%20right%20to%20information.%20In%20the%20second%20phase%2C%20various%20rulings%20had%20recognised%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceffective%20participation%20in%20democratic%20governance%20is%20not%20just%20a%20means%20to%20an%20end%20but%20is%20an%20end%20in%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20important%20to%20this%20process%20is%20information%20on%20political%20funding%3F%20The%20bench%20headed%20by%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20dwelt%20on%20this%20question%20and%20concluded%20that%20such%20information%20was%20essential%20if%20the%20voter%20is%20to%20exercise%20their%20franchise%20in%20an%20effective%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Electoral%20Bond%20Scheme%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20they%20infringe%20upon%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20the%20voter%20by%20anonymizing%20contributions%20through%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20are%20violative%20of%20Article%2019%20(1)(a).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20power%20of%20information%20to%20animate%20democracy%20was%20the%20leitmotif%20of%20this%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImran%20Khan%20%E2%80%98virtually%E2%80%99%20won%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%2C%20or%20should%20we%20say%20Imran%20Khan%20and%20his%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party%2C%20has%20beaten%20India%20in%20weaponising%20AI%20for%20electoral%20purposes%20%E2%80%93%20a%20trend%20that%20will%20almost%20certainly%20play%20out%20in%20the%20coming%20general%20election%20in%20this%20country%20later%20this%20year.%20But%20for%20Khan%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20necessity%20proving%20once%20again%20to%20be%20the%20mother%20of%20all%20invention.%20When%20he%20found%20himself%20in%20jail%2C%20for%20various%20alleged%20political%20crimes%20including%20fraud%20last%20August%2C%20he%20did%20not%20allow%20his%20incarceration%20to%20end%20his%20political%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20long%20an%20audio%20clip%20of%20his%20voice%20generated%20by%20AI%20addressed%20millions%20on%20social%20media%20in%20what%20was%20quickly%20labeled%20as%20a%20virtual%20election%20rally.%20The%20provenance%20of%20his%20speech%20had%20an%20interesting%20back%20story.%20It%20emerged%20from%20a%20script%20dictated%20by%20Khan%20in%20jail%20and%20a%20text-to-audio%20AI%20model%20was%20used%20to%20convert%20it%20into%20a%20speech%20which%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20drawn%20over%201.4%20million%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20frenetic%20period%20of%20campaigning%20for%20Khan%20%E2%80%93%20virtually.%20As%20the%20Pakistan%20general%20election%20drew%20closer%2C%20a%20four-minute%20declamation%20scripted%20in%20jail%2C%20vetted%20by%20lawyers%2C%20worked%20on%20by%20techies%20using%20an%20AI%20tool%20from%20ElevenLabs%2C%20went%20on%20to%20electrify%20the%20party%20base%20by%20mid-December.%20It%20was%20a%20hit%2C%20especially%20among%20the%20youngsters%20(Pakistan%20like%20India%20has%20a%20disproportionately%20higher%20number%20of%20young%20adults%20in%20its%20population%20of%20240%20million).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20audience%20on%20social%20media%20had%20quadrupled%20defeating%20the%20cynical%20stratagems%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%20that%20went%20out%20of%20its%20way%20to%20bind%20the%20man%20and%20gag%20him%20%E2%80%93%20politically%20speaking.%20Apps%20were%20created%20so%20that%20the%20Voice%20could%20now%20seamlessly%20inhabit%20the%20Facebook%20and%20WhatsApp%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20counting%20day%20it%20was%20discovered%20that%20despite%20the%20man%20being%20in%20jail%2C%20the%20independents%20associated%20with%20his%20party%20had%20together%20got%20more%20votes%20than%20their%20counterparts%2C%20notching%20wins%20in%2097%20out%20of%20265%20seats.%20When%20his%20rivals%20claimed%20to%20have%20won%2C%20once%20again%20the%20AI%20version%20of%20Imran%20Khan%20emerged%2C%20this%20time%20with%20a%20victory%20speech%20complete%20with%20rhetorical%20embellishments%20characteristic%20of%20the%20original%3A%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CMy%20beloved%20countrymen.%20By%20turning%20out%20in%20such%20huge%20numbers%20and%20exercising%20your%20democratic%20right%20of%20franchise%2C%20you%20have%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20freedom%20to%20exercise%20citizens%E2%80%99%20rights.%20I%20congratulate%20you%20all%20on%20helping%20us%20win%20the%20elections%20handsomely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20People%E2%80%99s%20party%20(PPP)%20cobbled%20up%20an%20understanding%20to%20form%20the%20next%20government%2C%20leaving%20Imran%20Khan%20by%20the%20wayside%20despite%20his%20%E2%80%9Cvictory%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20means%20that%20the%20virtual%20Imran%20Khan%20will%20continue%20to%20rock%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20political%20boat%20in%20the%20years%20to%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVoices%20airbrushed%20out%20of%20the%20frame%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20lines%20jumped%20out%20of%20the%20page%20for%20me%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20families%20of%20those%20who%20had%20died%20on%2022%20December%20were%20not%20moved.%20Speaking%20about%20the%20new%20solar%20lights%20that%20had%20been%20set%20up%20across%20the%20village%20under%20Operation%20Sadbhavana%2C%20Lal%E2%80%99s%20daughter-in-law%2C%20Rangeela%20Begum%2C%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98They%20blacked%20out%20our%20lives%20and%20are%20now%20installing%20solar%20lights%E2%80%A6this%20is%20no%20substitute%20for%20justice.%20It%E2%80%99s%20just%20hooliganism.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20affected%20families%2C%20the%20bundles%20of%20cash%20they%20received%E2%80%94Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20the%20dead%20and%20lesser%20for%20the%20injured%E2%80%94were%20expected%20to%20replace%20their%20loved%20ones.%20Nazir%2C%20Shaukat%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20was%20visited%20by%20the%20commanding%20officer%20of%20the%2016%20RR%20and%20a%20brigadier%2C%20who%20handed%20him%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%20Vali%20was%20given%20the%20same%20amount.%20He%20told%20me%20he%20did%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do%20with%20it.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20labourers%20and%20I%20have%20worked%20my%20whole%20life%20with%20the%20border%20roads%20organisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20raised%20my%20children%20in%20extreme%20poverty%20and%20hoped%20one%20day%20they%20will%20take%20care%20of%20me%20when%20I%20get%20old.%E2%80%9D%20The%20money%20would%20do%20little%20to%20help.%20Farooq%20got%20Rs%202.3%20lakh%2C%20while%20Irfaan%20got%20Rs%201.5%20lakh.%20Fazal%20was%20given%20Rs%202.5%20lakh.%20Now%20barely%20able%20to%20walk%2C%20he%20told%20me%20the%20money%20was%20meaningless.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20five%20kids%20and%20a%20family%20of%20seven%20to%20support.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20myself%20being%20able%20to%20work%20ever%20again.%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fread-the-caravans-article-on-army-torture-the-union-government-wants-taken-down%5C%22%3EThe%20Caravan%E2%80%99s%20Article%20on%20Army%20Torture%20the%20Union%20Government%20Wants%20Taken%20Down%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20February%2013)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVanessa%20Dougnac%20is%20deported%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20shameful%20that%20former%20South%20Asia%20Correspondent%20for%20%3Cem%3ELa%20Croix%2C%20Le%20Point%2C%20Le%20Temps%2C%20Le%20Soir%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20has%20lived%20and%20worked%20as%20a%20professional%20in%20India%20for%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20has%20been%20deported%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20for%20her%20independent%20reporting%20on%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20in%20the%20Indian%20journalistic%20community%20who%20found%20this%20act%20of%20deportation%20abhorrent%20and%20a%20violation%20of%20media%20freedom%20in%20a%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20farewell%20letter%20was%20widely%20covered%20in%20the%20print%20media%2C%20along%20with%20its%20resonating%20opening%20lines%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20writing%20these%20words%20in%20tears.%20Today%2C%20I%20am%20leaving%20India%2C%20the%20country%20where%20I%20came%2025%20years%20ago%20as%20a%20student%2C%20and%20where%20I%20have%20worked%20for%2023%20years%20as%20a%20journalist.%20The%20place%20where%20I%20married%2C%20raised%20my%20son%2C%20and%20which%20I%20call%20my%20home.%C2%A0Leaving%20is%20not%20my%20choice%E2%80%9D%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ffrench-journalist-vanessa-dougnac-leaves-india-amid-expulsion-threat%5C%22%3EFrench%20Journalist%20Vanessa%20Dougnac%20Leaves%20India%20Amid%20Expulsion%20Threat%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20February%2016).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReaders%20write%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedia%20repression%20and%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESujata%20Madhok%20and%20A.M.%20Jigeesh%2C%20president%20and%20general%20secretary%20respectively%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%2C%20wrote%20in%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%20(DUJ)%20is%20deeply%20concerned%20that%20journalists%20are%20among%20those%20injured%20by%20police%20action%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests.%20Two%20journalists%2C%20Satender%20Chauhan%20and%20Niel%20Bhalinder%20Singh%2C%20suffered%20injuries%20while%20covering%20the%20protests%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20border%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSatender%20Chauhan%2C%20correspondent%20for%20Aaj%20Tak%2C%20was%20%E2%80%98live%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20channel%20when%20he%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20%E2%80%98chharra%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20eye%20area.%20The%20channel%20showed%20a%20colleague%20helping%20him%20to%20leave%20the%20spot.%20He%20was%20taken%20to%20hospital.%20Niel%20Bhalinder%20Singh%20of%20the%20Savera%20group%20of%20newspapers%20was%20taken%20to%20hospital%20bleeding%20heavily%20as%20a%20tear%20gas%20shell%20fired%20by%20a%20drone%20fell%20on%20his%20head.%20Unconfirmed%20reports%20have%20also%20come%20in%20regarding%20injuries%20to%20other%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Patiala%20Media%20Club%20and%20the%20Chandigarh%20Press%20Club%20have%20demanded%20safety%20for%20journalists%20covering%20such%20events.%20The%20DUJ%20is%20also%20concerned%20at%20the%20Internet%20shutdown%20imposed%20in%20seven%20districts%20of%20Haryana%20and%20three%20districts%20of%20Rajasthan%20which%20has%20made%20it%20extremely%20difficult%20for%20journalists%20to%20cover%20the%20protests.%20They%20also%20note%20that%20social%20media%20accounts%20of%20some%20journalists%20including%20Mandeep%20Punia%20of%20Gaon%20Savera%20have%20been%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDUJ%20condemned%20the%20violence%20on%20protesting%20farmers%20that%20has%20led%20to%20injuries%20and%20hospitalizations.%20They%20urged%20the%20central%20government%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demands%20are%20settled%20amicably.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20response%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReporting%20on%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20agitation%20has%20always%20been%20fraught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20eight%20journalists%20who%20had%20reported%20on%20the%20violence%20that%20broke%20out%20on%20Republic%20Day%20in%20Delhi%2C%20including%20the%20founder-editor%20of%20The%20Wire%2C%20had%20sedition%20and%20other%20criminal%20charges%20brought%20against%20them.%20This%20time%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20piece%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-social-media-accounts-withheld-protest%5C%22%3EAgenda%20Is%20to%20Silence%20Us%E2%80%99%3A%20Key%20Social%20Media%20Accounts%20Withheld%2C%20Farmers%20Vow%20to%20Boycott%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20Meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20(February%2014)%2C%20has%20highlighted%20how%20X%20accounts%20and%20Facebook%20pages%20of%20prominent%20farmer%20leaders%20as%20well%20as%20many%20others%20have%20been%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20banned%20official%20pages%20which%20supported%20the%20movement%20and%20posted%20updates%20on%20it%2C%20like%20%40Tractor2twitr_P%20run%20by%20Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%20and%20Progressive%20Farmers%20Front%2C%20run%20by%20Guramneet%20Singh%20Mangat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20the%20process%20of%20withholding%20these%20accounts%20has%20been%20largely%20understood%20to%20be%20opaque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20very%20interesting%20aspect%20of%20this%20repression%20was%20highlighted%20by%20Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20%40Tractor2Twitr_i%20page%20on%20X.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20Wire%20which%20was%20quoted%20in%20the%20story%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20accounts%20were%20withheld%20even%20as%20farmer%20leaders%20were%20sitting%20at%20a%20meeting%20with%20union%20ministers%20on%20February%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20an%20assumption%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20Union%20government%20but%20the%20Punjab%20government%20too%20which%20was%20involved%20in%20singling%20out%20farmer%20union%20leaders%E2%80%99%20accounts.%20This%20is%20a%20dangerous%20trend%2C%20as%20those%20accounts%20which%20were%20running%20propaganda%20against%20farmers%20are%20getting%20support%20while%20the%20official%20mouthpieces%20of%20farmers%20meant%20to%20debunk%20the%20propaganda%20and%20misinformation%20are%20being%20targeted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWrite%20to%20ombudsperson%40thewire.in.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708167903000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F30183824%2FIMG_4397-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-electoral-bond-journalists-ai-imran-khan-farmers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fortnightly%20column%20from%20The%20Wire's%20ombudsperson.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-electoral-bond-journalists-ai-imran-khan-farmers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Backstory%20%7C%20Moral%20of%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20Story%3A%20Information%20Is%20Essential%20for%20Democracy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F30183824%2FIMG_4397-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ETurning%20points%20have%20come%20but%20rarely%20in%20the%20ten%20years%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20given%20its%20astounding%20success%20in%20maintaining%20an%20iron-clad%2C%20surveillance-driven%20grip%20on%20every%20institution%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20of%20February%2015%20that%20outlawed%20electoral%20bonds%20is%20emphatically%20one%20of%20them%2C%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20recognised%20as%20another%20chance%20that%20has%20been%20given%20to%20us%2C%20as%20Indians%2C%20to%20redeem%20our%20besmirched%20republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20moment%20stands%20as%20testimony%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20to%20assert%20itself%2C%20something%20we%20felt%20it%20had%20become%20incapable%20of%20doing.%C2%A0%20It%20remembered%20its%20obligations%20to%20the%20Constitution%20and%20to%20one%20of%20its%20foundational%20principles%20%E2%80%93%20Article%2019%201(a)%20guaranteeing%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20as%20well%20as%20the%20concomitant%20right%20to%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%2C%20would%20the%20court%20have%20done%20the%20right%20thing%20and%20outlawed%20electoral%20bonds%20if%20it%20had%20not%20been%20for%20the%20dogged%20resistance%20of%20an%20unsung%2C%20often%20attacked%20and%20abused%20tribe%2C%20sometimes%20derided%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CRTI-%3Cem%3Ewallahs%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3F%20It%20is%20these%20women%20and%20men%20who%20kept%20up%20their%20date%20with%20the%20courts%2C%20%3Cem%3Etarikh-pe-tarikh%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20along%20with%20their%20praetorian%20guard%20of%20constitutional%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20journalist%20Nitin%20Sethi%2C%20tweeted%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%201%20or%202%20people%20or%20organisations.%20Many%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSauravDassss%5C%22%3E%40SauravDas%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Common%20Cause%2C%20Anjali%20B%20and%20her%20colleagues%2C%20Venkatesh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmediatrack_in%5C%22%3E%40mediatrack%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpoonamjourno%5C%22%3E%40poonamjourno%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmannama%5C%22%3E%40Amannama%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSharanyaHK%5C%22%3E%40SharanyaHK%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCommodoreBatra%5C%22%3E%40CommodoreBatra%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26amp%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fadrspeaks%5C%22%3E%40adrspeaks%3C%2Fa%3E%20leading.%20It%20took%20a%20village.%20But%20it%20ain%E2%80%99t%20over%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20did%20this%20right%20from%20the%20days%20when%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20was%20introduced%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Finance%20Bill%20in%20the%20Budget%20of%20February%202017.%20Within%20a%20span%20of%20six%20months%2C%20the%20lead%20petitioners%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20and%20Common%20Cause%2C%20were%20already%20knocking%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Altogether%20in%20the%20final%20hearing%20of%20the%20case%20there%20were%20five%20petitioners%20%E2%80%93%20apart%20from%20the%20lead%20petitioners%2C%20there%20were%20three%20tagged%20petitions%20representing%20the%20CPI(M)%2C%20Dr%20Jaya%20Thakur%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20banking%20lawyer%20Spandan%20Biswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20mainstream%20media%20generally%20preferring%20to%20look%20the%20other%20way%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20could%20drive%20a%20truck%20through%20the%20objections%20raised%20by%20various%20authorities%20to%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme.%20The%20Reserve%20Bank%2C%20as%20the%20recent%20apex%20court%20judgment%20noted%2C%20had%20as%20early%20as%20January%202017%20written%20to%20the%20Finance%20Ministry%20objecting%20to%20the%20proposal%20which%20it%20argued%20militated%20against%20its%20own%20authority%20to%20issue%20bearer%20instruments.%20Later%20Urjit%20Patel%2C%20who%20was%20then%20governor%20of%20the%20apex%20bank%2C%20conveyed%20to%20the%20finance%20ministry%20his%20views%20on%20the%20risks%20of%20money%20laundering%2C%20forgery%20and%20cross%20border%20counterfeiting%20that%20could%20emanate%20from%20the%20issuance%20of%20the%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20also%20displayed%20some%20spine%20in%20those%20early%20days.%20The%20judgment%20observed%20that%20on%20May%2026%2C%202017%2C%20the%20ECI%20wrote%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Law%20%26amp%3B%20Justice%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20amendments%20to%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20RPA%2C%20and%20Companies%20Act%20introduced%20by%20the%20Finance%20Act%202017%2C%20will%20have%20a%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20impact%20on%20transparency%20of%20political%20finance%2Ffunding%20of%20political%20parties%E2%80%9D.%20The%20ECI%20also%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20negative%20impacts%20that%20removing%20the%20cap%20on%20corporate%20donations%20would%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20one%20by%20one%2C%20these%20institutions%20fell%20silent%2C%20with%20the%20Modi%20government%20displaying%20extraordinary%20gumption%20and%20persisting%20with%20the%20scheme.%20And%20why%20would%20it%20not%3F%20The%20electoral%20bonds%20arrangement%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20cornucopia%20that%20the%20late%20finance%20minister%2C%20Arun%20Jaitley%2C%20had%20bequeathed%20his%20party%2C%20which%20gave%20and%20gave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20group%20that%20kept%20pushing%20back%20against%20it%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9CRTI-wallahs%E2%80%9D.%20It%20was%20their%20persistence%20which%20led%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20admitting%20in%20its%20order%20of%20April%2013%2C%202019%2C%20that%20the%20scheme%20gave%20rise%20to%20%E2%80%9Cweighty%20issues%20which%20have%20a%20bearing%20on%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20bench%2C%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20Ranjan%20Gogoi%2C%20refused%20to%20grant%20interim%20relief.%20A%20month%20later%2C%20in%20the%20general%20election%20that%20followed%2C%20the%20BJP%20emerged%20with%20an%20even%20bigger%20margin%20of%20votes%20than%20it%20had%20notched%20earlier%20(assisted%20undoubtedly%20by%20the%20generous%20flow%20of%20funds%20in%20its%20direction).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20discouraging%20trajectory%2C%20the%20petitioners%20kept%20filing%20petitions%2C%20time%20and%20again%2C%20but%20to%20little%20avail.%20On%20occasion%20the%20petitioners%20even%20met%20with%20hostility%20from%20their%20lordships.%20When%20the%20petition%20came%20up%20before%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20then%20chief%20justice%2C%20S.A.%20Bobde%2C%20it%20was%20not%20only%20rejected%20but%20firmly%20rebuffed%20with%20the%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20cannot%20be%20repeated%20applications%20seeking%20the%20same%20relief%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20days%20passed.%20In%20October%202023%2C%20with%20a%20new%20general%20election%20on%20the%20horizon%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20was%20once%20again%20approached%20by%20the%20petitioners.%20The%20bench%20led%20by%20the%20present%20chief%20justice%20saw%20the%20issue%20as%20one%20of%20%E2%80%9Cimportance%E2%80%9D%20and%20referred%20it%20to%20a%20constitution%20bench.%20A%20couple%20of%20hearings%20took%20place%20and%20a%20judgment%20was%20arrived%20at%20on%20November%202%2C%202023%2C%20which%20was%20reserved.%20The%20rest%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20this%20back%20story%20important%20for%20journalists%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20all%20about%20information%2C%20the%20life%20force%20of%20the%20profession.%20Many%20serious%20journalists%20%E2%80%93%20not%20of%20course%20the%20bejewelled%20and%20suited%20types%20inhabiting%20prime%20time%20%E2%80%93%20realised%20its%20worth%20and%20the%20value%20of%20chasing%20this%20story.%20They%20went%20on%20to%20unearth%20the%20unique%20alphanumeric%20number%20on%20the%20bond%20certificates%3B%20access%20file%20notings%3B%20and%20keep%20a%20river%20of%20information%20flowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20argument%20that%20the%20petitioners%20made%20to%20the%20court%20was%20straightforward%3A%20the%20opacity%20that%20marked%20the%20scheme%20%E2%80%9Cdefeats%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20know%20about%20the%20funding%20of%20political%20parties%20and%20promotes%20corruption.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Modi%20government%2C%20in%20its%20response%20was%20having%20none%20of%20that.%20It%20actually%20put%20forward%20the%20mind-blowing%20counter-argument%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccitizens%20did%20not%20have%20a%20%E2%80%98general%20right%20to%20know%20regarding%20the%20funding%20of%20political%20parties%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20emphasised%20that%20%E2%80%98right%20to%20know%E2%80%99%20itself%20is%20not%20a%20general%20right%20available%20to%20citizens%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpart-of-secret-ballot-how-the-modi-govt-backed-electoral-bonds-in-the-supreme-court%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNew%2520Delhi%253A%2520The%2520Supreme%2520Court%2Canonymous%2520donations%2520to%2520political%2520parties.%5C%22%3EPart%20of%20Secret%20Ballot%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20the%20Modi%20Govt%20Backed%20Electoral%20Bonds%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20February%2016).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20arguments%20did%20not%20fortunately%20convince%20the%20bench.%20There%20was%20no%20getting%20away%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20%E2%80%9Canonymity%E2%80%9D%20was%20crucial%20to%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%2C%20yet%20this%20very%20non-disclosure%20of%20information%20on%20electoral%20contributions%20was%20clearly%20violative%20of%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20the%20voter%20and%20therefore%20the%20freedom%20of%20expression%20guarantee%20in%20the%20constitution.%20This%20was%20the%20line%20the%20petitioners%20chose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20when%20it%20weighed%20in%2C%20cited%20two%20phases%20of%20court%20rulings%20on%20Article%2019%20(1)(a).%20The%20first%20linked%20the%20%E2%80%9Cright%20to%20information%20to%20the%20values%20of%20good%20governance%2C%20transparency%20and%20accountability%E2%80%9D%20and%20recognised%20the%20role%20of%20citizens%20in%20holding%20the%20state%20accountable%20for%20its%20actions%20and%20inactions%20and%20argued%20that%20they%20must%20possess%20relevant%20information%20in%20order%20to%20do%20this.%20In%20the%20second%20phase%2C%20the%20focus%20was%20on%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20jurisprudence%20on%20the%20right%20to%20information.%20In%20the%20second%20phase%2C%20various%20rulings%20had%20recognised%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceffective%20participation%20in%20democratic%20governance%20is%20not%20just%20a%20means%20to%20an%20end%20but%20is%20an%20end%20in%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20important%20to%20this%20process%20is%20information%20on%20political%20funding%3F%20The%20bench%20headed%20by%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20dwelt%20on%20this%20question%20and%20concluded%20that%20such%20information%20was%20essential%20if%20the%20voter%20is%20to%20exercise%20their%20franchise%20in%20an%20effective%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Electoral%20Bond%20Scheme%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20they%20infringe%20upon%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20the%20voter%20by%20anonymizing%20contributions%20through%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20are%20violative%20of%20Article%2019%20(1)(a).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20power%20of%20information%20to%20animate%20democracy%20was%20the%20leitmotif%20of%20this%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImran%20Khan%20%E2%80%98virtually%E2%80%99%20won%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%2C%20or%20should%20we%20say%20Imran%20Khan%20and%20his%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party%2C%20has%20beaten%20India%20in%20weaponising%20AI%20for%20electoral%20purposes%20%E2%80%93%20a%20trend%20that%20will%20almost%20certainly%20play%20out%20in%20the%20coming%20general%20election%20in%20this%20country%20later%20this%20year.%20But%20for%20Khan%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20necessity%20proving%20once%20again%20to%20be%20the%20mother%20of%20all%20invention.%20When%20he%20found%20himself%20in%20jail%2C%20for%20various%20alleged%20political%20crimes%20including%20fraud%20last%20August%2C%20he%20did%20not%20allow%20his%20incarceration%20to%20end%20his%20political%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20long%20an%20audio%20clip%20of%20his%20voice%20generated%20by%20AI%20addressed%20millions%20on%20social%20media%20in%20what%20was%20quickly%20labeled%20as%20a%20virtual%20election%20rally.%20The%20provenance%20of%20his%20speech%20had%20an%20interesting%20back%20story.%20It%20emerged%20from%20a%20script%20dictated%20by%20Khan%20in%20jail%20and%20a%20text-to-audio%20AI%20model%20was%20used%20to%20convert%20it%20into%20a%20speech%20which%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20drawn%20over%201.4%20million%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20frenetic%20period%20of%20campaigning%20for%20Khan%20%E2%80%93%20virtually.%20As%20the%20Pakistan%20general%20election%20drew%20closer%2C%20a%20four-minute%20declamation%20scripted%20in%20jail%2C%20vetted%20by%20lawyers%2C%20worked%20on%20by%20techies%20using%20an%20AI%20tool%20from%20ElevenLabs%2C%20went%20on%20to%20electrify%20the%20party%20base%20by%20mid-December.%20It%20was%20a%20hit%2C%20especially%20among%20the%20youngsters%20(Pakistan%20like%20India%20has%20a%20disproportionately%20higher%20number%20of%20young%20adults%20in%20its%20population%20of%20240%20million).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20audience%20on%20social%20media%20had%20quadrupled%20defeating%20the%20cynical%20stratagems%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%20that%20went%20out%20of%20its%20way%20to%20bind%20the%20man%20and%20gag%20him%20%E2%80%93%20politically%20speaking.%20Apps%20were%20created%20so%20that%20the%20Voice%20could%20now%20seamlessly%20inhabit%20the%20Facebook%20and%20WhatsApp%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20counting%20day%20it%20was%20discovered%20that%20despite%20the%20man%20being%20in%20jail%2C%20the%20independents%20associated%20with%20his%20party%20had%20together%20got%20more%20votes%20than%20their%20counterparts%2C%20notching%20wins%20in%2097%20out%20of%20265%20seats.%20When%20his%20rivals%20claimed%20to%20have%20won%2C%20once%20again%20the%20AI%20version%20of%20Imran%20Khan%20emerged%2C%20this%20time%20with%20a%20victory%20speech%20complete%20with%20rhetorical%20embellishments%20characteristic%20of%20the%20original%3A%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CMy%20beloved%20countrymen.%20By%20turning%20out%20in%20such%20huge%20numbers%20and%20exercising%20your%20democratic%20right%20of%20franchise%2C%20you%20have%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20freedom%20to%20exercise%20citizens%E2%80%99%20rights.%20I%20congratulate%20you%20all%20on%20helping%20us%20win%20the%20elections%20handsomely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20People%E2%80%99s%20party%20(PPP)%20cobbled%20up%20an%20understanding%20to%20form%20the%20next%20government%2C%20leaving%20Imran%20Khan%20by%20the%20wayside%20despite%20his%20%E2%80%9Cvictory%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20means%20that%20the%20virtual%20Imran%20Khan%20will%20continue%20to%20rock%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20political%20boat%20in%20the%20years%20to%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVoices%20airbrushed%20out%20of%20the%20frame%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20lines%20jumped%20out%20of%20the%20page%20for%20me%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20families%20of%20those%20who%20had%20died%20on%2022%20December%20were%20not%20moved.%20Speaking%20about%20the%20new%20solar%20lights%20that%20had%20been%20set%20up%20across%20the%20village%20under%20Operation%20Sadbhavana%2C%20Lal%E2%80%99s%20daughter-in-law%2C%20Rangeela%20Begum%2C%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98They%20blacked%20out%20our%20lives%20and%20are%20now%20installing%20solar%20lights%E2%80%A6this%20is%20no%20substitute%20for%20justice.%20It%E2%80%99s%20just%20hooliganism.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20affected%20families%2C%20the%20bundles%20of%20cash%20they%20received%E2%80%94Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20the%20dead%20and%20lesser%20for%20the%20injured%E2%80%94were%20expected%20to%20replace%20their%20loved%20ones.%20Nazir%2C%20Shaukat%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20was%20visited%20by%20the%20commanding%20officer%20of%20the%2016%20RR%20and%20a%20brigadier%2C%20who%20handed%20him%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%20Vali%20was%20given%20the%20same%20amount.%20He%20told%20me%20he%20did%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do%20with%20it.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20labourers%20and%20I%20have%20worked%20my%20whole%20life%20with%20the%20border%20roads%20organisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20raised%20my%20children%20in%20extreme%20poverty%20and%20hoped%20one%20day%20they%20will%20take%20care%20of%20me%20when%20I%20get%20old.%E2%80%9D%20The%20money%20would%20do%20little%20to%20help.%20Farooq%20got%20Rs%202.3%20lakh%2C%20while%20Irfaan%20got%20Rs%201.5%20lakh.%20Fazal%20was%20given%20Rs%202.5%20lakh.%20Now%20barely%20able%20to%20walk%2C%20he%20told%20me%20the%20money%20was%20meaningless.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20five%20kids%20and%20a%20family%20of%20seven%20to%20support.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20myself%20being%20able%20to%20work%20ever%20again.%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fread-the-caravans-article-on-army-torture-the-union-government-wants-taken-down%5C%22%3EThe%20Caravan%E2%80%99s%20Article%20on%20Army%20Torture%20the%20Union%20Government%20Wants%20Taken%20Down%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20February%2013)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVanessa%20Dougnac%20is%20deported%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20shameful%20that%20former%20South%20Asia%20Correspondent%20for%20%3Cem%3ELa%20Croix%2C%20Le%20Point%2C%20Le%20Temps%2C%20Le%20Soir%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20has%20lived%20and%20worked%20as%20a%20professional%20in%20India%20for%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20has%20been%20deported%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20for%20her%20independent%20reporting%20on%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20in%20the%20Indian%20journalistic%20community%20who%20found%20this%20act%20of%20deportation%20abhorrent%20and%20a%20violation%20of%20media%20freedom%20in%20a%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20farewell%20letter%20was%20widely%20covered%20in%20the%20print%20media%2C%20along%20with%20its%20resonating%20opening%20lines%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20writing%20these%20words%20in%20tears.%20Today%2C%20I%20am%20leaving%20India%2C%20the%20country%20where%20I%20came%2025%20years%20ago%20as%20a%20student%2C%20and%20where%20I%20have%20worked%20for%2023%20years%20as%20a%20journalist.%20The%20place%20where%20I%20married%2C%20raised%20my%20son%2C%20and%20which%20I%20call%20my%20home.%C2%A0Leaving%20is%20not%20my%20choice%E2%80%9D%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ffrench-journalist-vanessa-dougnac-leaves-india-amid-expulsion-threat%5C%22%3EFrench%20Journalist%20Vanessa%20Dougnac%20Leaves%20India%20Amid%20Expulsion%20Threat%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20February%2016).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReaders%20write%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedia%20repression%20and%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESujata%20Madhok%20and%20A.M.%20Jigeesh%2C%20president%20and%20general%20secretary%20respectively%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%2C%20wrote%20in%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%20(DUJ)%20is%20deeply%20concerned%20that%20journalists%20are%20among%20those%20injured%20by%20police%20action%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests.%20Two%20journalists%2C%20Satender%20Chauhan%20and%20Niel%20Bhalinder%20Singh%2C%20suffered%20injuries%20while%20covering%20the%20protests%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20border%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSatender%20Chauhan%2C%20correspondent%20for%20Aaj%20Tak%2C%20was%20%E2%80%98live%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20channel%20when%20he%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20%E2%80%98chharra%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20eye%20area.%20The%20channel%20showed%20a%20colleague%20helping%20him%20to%20leave%20the%20spot.%20He%20was%20taken%20to%20hospital.%20Niel%20Bhalinder%20Singh%20of%20the%20Savera%20group%20of%20newspapers%20was%20taken%20to%20hospital%20bleeding%20heavily%20as%20a%20tear%20gas%20shell%20fired%20by%20a%20drone%20fell%20on%20his%20head.%20Unconfirmed%20reports%20have%20also%20come%20in%20regarding%20injuries%20to%20other%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Patiala%20Media%20Club%20and%20the%20Chandigarh%20Press%20Club%20have%20demanded%20safety%20for%20journalists%20covering%20such%20events.%20The%20DUJ%20is%20also%20concerned%20at%20the%20Internet%20shutdown%20imposed%20in%20seven%20districts%20of%20Haryana%20and%20three%20districts%20of%20Rajasthan%20which%20has%20made%20it%20extremely%20difficult%20for%20journalists%20to%20cover%20the%20protests.%20They%20also%20note%20that%20social%20media%20accounts%20of%20some%20journalists%20including%20Mandeep%20Punia%20of%20Gaon%20Savera%20have%20been%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDUJ%20condemned%20the%20violence%20on%20protesting%20farmers%20that%20has%20led%20to%20injuries%20and%20hospitalizations.%20They%20urged%20the%20central%20government%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demands%20are%20settled%20amicably.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20response%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReporting%20on%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20agitation%20has%20always%20been%20fraught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20eight%20journalists%20who%20had%20reported%20on%20the%20violence%20that%20broke%20out%20on%20Republic%20Day%20in%20Delhi%2C%20including%20the%20founder-editor%20of%20The%20Wire%2C%20had%20sedition%20and%20other%20criminal%20charges%20brought%20against%20them.%20This%20time%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20piece%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-social-media-accounts-withheld-protest%5C%22%3EAgenda%20Is%20to%20Silence%20Us%E2%80%99%3A%20Key%20Social%20Media%20Accounts%20Withheld%2C%20Farmers%20Vow%20to%20Boycott%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20Meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20(February%2014)%2C%20has%20highlighted%20how%20X%20accounts%20and%20Facebook%20pages%20of%20prominent%20farmer%20leaders%20as%20well%20as%20many%20others%20have%20been%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20banned%20official%20pages%20which%20supported%20the%20movement%20and%20posted%20updates%20on%20it%2C%20like%20%40Tractor2twitr_P%20run%20by%20Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%20and%20Progressive%20Farmers%20Front%2C%20run%20by%20Guramneet%20Singh%20Mangat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20the%20process%20of%20withholding%20these%20accounts%20has%20been%20largely%20understood%20to%20be%20opaque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20very%20interesting%20aspect%20of%20this%20repression%20was%20highlighted%20by%20Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20%40Tractor2Twitr_i%20page%20on%20X.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20Wire%20which%20was%20quoted%20in%20the%20story%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20accounts%20were%20withheld%20even%20as%20farmer%20leaders%20were%20sitting%20at%20a%20meeting%20with%20union%20ministers%20on%20February%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20an%20assumption%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20Union%20g