emen.%20Currently%2C%20the%20farmers%20sell%20loose%20produce%20at%20local%20stores%20and%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20avenues%20where%20they%20can%20sell.%20So%20we%20have%20created%20this%20brand%20%5BKanthalloor%20Millets%5D%20and%20shown%20them%20ways%20to%20sell%20to%20become%20self-reliant%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pratima%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20millet%20will%20also%20be%20part%20of%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20programmes%20at%20the%20%3Cem%3Eanganwadis%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Kanthalloor%20received%20the%20%E2%80%98Best%20Rural%20Tourism%20Village%20Gold%20Award%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20Union%20Government.%20With%20more%20than%20250%20homestays%2C%20the%20village%20attracts%20many%20visitors%20on%20weekends.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325105%2Fhyderabad-entrepreneur-raju-bhupati-makes-affordable-troo-good-millet-snacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMillet%20kiosks%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20set%20up%20at%20each%20homestay%2C%20serving%20as%20both%20sales%20points%20and%20seed%20banks%20for%20Kanthalloor%20Millets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201201px)%20100vw%2C%201201px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo2-1708067456.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221201%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Millet%20kiosks%20will%20be%20set%20up%20at%20each%20homestay%2C%20serving%20as%20both%20sales%20points%20and%20seed%20banks%20for%20Kanthalloor%20Millets.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo2-1708067456.jpeg%201201w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo2-1708067456-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo2-1708067456-500x666.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2