0this%20scientist%20would%20befriend%20her%2C%20she%20accepted%20the%20request%2C%20and%20the%20rest%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20got%20chatting%20about%20science%2C%20which%20later%20led%20to%20their%20meeting.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%2072-year-old%20shared%20that%20Atul%20told%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20very%20happy%20and%20busy%20running%20around%2C%20but%20if%20you%20want%20change%20%5Bcompanionship%5D%2C%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20happen%20automatically.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20article%20penned%20by%20Atul%2C%20who%20had%20tragically%20lost%20his%20wife%20of%2036%20years%20to%20cancer%2C%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20Suhasini.%20Atul%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20showed%20how%20he%20decided%20to%20make%20his%20late%20wife%20happy%2C%20instead%20of%20%E2%80%9Csitting%20and%20crying%20over%20it%E2%80%9D.%20This%20resilient%20outlook%20towards%20life%20resonated%20with%20Suhasini%20and%20was%20instrumental%20in%20her%20falling%20in%20love%20with%20Atul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20lived%20alone%20in%20Mumbai%20for%2020%20years%20before%20meeting%20Atul%2C%20this%20is%20Suhasini%E2%80%99s%20first%20marriage.%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20thought%20of%20getting%20married.%20You%20commit%20because%20you%20want%20to%2C%20not%20because%20society%20is%20pushing%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707915442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FAjrqPGWSJgE%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Remarriage%2C%20once%20taboo%2C%20is%20now%20embraced%2C%20exemplified%20by%20children%20advocating%20for%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20happiness.%20These%20Valentine%E2%80%99s%20Day%20tales%20of%20love%20underscore%20the%20timeless%20